"use strict";(globalThis.webpackChunkwebsite=globalThis.webpackChunkwebsite||[]).push([[3345],{2858(e){e.exports=JSON.parse('{"archive":{"blogPosts":[{"id":"rentiva-v4.33.1-release","metadata":{"permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/rentiva-v4.33.1-release","editUrl":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade/mhm-rentiva-docs/tree/main/blog/2026-04-29-rentiva-v4.33.1-release.md","source":"@site/i18n/tr/docusaurus-plugin-content-blog/2026-04-29-rentiva-v4.33.1-release.md","title":"Rentiva v4.33.1 \u2014 Arama Cilas\u0131 ve Bayi Ad\u0131 D\xfczeltmesi","description":"Ara\xe7 y\xf6netimi ve \xd6ne \xc7\u0131kan Ara\xe7lar y\xfczeyinde \xfc\xe7 d\xfczeltmeyi paketleyen odakl\u0131 bir patch \u2014 Ya\u015fam D\xf6ng\xfcs\xfc meta kutusu art\u0131k bayiyi ad\u0131yla tan\u0131yor, \xd6ne \xc7\u0131kan Ara\xe7lar slider\'\u0131 az ara\xe7l\u0131 listelerde flicker yapmay\u0131 b\u0131rak\u0131yor, ve \xd6ne \xc7\u0131kan Ara\xe7lar Ara\xe7 Izgaras\u0131 ile parite olarak bir \\"T\xfcm\xfcn\xfc G\xf6r\\" linki kazan\u0131yor.","date":"2026-04-29T18:00:00.000Z","tags":[{"inline":true,"label":"release","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/release"},{"inline":true,"label":"rentiva","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/rentiva"},{"inline":true,"label":"ux","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/ux"},{"inline":true,"label":"patch","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/patch"}],"readingTime":2.13,"hasTruncateMarker":true,"authors":[{"name":"MaxHandMade","title":"Maintainer","url":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade","imageURL":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade.png","key":"maxhandmade","page":null}],"frontMatter":{"slug":"rentiva-v4.33.1-release","title":"Rentiva v4.33.1 \u2014 Arama Cilas\u0131 ve Bayi Ad\u0131 D\xfczeltmesi","authors":["maxhandmade"],"tags":["release","rentiva","ux","patch"],"date":"2026-04-29T18:00"},"unlisted":false,"nextItem":{"title":"Rentiva v4.33.0 \u2014 Pro Gate Birle\u015ftirme","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/rentiva-v4.33.0-release"}},"content":"Ara\xe7 y\xf6netimi ve \xd6ne \xc7\u0131kan Ara\xe7lar y\xfczeyinde \xfc\xe7 d\xfczeltmeyi paketleyen odakl\u0131 bir patch \u2014 Ya\u015fam D\xf6ng\xfcs\xfc meta kutusu art\u0131k bayiyi ad\u0131yla tan\u0131yor, \xd6ne \xc7\u0131kan Ara\xe7lar slider\'\u0131 az ara\xe7l\u0131 listelerde flicker yapmay\u0131 b\u0131rak\u0131yor, ve \xd6ne \xc7\u0131kan Ara\xe7lar Ara\xe7 Izgaras\u0131 ile parite olarak bir \\"T\xfcm\xfcn\xfc G\xf6r\\" linki kazan\u0131yor.\\n\\n\x3c!--truncate--\x3e\\n\\n## Bu s\xfcr\xfcm neden var\\n\\n\xdc\xe7 k\xfc\xe7\xfck s\xfcrt\xfcnme birikmi\u015fti:\\n\\n1. Ara\xe7 d\xfczenleme ekran\u0131ndaki Ya\u015fam D\xf6ng\xfcs\xfc meta kutusu bayinin g\xfcvenilirlik puan\u0131n\u0131 g\xf6steriyordu (\xf6r. *Sat\u0131c\u0131 Skoru: 100/100 \u2014 M\xfckemmel*) ama puan\u0131n hangi bayiye ait oldu\u011funu s\xf6ylemiyordu. Admin\'ler bayiyi bulmak i\xe7in kullan\u0131c\u0131 listesine ge\xe7mek zorundayd\u0131.\\n2. \xd6ne \xc7\u0131kan Ara\xe7lar slider\'\u0131 Swiper\'in `loop: true` modunu ko\u015fulsuz kullan\u0131yordu. Az ara\xe7l\u0131 listelerde (slide say\u0131s\u0131 \u2264 columns \xd7 2) Swiper\'in loop algoritmas\u0131 yeterli duplicate slide\'a sahip olmuyor ve slider bo\u015f kareler \xfczerinde d\xf6n\xfcyor.\\n3. Ara\xe7 Izgaras\u0131\'n\u0131n alt\u0131nda bir *T\xfcm\xfcn\xfc G\xf6r* linki vard\u0131 (`view_all_url` / `view_all_text` \xf6zellikleri); \xd6ne \xc7\u0131kan Ara\xe7lar\'da yoktu. Tutarl\u0131 davranmas\u0131 gereken iki shortcode tutars\u0131zd\u0131.\\n\\nBu s\xfcr\xfcm \xfc\xe7\xfcn\xfc de \xe7\xf6z\xfcyor.\\n\\n## De\u011fi\u015fiklikler\\n\\n### D\xfczeltildi: Ya\u015fam D\xf6ng\xfcs\xfc meta kutusu art\u0131k bayiyi ad\u0131yla tan\u0131yor\\n\\n`src/Admin/Vehicle/Meta/LifecycleMetaBox.php` art\u0131k `$post->post_author`\'dan bayiyi \xe7\xf6z\xfcp g\xfcvenilirlik puan\u0131n\u0131n \xfcst\xfcnde bir **Sat\u0131c\u0131:** sat\u0131r\u0131 render ediyor:\\n\\n```\\nDurum: Aktif\\nBa\u015flang\u0131\xe7: 30 Mar 2026\\nBiti\u015f: 28 Haz 2026 (60 g\xfcn)\\n\\n\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\\nSat\u0131c\u0131: Acme Filo Kiralama\\nSat\u0131c\u0131 Skoru: 100/100 \u2014 M\xfckemmel\\n```\\n\\n\xc7\xf6z\xfcmleme zinciri: `$user->display_name` \u2192 `$user->user_login` (display_name bo\u015fsa fallback). S\u0131f\u0131r olmayan `post_author` i\xe7in bayi sat\u0131r\u0131 asla bo\u015f g\xf6r\xfcnmez.\\n\\n### D\xfczeltildi: \xd6ne \xc7\u0131kan Ara\xe7lar slider\'\u0131 az ara\xe7l\u0131 listelerde flicker yapm\u0131yor\\n\\n`assets/js/frontend/featured-vehicles.js` art\u0131k Swiper ba\u015flat\u0131lmadan \xf6nce sayfadaki `.swiper-slide` elementlerini say\u0131yor ve `loop: true`\'yu yaln\u0131zca slide say\u0131s\u0131 `columns \xd7 2`\'den fazlaysa a\xe7\u0131yor:\\n\\n```js\\nconst slideCount = container.find(\'.swiper-slide\').length;\\nconst enableLoop = slideCount > columns * 2;\\n\\nnew Swiper(container[0], {\\n    loop: enableLoop,\\n    // ...\\n});\\n```\\n\\nAz slide = d\xfcz kayd\u0131rma (loop yok, flicker yok). \xc7ok slide = sonsuz loop (orijinal davran\u0131\u015f). Otomatik; kullan\u0131c\u0131 taraf\u0131nda ayar yok.\\n\\n### Eklendi: \xd6ne \xc7\u0131kan Ara\xe7lar i\xe7in `view_all_url` ve `view_all_text`\\n\\nAra\xe7 Izgaras\u0131 ile parite. \xdc\xe7 y\xfczey:\\n\\n**Shortcode:**\\n```\\n[rentiva_featured_vehicles limit=\\"6\\" view_all_url=\\"/araclar/\\" view_all_text=\\"T\xfcm Ara\xe7lar\u0131 G\xf6r\\"]\\n```\\n\\n**Elementor widget:** *Carousel Options* panelinde iki yeni alan (*View All URL* ve *View All Button Text*).\\n\\n**Gutenberg blok:** Inspector Controls\'te iki yeni TextControl (URL girilince ikincisi g\xf6r\xfcn\xfcr).\\n\\n`view_all_url` bo\u015f de\u011filse template footer\'\u0131nda link render ediliyor. Varsay\u0131lan metin \\"T\xfcm Ara\xe7lar\u0131 G\xf6r\xfcnt\xfcle\\" (\xe7evrilebilir).\\n\\n## Testler\\n\\n- 822 \u2192 **824 PHPUnit** (+2: `lifecycle_meta_box_renders_vendor_display_name`, `lifecycle_meta_box_falls_back_to_user_login_when_display_name_is_empty`)\\n- `FeaturedVehiclesDefaultsParityTest` iki yeni mapping ile geni\u015fletildi (`view_all_url`, `view_all_text`)\\n- PHPCS: de\u011fi\u015fen 6 dosyada 0 hata\\n- i18n: 2 yeni string (*Sat\u0131c\u0131:*, *Galerinin alt\u0131na \\"T\xfcm\xfcn\xfc G\xf6r\\" linki ekler...*) T\xfcrk\xe7e \xe7evirileriyle; mevcut *T\xfcm Ara\xe7lar\u0131 G\xf6r\xfcnt\xfcle* / *T\xfcm\xfcn\xfc G\xf6r URL\'si* / *T\xfcm\xfcn\xfc G\xf6r D\xfc\u011fme Metni* \xe7evirileri Ara\xe7 Izgaras\u0131\'ndan `msgmerge` ile reuse edildi (fuzzy=0)\\n\\n## Uyumluluk\\n\\nLisans-sunucu g\xfcncellemesi gerektirmez. v4.33.0 i\xe7in drop-in yedek.\\n\\n## Ba\u011flant\u0131lar\\n\\n- [GitHub Release](https://github.com/MaxHandMade/mhm-rentiva/releases/tag/v4.33.1)"},{"id":"rentiva-v4.33.0-release","metadata":{"permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/rentiva-v4.33.0-release","editUrl":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade/mhm-rentiva-docs/tree/main/blog/2026-04-27-rentiva-v4.33.0-release.md","source":"@site/i18n/tr/docusaurus-plugin-content-blog/2026-04-27-rentiva-v4.33.0-release.md","title":"Rentiva v4.33.0 \u2014 Pro Gate Birle\u015ftirme","description":"v4.33.0, v4.31.0 RSA token migration\'\u0131ndan kalan \xfc\xe7 bo\u015flu\u011fu kapat\u0131yor: token kontrol\xfcn\xfc atlayan 22 callsite, yan\u0131lt\u0131c\u0131 bir License Admin mesaj\u0131, ve lokalde lisans sunucusu \xe7al\u0131\u015ft\u0131rmadan Pro \xf6zelliklerini test edememe.","date":"2026-04-27T18:00:00.000Z","tags":[{"inline":true,"label":"release","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/release"},{"inline":true,"label":"rentiva","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/rentiva"},{"inline":true,"label":"license","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/license"},{"inline":true,"label":"security","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/security"}],"readingTime":4.32,"hasTruncateMarker":true,"authors":[{"name":"MaxHandMade","title":"Maintainer","url":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade","imageURL":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade.png","key":"maxhandmade","page":null}],"frontMatter":{"slug":"rentiva-v4.33.0-release","title":"Rentiva v4.33.0 \u2014 Pro Gate Birle\u015ftirme","authors":["maxhandmade"],"tags":["release","rentiva","license","security"],"date":"2026-04-27T18:00"},"unlisted":false,"prevItem":{"title":"Rentiva v4.33.1 \u2014 Arama Cilas\u0131 ve Bayi Ad\u0131 D\xfczeltmesi","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/rentiva-v4.33.1-release"},"nextItem":{"title":"Currency Switcher v0.7.0 \u2014 Aboneli\u011finizi eklenti i\xe7inden y\xf6netin","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/cs-v0.7.0-release"}},"content":"v4.33.0, v4.31.0 RSA token migration\'\u0131ndan kalan \xfc\xe7 bo\u015flu\u011fu kapat\u0131yor: token kontrol\xfcn\xfc atlayan 22 callsite, yan\u0131lt\u0131c\u0131 bir License Admin mesaj\u0131, ve lokalde lisans sunucusu \xe7al\u0131\u015ft\u0131rmadan Pro \xf6zelliklerini test edememe.\\n\\n\x3c!--truncate--\x3e\\n\\n## Bu s\xfcr\xfcm neden var\\n\\nv4.31.0, RSA-imzal\u0131 feature token\'lar\u0131n\u0131 `Mode::featureGranted()` arac\u0131l\u0131\u011f\u0131yla tek Pro otorite olarak getirdi. Her Pro feature gate\'inin bu metodu (veya delege eden `canUse*()` wrapper\'lar\u0131ndan birini) \xe7a\u011f\u0131rmas\u0131 gerekiyordu. Ama codebase\'de 22 yer h\xe2l\xe2 eski `Mode::featureEnabled()` API\'sini \xe7a\u011f\u0131r\u0131yordu \u2014 bu yaln\u0131zca `isPro()` kontrol ediyordu, token do\u011frulamas\u0131 yok. Cracked bir binary\'nin `LicenseManager::isActive()` metodunu `true` d\xf6nd\xfcrecek \u015fekilde patch\'lemesi, ge\xe7erli bir token olmadan o callsite\'larda mesajlar\u0131, geli\u015fmi\u015f raporlar\u0131 ve export\'u a\xe7abiliyordu.\\n\\nBu s\xfcr\xfcm her callsite\'\u0131 migrate ediyor, eski API\'yi soft-deprecate ediyor, ve birikmi\u015f iki UX d\xfczeltmesi ekliyor.\\n\\n## De\u011fi\u015fiklikler\\n\\n### \ud83d\udd12 G\xfcvenlik: 22 callsite art\u0131k token do\u011fruluyor\\n\\n| Dosya | Callsite |\\n|---|---|\\n| `Frontend/Account/AccountRenderer.php` | 1 |\\n| `Frontend/Account/WooCommerceIntegration.php` | 2 |\\n| `Messages/Core/Messages.php` | 1 |\\n| `Messages/Frontend/CustomerMessages.php` | 1 |\\n| `Messages/REST/*.php` (3 dosya) | 3 |\\n| `Reports/Reports.php` | 2 |\\n| `Utilities/Export/Export.php` | 3 |\\n| `Utilities/Export/ExportReports.php` | 6 |\\n| `Utilities/Menu/Menu.php` | 3 |\\n\\nT\xfcm\xfc uygun `Mode::canUse*()` metoduna migrate edildi. `Mode::featureEnabled()` art\u0131k `WP_DEBUG`\'da `_deprecated_function()` notice\'\u0131 yayan soft-deprecated bir wrapper. Body \xfc\xe7\xfcnc\xfc taraf \xe7a\u011fr\u0131c\u0131lar i\xe7in korundu; tam kald\u0131rma v5.0 i\xe7in planland\u0131.\\n\\n### \ud83d\udd27 License Admin: sabit metin yerine ger\xe7ek durum\\n\\nLisans sayfas\u0131 bir lisans aktif oldu\u011funda her seferinde **\\"All Pro features active: Unlimited vehicles/bookings, export, advanced reports, Vendor & Payout.\\"** yaz\u0131yordu \u2014 sunucunun asl\u0131nda hangi feature token\'lar\u0131n\u0131 verdi\u011fine bakmaks\u0131z\u0131n. Bo\u015f veya k\u0131smi token\'\u0131 olan m\xfc\u015fteriler bu sat\u0131r\u0131 okuyup Vendor men\xfcs\xfcn\xfcn neden eksik oldu\u011funu merak ediyordu.\\n\\nYeni render ger\xe7ek gate kararlar\u0131ndan t\xfcreyen liste:\\n\\n> Aktif Pro \xf6zellikleri: Vendor & Payout, Geli\u015fmi\u015f Raporlar, Mesajlar, Geni\u015fletilmi\u015f Export\\n\\nHi\xe7 gate aktif de\u011filse (lisans aktif ama token bo\u015f \u2014 normal \u015fartlarda olmamas\u0131 gereken ama v4.30.x \u2192 v4.31.0 ge\xe7i\u015finde olan durum), sayfa art\u0131k yan\u0131lt\u0131c\u0131 metin yerine \\"Re-validate Now\\" CTA\'l\u0131 bir uyar\u0131 bildirimi g\xf6steriyor.\\n\\n### \u2728 Lokal Pro testi i\xe7in Geli\u015ftirici Modu\\n\\nv4.31.0\'dan beri lokalde Pro feature eklemek zahmetliydi: RSA-imzal\u0131 feature token\'\u0131 lisans sunucusu taraf\u0131ndan veriliyor, geli\u015ftiriciler bunu makinelerinde \xe7al\u0131\u015ft\u0131rm\u0131yor olabilir. Sonu\xe7 fail-closed gate\'di \u2014 lokal Pro feature\'lar production\'dan token kopyalamadan test edilemezdi (kopyalanmamal\u0131).\\n\\n\u0130ki yeni constant bypass\'\u0131 etkinle\u015ftiriyor:\\n\\n```php\\n// wp-config.php (yaln\u0131zca geli\u015ftirme)\\ndefine( \'WP_DEBUG\', true );\\ndefine( \'MHM_RENTIVA_DEV_PRO\', true );\\n```\\n\\n**\u0130kisi de** true oldu\u011funda `Mode::featureGranted()` token do\u011frulama ad\u0131m\u0131n\u0131 atlar ve `true` d\xf6ner. `isPro()` kontrol\xfc h\xe2l\xe2 \xf6nce \xe7al\u0131\u015f\u0131r, dolay\u0131s\u0131yla bir Lite lisans\u0131 Pro\'ya bypass edemez \u2014 yine aktif bir lisansa ihtiyac\u0131n var, sadece ge\xe7erli token\'a de\u011fil.\\n\\nProduction g\xfcvenli\u011fi: Hostinger production ortamlar\u0131nda `WP_DEBUG=false` default\'tur, dolay\u0131s\u0131yla `MHM_RENTIVA_DEV_PRO` bir production `wp-config.php`\'sine s\u0131zm\u0131\u015f olsa bile (s\u0131zmamal\u0131), bypass devreye girmez.\\n\\nSar\u0131 \\"Geli\u015ftirici Modu\\" banner alt ba\u015fl\u0131\u011f\u0131 art\u0131k bypass\'\u0131n ger\xe7ekten aktif mi yoksa sadece pasif mi oldu\u011funu yans\u0131t\u0131yor.\\n\\nYeni bir `mhm_rentiva_dev_pro_bypass` filter\'\u0131 bypass karar\u0131n\u0131 test edilebilirlik i\xe7in a\xe7\u0131\u011fa \xe7\u0131kar\u0131yor \u2014 PHPUnit tek bir process i\xe7inde PHP define\'lar\u0131n\u0131 toggle edemez.\\n\\n### \u26a0\ufe0f KIRICI: Lite kullan\u0131c\u0131lar xlsx/pdf export eri\u015fimini kaybediyor\\n\\nEski `featureEnabled(FEATURE_EXPORT)` Lite kullan\u0131c\u0131lar i\xe7in ko\u015fulsuz `true` d\xf6n\xfcyordu. Bu bir bug\'d\u0131 \u2014 \xe7a\u011f\u0131ranlardaki format kontrol\xfc (`! in_array($format, [\'csv\', \'json\'])`) ikinci gate olmas\u0131 gerekiyordu, ama `featureEnabled` k\u0131sa devre yap\u0131yordu. Yani Lite kullan\u0131c\u0131lar xlsx ve pdf export isteyebiliyordu.\\n\\n`canUseExport()` Lite i\xe7in do\u011fru \u015fekilde `false` d\xf6n\xfcyor. CSV ve JSON h\xe2l\xe2 \xfccretsiz; xlsx ve pdf art\u0131k niyetlendi\u011fi gibi yaln\u0131zca Pro.\\n\\nEtkilenen Lite kullan\u0131c\u0131lar i\xe7in g\xf6\xe7 yolu: tam format eri\u015fimi i\xe7in Pro\'ya y\xfckselt, ya da CSV/JSON ile devam et.\\n\\n### \ud83c\udf10 \xc7eviri kalitesi (collateral)\\n\\nv4.33.0 i18n turu, t\xfcm TR katalo\u011fu \xfczerinde bir `msgmerge` tetikledi. Daha \xf6nceki s\xfcr\xfcmlerde otomatik fuzzy olarak i\u015faretlenen ve hi\xe7 g\xf6zden ge\xe7irilmeyen mevcut \xe7eviriler vard\u0131. Bu turda 22 tanesini d\xfczelttik:\\n\\n- **\\"Airport Transfer\\"** yanl\u0131\u015fl\u0131kla **\\"Aktar\u0131m\u0131 \u0130zin Ver\\"** (kelimesi kelimesine \\"Allow Transfer\\") olarak \xe7evrilmi\u015fti. \u015eimdi do\u011fru \u015fekilde **\\"Havaliman\u0131 Transferi\\"**.\\n- **\\"Report Issue\\"** **\\"Raporlar\\"** (Reports) idi. \u015eimdi **\\"Sorun Bildir\\"**.\\n- Birden \xe7ok plural form `%d/%d`\'den positional `%1$d/%2$d`\'ye ge\xe7ti (kaynak arg\xfcman s\u0131ras\u0131 ile e\u015fle\u015fir).\\n- Daha \xf6nceki turlarda d\xfc\u015f\xfcr\xfclen birka\xe7 email etiketi iki noktas\u0131 restore edildi.\\n\\n`msgmerge` fuzzy say\u0131s\u0131 post-merge: 0 \u2014 otomasyon taraf\u0131ndan do\u011fruland\u0131.\\n\\n## Uyumluluk\\n\\n| Bile\u015fen | Gerekli s\xfcr\xfcm |\\n|---|---|\\n| `mhm-license-server` | **v1.11.2** (verilen feature-token allowlist\'ine `\'export\'` ekler) |\\n| `mhm-polar-bridge` | v1.9.0+ |\\n| WordPress | 6.7+ |\\n| PHP | 8.1+ |\\n\\nE\u011fer v4.33.0 mhm-license-server v1.11.2\'den \xf6nce yay\u0131nlan\u0131rsa, **Pro kullan\u0131c\u0131lar 24 saate kadar xlsx/pdf export eri\u015fimini kaybeder** \u2014 yeni `canUseExport()` gate\'i sunucunun hen\xfcz vermedi\u011fi bir `\'export\'` token claim\'i ar\u0131yor. Sunucunun g\xfcnl\xfck cron\'u token\'lar\u0131 yeniden veriyor; License sayfas\u0131nda \\"Re-validate Now\\"a manuel t\u0131klamak hemen yeniliyor.\\n\\n\u0130\u015fte bu y\xfczden release zinciri s\u0131ras\u0131 \xf6nce server v1.11.2, sonra plugin v4.33.0.\\n\\n## Testler\\n\\n- 807 \u2192 822 PHPUnit (+15)\\n  - 5 `ModeDevBypassTest`\'te\\n  - 4 `LicenseAdminActiveFeaturesTest`\'te\\n  - 6 `ModeGateMigrationTest`\'te\\n- PHPCS: 0 hata, 0 uyar\u0131 (release scope)\\n- Plugin Check (WordPress.org uyumlulu\u011fu): 0 HATA, 27 UYARI (hepsi \xf6nceden var olan, hepsi Plugin Check\'in `phpcs.xml` prefix konfig\xfcrasyonunu okumamas\u0131ndan gelen bilinen yanl\u0131\u015f-pozitifler)\\n\\n## Y\xfckseltme notlar\u0131\\n\\n1. mhm-license-server v1.11.2\'nin canl\u0131ya \xe7\u0131kmas\u0131n\u0131 bekle (yoksa Pro export ~24h k\u0131r\u0131l\u0131r).\\n2. Plugin\'i WP Admin \u2192 Eklentiler \u2192 Y\xfckle ile veya FTP \xfczerinden ZIP\'i de\u011fi\u015ftirerek g\xfcncelle.\\n3. G\xfcncelleme sonras\u0131 License sayfas\u0131nda bir kez \\"Re-validate Now\\"a t\u0131kla. Bu, istemcinin sunucudan taze token almas\u0131n\u0131 zorlar \u2014 onsuz bir sonraki yenileme penceresi g\xfcnl\xfck cron.\\n4. (Bug-enabled) xlsx export\'lar\u0131na g\xfcvenen Lite kullan\u0131c\u0131lar: Pro\'ya y\xfckselt ya da CSV/JSON\'a ge\xe7.\\n\\n## Lokal geli\u015ftirme\\n\\nE\u011fer bir fork s\xfcrd\xfcr\xfcyor ya da plugin\'i geni\u015fletiyorsan:\\n\\n```php\\n// wp-config.php\\ndefine( \'WP_DEBUG\', true );\\ndefine( \'MHM_RENTIVA_DEV_PRO\', true );  // token kontrol\xfcn\xfc atla, Pro gate\'leri \xe7al\u0131\u015ft\u0131r\\n```\\n\\nBu, ger\xe7ek bir RSA-imzal\u0131 token olmadan aktif lisansa kar\u015f\u0131 Vendor Marketplace, Geli\u015fmi\u015f Raporlar, Mesajlar ve Geni\u015fletilmi\u015f Export\'u a\xe7ar. Production\'a g\xf6nderme."},{"id":"cs-v0.7.0-release","metadata":{"permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/cs-v0.7.0-release","editUrl":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade/mhm-rentiva-docs/tree/main/blog/2026-04-27-cs-v0.7.0-release.md","source":"@site/i18n/tr/docusaurus-plugin-content-blog/2026-04-27-cs-v0.7.0-release.md","title":"Currency Switcher v0.7.0 \u2014 Aboneli\u011finizi eklenti i\xe7inden y\xf6netin","description":"Lisans sekmesinde art\u0131k yeni sekmede Polar m\xfc\u015fteri portal\u0131n\u0131 a\xe7an bir Aboneli\u011fi Y\xf6net butonu var. Otomatik yenilemeyi iptal et, kart bilgini g\xfcncelle, plan de\u011fi\u015ftir veya yeniden abone ol \u2014 WordPress y\xf6neticisinden \xe7\u0131kmadan. MHM Rentiva v4.32.0\'\u0131n snake_case + REST/React paritesi.","date":"2026-04-27T08:30:00.000Z","tags":[{"inline":true,"label":"release","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/release"},{"inline":true,"label":"currency-switcher","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/currency-switcher"},{"inline":true,"label":"license","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/license"}],"readingTime":2.03,"hasTruncateMarker":true,"authors":[{"name":"MaxHandMade","title":"Maintainer","url":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade","imageURL":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade.png","key":"maxhandmade","page":null}],"frontMatter":{"slug":"cs-v0.7.0-release","title":"Currency Switcher v0.7.0 \u2014 Aboneli\u011finizi eklenti i\xe7inden y\xf6netin","authors":["maxhandmade"],"tags":["release","currency-switcher","license"],"date":"2026-04-27T08:30"},"unlisted":false,"prevItem":{"title":"Rentiva v4.33.0 \u2014 Pro Gate Birle\u015ftirme","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/rentiva-v4.33.0-release"},"nextItem":{"title":"Rentiva v4.32.0 \u2014 Aboneli\u011finizi eklenti i\xe7inden y\xf6netin","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/rentiva-v4.32.0-release"}},"content":"Lisans sekmesinde art\u0131k yeni sekmede **Polar m\xfc\u015fteri portal\u0131n\u0131** a\xe7an bir **Aboneli\u011fi Y\xf6net** butonu var. Otomatik yenilemeyi iptal et, kart bilgini g\xfcncelle, plan de\u011fi\u015ftir veya yeniden abone ol \u2014 WordPress y\xf6neticisinden \xe7\u0131kmadan. **MHM Rentiva v4.32.0**\'\u0131n snake_case + REST/React paritesi.\\n\\n\x3c!--truncate--\x3e\\n\\n## Ne de\u011fi\u015fti\\n\\nLisans sekmesinde **License Management** b\xf6lgesinde (Pro lisans aktifken g\xf6r\xfcn\xfcr), mevcut iki butona \xfc\xe7\xfcnc\xfc ekleniyor:\\n\\n1. **Aboneli\u011fi Y\xf6net** \u2014 Polar m\xfc\u015fteri portal\u0131n\u0131 a\xe7ar (bu s\xfcr\xfcm)\\n2. Re-validate Now\\n3. Deactivate License\\n\\nYeni buton, Polar\'a halihaz\u0131rda kulland\u0131\u011f\u0131m\u0131z ayn\u0131 lisans sunucusu \xfczerinden eri\u015fir. Sitenizden bak\u0131ld\u0131\u011f\u0131nda yeni bir d\u0131\u015f servisle ileti\u015fim yok. \u015eema ve imza b\xfct\xfcnl\xfc\u011f\xfc RSA ile korunmaya devam ediyor (v0.6.0+ pipeline).\\n\\n## Duruma g\xf6re vurgu\\n\\nButon, yenilemeye olan uzakl\u0131\u011fa g\xf6re renk de\u011fi\u015ftiriyor:\\n\\n| Kalan g\xfcn | Renk | Niyet |\\n|---|---|---|\\n| > 30 | Standart birincil mavi | \\"Bolca s\xfcre var\\" |\\n| \u2264 30 | Sar\u0131 | \\"Dikkat \u2014 yenileme yakla\u015f\u0131yor\\" |\\n| \u2264 7 | Kehribar + parlama | \\"\u015eimdi karar ver\\" |\\n| S\xfcresi dolmu\u015f (0) | Kehribar + parlama | \\"Pro\'yu s\xfcrd\xfcrmek i\xe7in yeniden abone ol\\" |\\n\\nPortal oturumu \xfcretilirken (k\u0131sa bir async \xe7a\u011fr\u0131), buton metni \\"A\xe7\u0131l\u0131yor\u2026\\" olur ve stil hafif\xe7e solukla\u015f\u0131r \u2014 t\u0131klaman\u0131n kaydoldu\u011funu g\xf6rsel olarak iletir.\\n\\n## Hata durumu y\xf6netimi\\n\\nPortal oturumu \xfcretilemezse (sunucu hatas\u0131, a\u011f kesintisi, sayfa a\xe7\u0131ld\u0131ktan sonra lisans\u0131n iptal edilmesi), buton k\u0131r\u0131lmak yerine sekme i\xe7i bir bildirim g\xf6sterir:\\n\\n> Abonelik y\xf6netimi \u015fu an m\xfcmk\xfcn de\u011fil. L\xfctfen daha sonra tekrar deneyin veya support@wpalemi.com ile ileti\u015fime ge\xe7in.\\n\\nHam teknik string son kullan\u0131c\u0131ya asla s\u0131zmaz.\\n\\n## Mimari\\n\\n- Yeni public method `LicenseManager::create_customer_portal_session(string $return_url): array` (Rentiva\'n\u0131n camelCase\'ine snake_case paritesi)\\n- Yeni REST endpoint `POST /mhm-currency/v1/license/manage-subscription` (manage_options yetkili)\\n- `License.jsx` i\xe7inde yeni React state + callback, `isActive && license.maskedKey` ko\u015fulunda Deactivate\'in solunda render\\n- Yeni CSS kurallar\u0131 compound selector kullan\u0131r (`.button.mhm-cs-license-warning` / `.mhm-cs-license-urgent`) \u2014 mevcut `.mhm-cs-license-warning` uyar\u0131 pilini bozmamak i\xe7in\\n- 4 yeni \xe7evirilebilir string, hepsi T\xfcrk\xe7eye \xe7evrildi\\n\\n## Uyumluluk\\n\\n| Bile\u015fen | Gerekli s\xfcr\xfcm |\\n|---|---|\\n| `mhm-license-server` | v1.11.0+ (yeni `/customer-portal-session` endpoint\'i) |\\n| `mhm-polar-bridge` | v1.9.0+ (yenileme hat\u0131rlatma cron\'u) |\\n| WordPress | 6.0+ |\\n| PHP | 7.4+ |\\n\\n`/customer-portal-session` endpoint\'ine sahip olmayan eski lisans sunucu s\xfcr\xfcmleri, k\u0131r\u0131lmak yerine zarif bir sekme i\xe7i bildirim d\xf6ner.\\n\\n## Bu s\xfcr\xfcmde yok (kapsam d\u0131\u015f\u0131)\\n\\n- **Past-due / dunning bildirimleri** \u2014 Polar bunlar\u0131 do\u011frudan e-postayla y\xf6netiyor.\\n- **Y\u0131ll\u0131k abonelik yenileme hat\u0131rlatmalar\u0131** \u2014 Polar bunlar\u0131 otomatik olarak yenilemeden 7 g\xfcn \xf6nce g\xf6nderiyor.\\n\\nAyl\u0131k abonelere `mhm-polar-bridge v1.9.0+` \xfczerinden 7 g\xfcn \xf6nceden ek bir hat\u0131rlatma e-postas\u0131 gidiyor; \xe7\xfcnk\xfc Polar k\u0131sa fatura d\xf6ng\xfcleri i\xe7in bunu \xfcretmiyor.\\n\\n## Testler\\n\\n- 148 \u2192 158 PHPUnit (+10 yeni, 2 test dosyas\u0131nda)\\n- PHPCS yeni dosyalar: 0 hata (PHPCBF sonras\u0131)\\n- PHPStan level 6: 0 hata\\n- npm run build: ba\u015far\u0131l\u0131\\n- i18n: yeni string\'lerde 0 fuzzy, 4 string tamamen \xe7evrildi"},{"id":"rentiva-v4.32.0-release","metadata":{"permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/rentiva-v4.32.0-release","editUrl":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade/mhm-rentiva-docs/tree/main/blog/2026-04-27-rentiva-v4.32.0-release.md","source":"@site/i18n/tr/docusaurus-plugin-content-blog/2026-04-27-rentiva-v4.32.0-release.md","title":"Rentiva v4.32.0 \u2014 Aboneli\u011finizi eklenti i\xe7inden y\xf6netin","description":"Lisans sayfas\u0131nda art\u0131k yeni sekmede Polar m\xfc\u015fteri portal\u0131n\u0131 a\xe7an bir Aboneli\u011fi Y\xf6net butonu var. Otomatik yenilemeyi iptal et, kart bilgini g\xfcncelle, plan de\u011fi\u015ftir veya yeniden abone ol \u2014 WordPress y\xf6neticisinden \xe7\u0131kmadan.","date":"2026-04-27T08:00:00.000Z","tags":[{"inline":true,"label":"release","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/release"},{"inline":true,"label":"rentiva","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/rentiva"},{"inline":true,"label":"license","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/license"}],"readingTime":1.85,"hasTruncateMarker":true,"authors":[{"name":"MaxHandMade","title":"Maintainer","url":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade","imageURL":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade.png","key":"maxhandmade","page":null}],"frontMatter":{"slug":"rentiva-v4.32.0-release","title":"Rentiva v4.32.0 \u2014 Aboneli\u011finizi eklenti i\xe7inden y\xf6netin","authors":["maxhandmade"],"tags":["release","rentiva","license"],"date":"2026-04-27T08:00"},"unlisted":false,"prevItem":{"title":"Currency Switcher v0.7.0 \u2014 Aboneli\u011finizi eklenti i\xe7inden y\xf6netin","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/cs-v0.7.0-release"},"nextItem":{"title":"Lisans G\xfcvenlik Sertle\u015ftirme Sprint\'i: Rentiva v4.30.0 \u2192 v4.30.2 (mhm-license-server v1.9.0\u2013v1.9.3 ve CS v0.5.x ile)","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/license-security-sprint-v4.30.x"}},"content":"Lisans sayfas\u0131nda art\u0131k yeni sekmede **Polar m\xfc\u015fteri portal\u0131n\u0131** a\xe7an bir **Aboneli\u011fi Y\xf6net** butonu var. Otomatik yenilemeyi iptal et, kart bilgini g\xfcncelle, plan de\u011fi\u015ftir veya yeniden abone ol \u2014 WordPress y\xf6neticisinden \xe7\u0131kmadan.\\n\\n\x3c!--truncate--\x3e\\n\\n## Ne de\u011fi\u015fti\\n\\nLicense Management b\xf6l\xfcm\xfcnde (lisans aktifken g\xf6r\xfcn\xfcr) art\u0131k \xfc\xe7 buton bulunuyor:\\n\\n1. **Aboneli\u011fi Y\xf6net** \u2014 Polar m\xfc\u015fteri portal\u0131n\u0131 a\xe7ar (bu s\xfcr\xfcm)\\n2. Re-validate Now (v4.31.2)\\n3. Deactivate License\\n\\nYeni buton, Polar\'a halihaz\u0131rda kulland\u0131\u011f\u0131m\u0131z ayn\u0131 lisans sunucusu \xfczerinden eri\u015fir. Sitenizden bak\u0131ld\u0131\u011f\u0131nda yeni bir d\u0131\u015f servisle ileti\u015fim yok. \u015eema ve imza b\xfct\xfcnl\xfc\u011f\xfc RSA ile korunmaya devam ediyor (v4.30.0+ pipeline).\\n\\n## Duruma g\xf6re vurgu\\n\\nButon, yenilemeye olan uzakl\u0131\u011fa g\xf6re renk de\u011fi\u015ftiriyor:\\n\\n| Kalan g\xfcn | Renk | Niyet |\\n|---|---|---|\\n| > 30 | Standart birincil mavi | \\"Bolca s\xfcre var\\" |\\n| \u2264 30 | Sar\u0131 | \\"Dikkat \u2014 yenileme yakla\u015f\u0131yor\\" |\\n| \u2264 7 | Kehribar + parlama | \\"\u015eimdi karar ver\\" |\\n| S\xfcresi dolmu\u015f (0) | Kehribar + parlama | \\"Pro\'yu s\xfcrd\xfcrmek i\xe7in yeniden abone ol\\" |\\n\\nM\xfc\u015fteri, e-posta hat\u0131rlatmalar\u0131n\u0131 okumasa bile yenilemenin ne kadar yak\u0131n oldu\u011funu tek bak\u0131\u015fta g\xf6r\xfcr.\\n\\n## Hata durumu y\xf6netimi\\n\\nPortal oturumu \xfcretilemezse (sunucu hatas\u0131, a\u011f kesintisi, sayfa a\xe7\u0131ld\u0131ktan sonra lisans\u0131n iptal edilmesi), y\xf6netici License sayfas\u0131na geri d\xf6ner ve m\xfc\u015fteri-dostu, \xe7evirili bir uyar\u0131 g\xf6r\xfcr:\\n\\n> \u2139\ufe0f Abonelik y\xf6netimi \u015fu an m\xfcmk\xfcn de\u011fil (servis kullan\u0131lam\u0131yor). L\xfctfen daha sonra tekrar deneyin veya support@wpalemi.com ile ileti\u015fime ge\xe7in.\\n\\nBe\u015f hata kodu k\u0131sa T\xfcrk\xe7e etiketlere maplan\u0131r (`get_manage_unavailable_label()`). Ham teknik string son kullan\u0131c\u0131ya asla s\u0131zmaz.\\n\\n## Mimari\\n\\n- Yeni public method `LicenseManager::createCustomerPortalSession(string $return_url): array`\\n- Yeni admin-post handler `LicenseAdmin::handle_manage_subscription()` \u2014 yetki + nonce kap\u0131l\u0131\\n- `assets/css/admin/license-admin.css` dosyas\u0131na yeni CSS kurallar\u0131, `filemtime` ile cache-bust\\n- 9 yeni \xe7evirilebilir string, hepsi T\xfcrk\xe7eye \xe7evrildi\\n\\n## Uyumluluk\\n\\n| Bile\u015fen | Gerekli s\xfcr\xfcm |\\n|---|---|\\n| `mhm-license-server` | v1.11.0+ (yeni `/customer-portal-session` endpoint\'i) |\\n| `mhm-polar-bridge` | v1.9.0+ (yenileme hat\u0131rlatma cron\'u) |\\n| WordPress | 6.7+ |\\n| PHP | 8.1+ |\\n\\n`/customer-portal-session` endpoint\'ine sahip olmayan eski lisans sunucu s\xfcr\xfcmleri, k\u0131r\u0131lmak yerine zarif bir `manage_unavailable` bildirimi d\xf6ner \u2014 m\xfc\u015fteri bozuk redirect de\u011fil, \xe7evirili bir uyar\u0131 g\xf6r\xfcr.\\n\\n## Bu s\xfcr\xfcmde yok (kapsam d\u0131\u015f\u0131)\\n\\n- **Past-due / dunning bildirimleri** \u2014 Polar bunlar\u0131 do\u011frudan e-postayla y\xf6netiyor.\\n- **Y\u0131ll\u0131k abonelik yenileme hat\u0131rlatmalar\u0131** \u2014 Polar bunlar\u0131 otomatik olarak yenilemeden 7 g\xfcn \xf6nce g\xf6nderiyor.\\n\\nAyl\u0131k abonelere `mhm-polar-bridge v1.9.0+` \xfczerinden 7 g\xfcn \xf6nceden ek bir hat\u0131rlatma e-postas\u0131 gidiyor; \xe7\xfcnk\xfc Polar k\u0131sa fatura d\xf6ng\xfcleri i\xe7in bunu \xfcretmiyor.\\n\\n## Testler\\n\\n- 793 \u2192 807 PHPUnit (+14 yeni, 3 test dosyas\u0131nda)\\n- PHPCS: 0 hata\\n- i18n: yeni string\'lerde 0 fuzzy, 9 string tamamen \xe7evrildi"},{"id":"license-security-sprint-v4.30.x","metadata":{"permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/license-security-sprint-v4.30.x","editUrl":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade/mhm-rentiva-docs/tree/main/blog/2026-04-25-license-security-sprint.md","source":"@site/i18n/tr/docusaurus-plugin-content-blog/2026-04-25-license-security-sprint.md","title":"Lisans G\xfcvenlik Sertle\u015ftirme Sprint\'i: Rentiva v4.30.0 \u2192 v4.30.2 (mhm-license-server v1.9.0\u2013v1.9.3 ve CS v0.5.x ile)","description":"Rentiva (ve Currency Switcher) Pro lisans katman\u0131n\u0131 kaynak-d\xfczenleme bypass sald\u0131r\u0131lar\u0131na kar\u015f\u0131 sertle\u015ftiren iki g\xfcnl\xfck \xe7apraz-eklenti sprint\'i. \xdc\xe7 Rentiva istemci s\xfcr\xfcm\xfc (v4.30.0 / v4.30.1 / v4.30.2), d\xf6rt lisans-sunucu s\xfcr\xfcm\xfc (v1.9.0 \u2192 v1.9.3) ve \xfc\xe7 Currency Switcher s\xfcr\xfcm\xfc (v0.5.0 / v0.5.1 / v0.5.2) ile birlikte yay\u0131mland\u0131. Canl\u0131da mhmrentiva.com + wpalemi.com \xfczerinde u\xe7tan-uca do\u011fruland\u0131.","date":"2026-04-25T22:00:00.000Z","tags":[{"inline":true,"label":"release","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/release"},{"inline":true,"label":"security","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/security"},{"inline":true,"label":"license","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/license"},{"inline":true,"label":"hardening","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/hardening"},{"inline":true,"label":"mhm-rentiva","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/mhm-rentiva"},{"inline":true,"label":"mhm-license-server","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/mhm-license-server"},{"inline":true,"label":"mhm-currency-switcher","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/mhm-currency-switcher"}],"readingTime":7.1,"hasTruncateMarker":true,"authors":[{"name":"MaxHandMade","title":"Maintainer","url":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade","imageURL":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade.png","key":"maxhandmade","page":null}],"frontMatter":{"slug":"license-security-sprint-v4.30.x","title":"Lisans G\xfcvenlik Sertle\u015ftirme Sprint\'i: Rentiva v4.30.0 \u2192 v4.30.2 (mhm-license-server v1.9.0\u2013v1.9.3 ve CS v0.5.x ile)","authors":["maxhandmade"],"tags":["release","security","license","hardening","mhm-rentiva","mhm-license-server","mhm-currency-switcher"],"date":"2026-04-25T22:00"},"unlisted":false,"prevItem":{"title":"Rentiva v4.32.0 \u2014 Aboneli\u011finizi eklenti i\xe7inden y\xf6netin","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/rentiva-v4.32.0-release"},"nextItem":{"title":"MHM Rentiva v4.27.4\u2013v4.27.6: Migration \u015eerit Mimarisi, Lisans Slug \u0130letimi, WordPress.org Cilas\u0131","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/v4.27.4-v4.27.6-stability-sprint"}},"content":"Rentiva (ve Currency Switcher) Pro lisans katman\u0131n\u0131 kaynak-d\xfczenleme bypass sald\u0131r\u0131lar\u0131na kar\u015f\u0131 sertle\u015ftiren iki g\xfcnl\xfck \xe7apraz-eklenti sprint\'i. **\xdc\xe7 Rentiva istemci s\xfcr\xfcm\xfc** (v4.30.0 / v4.30.1 / v4.30.2), **d\xf6rt lisans-sunucu s\xfcr\xfcm\xfc** (v1.9.0 \u2192 v1.9.3) ve **\xfc\xe7 Currency Switcher s\xfcr\xfcm\xfc** (v0.5.0 / v0.5.1 / v0.5.2) ile birlikte yay\u0131mland\u0131. Canl\u0131da mhmrentiva.com + wpalemi.com \xfczerinde u\xe7tan-uca do\u011fruland\u0131.\\n\\n\x3c!--truncate--\x3e\\n\\n## Bu sprint neden ger\xe7ekle\u015fti\\n\\nRentiva eklentisi kaynak kodu **public GitHub repository\'sinde** yay\u0131nlan\u0131yor. Motive bir sald\u0131rgan kodu klonlay\u0131p `Mode::canUseVendorMarketplace()`\'i `return true;` olarak yamalayabilir ve lisans sunucusunu hi\xe7 \xe7a\u011f\u0131rmadan Pro \xf6zellikleri a\xe7abilir. v1.8.0 *\xe7apraz \xfcr\xfcn* anahtar yeniden kullan\u0131m\u0131n\u0131 (Currency Switcher anahtar\u0131 Rentiva\'da) kapatt\u0131, ancak kaynak-d\xfczenleme bypass\'a kar\u015f\u0131 hi\xe7bir \u015fey yapmad\u0131. **v4.30.x maliyeti y\xfckseltir: bir crack art\u0131k HMAC imzas\u0131 taklit etmek, sahte bir do\u011frulay\u0131c\u0131 bar\u0131nd\u0131rmak VE s\xfcrekli yeni feature token\'lar yaymak zorunda \u2014 ve yine de token\'lar 24 saat i\xe7inde sona erer.**\\n\\nTasar\u0131m hedefi olarak be\u015f sald\u0131r\u0131 senaryosu kullan\u0131ld\u0131:\\n\\n| Sald\u0131r\u0131 | Mekanizma | Taraf\u0131ndan savunulur |\\n|---|---|---|\\n| Kaynak-d\xfczenleme `isActive() { return true; }` | Yerel Pro kap\u0131s\u0131n\u0131 yama | Katman 4 (feature token) |\\n| \xc7apraz \xfcr\xfcn anahtar yeniden kullan\u0131m\u0131 | CS anahtar\u0131n\u0131 Rentiva\'da kullan | Katman 1 (slug ba\u011flama, v1.8.0) |\\n| Bo\u015f `product_slug` g\xf6vde | Sat\u0131r\u0131 sil, eski uyumlulu\u011fa bin | v1.9.3\'te sertle\u015ftirilmi\u015f Katman 1 |\\n| Sahte activate POST (script\'ten) | \u0130ddia edilen site \xfczerinde kontrol yok | Katman 3 (ters site do\u011frulamas\u0131) |\\n| Korsan anahtar + sahte sunucu | DNS hijack ile benzer | Katman 2 (yan\u0131t imzalama) |\\n\\n## v4.30.0 \u2014 Faz B \u0130stemci (temel, 2026-04-24)\\n\\n**mhm-license-server v1.9.0** (Faz A \u2014 sunucu taraf\u0131 \xfc\xe7 katmanl\u0131 savunma) ile uyumlu.\\n\\n### `src/Admin/Licensing/` alt\u0131nda d\xf6rt yeni yard\u0131mc\u0131\\n\\n- **`ClientSecrets`** \u2014 \xfc\xe7 yeni wp-config sabitini \xe7\xf6zer (`MHM_RENTIVA_LICENSE_RESPONSE_HMAC_SECRET`, `MHM_RENTIVA_LICENSE_FEATURE_TOKEN_KEY`, `MHM_RENTIVA_LICENSE_PING_SECRET`).\\n- **`ResponseVerifier`** \u2014 her imzal\u0131 activate/validate yan\u0131t\u0131n\u0131n HMAC-SHA256 do\u011frulamas\u0131. Sunucunun recursive ksort + JSON_UNESCAPED_SLASHES|UNICODE canonicalization\'\u0131n\u0131 byte-byte yans\u0131t\u0131r \u2014 drift = legitimate yan\u0131tlar tampered g\xf6r\xfcn\xfcr.\\n- **`FeatureTokenVerifier`** \u2014 sunucunun yay\u0131nlad\u0131\u011f\u0131 `{base64(json)}.{hmac}` token\'lar\u0131n\u0131 do\u011frular. 24s TTL. `hasFeature($payload, $flag)` eri\u015fimcisi Mode kap\u0131lar\u0131 taraf\u0131ndan kullan\u0131l\u0131r.\\n- **`VerifyEndpoint`** \u2014 sunucunun ters do\u011frulama s\u0131ras\u0131nda `X-MHM-Challenge`\'\u0131na yan\u0131t veren public REST route `/wp-json/mhm-rentiva-verify/v1/ping`.\\n\\n### Mode kap\u0131 refactor\\n\\n`canUseVendorMarketplace()`, `canUseMessages()`, `canUseAdvancedReports()`, `canUseVendorPayout()` art\u0131k tek bir `featureGranted()` private helper \xfczerinden y\xf6nlendiriliyor:\\n\\n1. \xd6nce `isPro()` hard-check\\n2. E\u011fer `FEATURE_TOKEN_KEY` tan\u0131ms\u0131zsa \u2192 legacy `isPro()` fallback (mevcut m\xfc\u015fteriler k\u0131r\u0131lm\u0131yor)\\n3. Aksi takdirde yerel olarak saklanan feature token\'\u0131n HMAC\'ini do\u011frular\\n4. Payload\'dan belirli flag\'i okur (`vendor_marketplace`, `messaging`, `advanced_reports`, vb.)\\n\\n`isActive()` \xfczerinde bir `return true;` yamas\u0131 art\u0131k hi\xe7bir \u015fey a\xe7m\u0131yor \xe7\xfcnk\xfc kap\u0131 ba\u011f\u0131ms\u0131z olarak sunucu-taraf\u0131ndan verilmi\u015f bir flag istiyor.\\n\\n### LicenseManager ba\u011flant\u0131s\u0131\\n\\n- `activate()` istek g\xf6vdesi art\u0131k `client_version = MHM_RENTIVA_VERSION` i\xe7eriyor. Sunucu bunu s\xfcr\xfcm-bazl\u0131 ters do\u011frulama enforcement i\xe7in kullan\u0131r (Rentiva i\xe7in \u22654.30.0 alt s\u0131n\u0131r).\\n- Ba\u015far\u0131l\u0131 yan\u0131t\u0131n `feature_token` alan\u0131 mevcut lisans kayd\u0131n\u0131n yan\u0131nda saklan\u0131r.\\n- G\xfcnl\xfck do\u011frulama cron\'u her tikte token\'\u0131 yeniler.\\n\\n### Test kapsam\u0131\\n\\n`tests/Unit/Licensing/` ve `tests/Integration/Licensing/` alt\u0131nda 6 yeni test dosyas\u0131, **36 yeni test**. Toplam: 776 / 2715, PHPCS temiz, 3 yeni TR \xe7evirisi.\\n\\n## v4.30.1 \u2014 Ters Do\u011frulama UX D\xfczeltmesi (2026-04-25 sabah)\\n\\nv4.30.0 `MHM_RENTIVA_LICENSE_PING_SECRET`\'\u0131 **zorunlu** yapt\u0131 \u2014 onsuz, `VerifyEndpoint` 503 `ping_secret_not_configured` d\xf6nd\xfcrd\xfc ve lisans sunucusu da `site_unreachable` ile aktivasyonu reddetti. **Her m\xfc\u015fteri sitesi `wp-config.php`\'de operat\xf6r-pinned bir secret\'a ihtiya\xe7 duyuyordu** \u2014 bir son kullan\u0131c\u0131 \xfcr\xfcn\xfc i\xe7in kabul edilemez.\\n\\n### D\xfczeltme\\n\\n`VerifyEndpoint::handle_ping()`, `ClientSecrets::getPingSecret()` bo\u015f d\xf6nd\xfc\u011f\xfcnde aktivasyon ba\u015f\u0131na `site_hash`\'e geri d\xfc\u015fer (`LicenseManager::siteHash()`\'in yapt\u0131\u011f\u0131 gibi hesaplan\u0131r \u2014 `sha256(home_url + site_url)` JSON-kodlanm\u0131\u015f). Sunucu taraf\u0131 `mhm-license-server v1.9.1+`, `Security\\\\SiteVerifier`\'da e\u015fle\u015fen fallback\'i uygular, b\xf6ylece `site_hash` teknik olarak gizli olmasa bile HMAC challenge do\u011frulanabilir kal\u0131r.\\n\\n### Neden yine g\xfcvenli\\n\\n`site_hash` herkese a\xe7\u0131k olarak t\xfcretilebilir ancak ters ping iddia edilen `site_url`\'i hedefledi\u011fi i\xe7in tampering hala ba\u015far\u0131s\u0131z. O domaine sahip olmayan sald\u0131rgan GET\'i intercept edip sahte HMAC ile yan\u0131t veremez, HMAC anahtar\u0131 gizli olsun olmas\u0131n.\\n\\n### Geriye d\xf6n\xfck uyumluluk\\n\\n`MHM_RENTIVA_LICENSE_PING_SECRET` tan\u0131ml\u0131ysa `VerifyEndpoint` hala onu kullan\u0131r \u2014 operat\xf6r yap\u0131land\u0131rmas\u0131n\u0131 sabitlenmi\u015f v4.30.0 deploy\'lar\u0131 oldu\u011fu gibi \xe7al\u0131\u015fmaya devam eder.\\n\\n## v4.30.2 \u2014 Lisans Bildirimi Defansif D\xfczeltmesi (2026-04-25 \xf6\u011fleden sonra)\\n\\n`LicenseAdmin::admin_notices()` i\xe7inde iki katmanl\u0131 hata:\\n\\n### Hata A \u2014 Bo\u015f error_message \\"License activation failed: \\" (sondaki bo\u015f kuyrukla) render ediyordu\\n\\nStale URL state (`?license=error`, `&message=...` olmadan; \xf6rn. taray\u0131c\u0131 geri/ileri, bookmark, k\u0131rp\u0131lm\u0131\u015f kopyala-yap\u0131\u015ft\u0131r) `match`\'in default k\u0131sm\u0131ndan `sprintf(\\"...: %s\\", \'\')` \xe7a\u011fr\u0131s\u0131na s\u0131z\u0131yordu. M\xfc\u015fteri hi\xe7bir \u015fey basmad\u0131\u011f\u0131 halde License sayfas\u0131n\u0131n \xfcst\xfcnde g\xf6r\xfcn\xfcyordu.\\n\\n### Hata B \u2014 v1.8.0+/v1.9.x sunucu hata kodlar\u0131 i\xe7in eksik match arm\'lar\u0131\\n\\n`site_unreachable`, `site_verification_failed`, `tampered_response`, `product_mismatch`, `product_slug_required` i\xe7in kullan\u0131c\u0131 dostu \xe7evirisi yoktu. Ayn\u0131 default arm\'a d\xfc\u015f\xfcyorlar, ham teknik kodlar\u0131 son kullan\u0131c\u0131lara s\u0131zd\u0131r\u0131yorlard\u0131 (\\"License activation failed: site_unreachable\\").\\n\\n### D\xfczeltme (\xfc\xe7 katman)\\n\\n1. **Defansif guard:** `if (\'\' === $error_message) { break; }` aksiyona ge\xe7irilebilir bir kod yoksa notice\'\u0131 tamamen atlar.\\n2. **Be\u015f yeni match arm\'\u0131**, m\xfc\u015fteri-dostu EN string\'leri + T\xfcrk\xe7e \xe7evirilerle.\\n3. **Generic default + `data-error-code` attribute:** bilinmeyen gelecek kodlar\u0131 \\"Lisans etkinle\u015ftirme ba\u015far\u0131s\u0131z oldu. L\xfctfen tekrar deneyin.\\" render eder, teknik kod `data-error-code` HTML attribute arac\u0131l\u0131\u011f\u0131yla a\xe7\u0131\u011fa \xe7\u0131kar\u0131l\u0131r (sadece debug / destek i\xe7in \u2014 asla inline metin de\u011fil).\\n\\n### Stable tag drift yakaland\u0131\\n\\nS\xfcr\xfcm bump\'\u0131 s\u0131ras\u0131nda bir audit `readme.txt` Stable tag\'inin `4.30.0`\'da tak\u0131l\u0131 kald\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131 yakalad\u0131 \u2014 v4.30.1 release\'i yanl\u0131\u015fl\u0131kla bump\'\u0131 atlam\u0131\u015ft\u0131. v4.30.2 `4.30.2`\'ye d\xfczeltir.\\n\\n### Test kapsam\u0131\\n\\n`tests/Unit/Licensing/LicenseAdminAdminNoticesTest.php` \u2014 empty defense, `site_unreachable` mapping, generic default + data attribute ve iki regression case\'i (`activated`, no-license-query) kapsayan 5 yeni test. Toplam: **781 / 2726**, PHPCS temiz.\\n\\n### Canl\u0131 do\u011frulama\\n\\nChrome DevTools MCP, v4.30.2 deploy\'undan sonra mhmrentiva.com\'da bir tur scriptledi:\\n\\n| URL | Beklenen | Canl\u0131 sonu\xe7 |\\n|---|---|---|\\n| `?license=error` | Notice yok (defansif guard) | \u2705 0 notice elementi |\\n| `?license=error&message=site_unreachable` | Friendly EN mesaj + `data-error-code=\\"site_unreachable\\"`, inline metinde ham kod yok | \u2705 DOM script ile teyit |\\n| `?license=error&message=imaginary_code_42` | Generic mesaj + `data-error-code=\\"imaginary_code_42\\"`, inline metinde ham kod yok | \u2705 teyit |\\n\\n## E\u015flik eden sunucu s\xfcr\xfcmleri (mhm-license-server, wpalemi.com\'da)\\n\\n- **v1.9.0** \u2014 Faz A: HMAC yan\u0131t imzalama, ters site do\u011frulama, feature token issuer (24s TTL).\\n- **v1.9.1** \u2014 `Security\\\\SiteVerifier::verify()` i\xe7inde `site_hash` fallback (v4.30.1 istemcisi ile e\u015fle\u015fir).\\n- **v1.9.2** \u2014 `SecretManager::getPingSecret()` opt-in only (file fallback yok) \u2014 sunucu otomatik olarak `wp-uploads/mhm-license-secrets/ping.key` \xfcretti\u011fi i\xe7in m\xfc\u015fterilerin zero-config \xe7al\u0131\u015ft\u0131\u011f\u0131 asimetrik HMAC hatas\u0131n\u0131 kapatt\u0131.\\n- **v1.9.3 (KR\u0130T\u0130K)** \u2014 `LicenseActivator::activate()` art\u0131k slug-ba\u011fl\u0131 bir lisans sat\u0131r\u0131na kar\u015f\u0131 bo\u015f `product_slug`\'\u0131 hard-reddediyor. \xd6nceki kod yolu, tek bir kaynak d\xfczenlemesinin slug\'\u0131 istek g\xf6vdesinden silmesine ve hem v1.8.0 ba\u011flamay\u0131 HEM de v1.9.0 ters do\u011frulamay\u0131 (`REVERSE_VALIDATION_FLOOR[\'\'] === null` legacy-pass branch\'ine d\xfc\u015ft\xfc\u011f\xfc i\xe7in) atlamas\u0131na izin veriyordu.\\n\\nBirle\u015fik: sunucu taraf\u0131nda **143 PHPUnit, 398 assertion, PHPCS temiz**.\\n\\nv1.9.3 deploy\'undan sonra \xfc\xe7 canl\u0131 sald\u0131r\u0131 senaryosu `wpalemi.com`\'da curl ile do\u011fruland\u0131:\\n\\n| Senaryo | Beklenen | Canl\u0131 sonu\xe7 |\\n|---|---|---|\\n| `product_slug` g\xf6vdeden kald\u0131r\u0131lm\u0131\u015f | `product_slug_required` reject | \u2705 teyit |\\n| \xc7apraz \xfcr\xfcn slug swap (CS slug + Rentiva site) | `site_unreachable` (CS verify endpoint Rentiva site\'inde yok) | \u2705 teyit |\\n| Do\u011fru ak\u0131\u015f regression | 200 active | \u2705 teyit |\\n\\n## E\u015flik eden Currency Switcher s\xfcr\xfcmleri\\n\\n`mhm-currency-switcher v0.5.0` (Faz C istemcisi) \u2192 `v0.5.1` (CI hotfix: `str_ends_with` PHP 7.4 uyumu + `OrderFilterTest` `WC_Order` stub) \u2192 `v0.5.2` (`VerifyEndpoint` `site_hash` fallback). Ayn\u0131 be\u015f-sald\u0131r\u0131 y\xfczeyli savunma CS Mode kap\u0131lar\u0131na sekiz feature flag ile uyguland\u0131 (`fixed_pricing`, `nav_menu_switcher`, `flag_library`, `geolocation`, `payment_restrictions`, `auto_rate_update`, `multilingual`, `rest_api_filter`).\\n\\n## M\xfc\u015fteri etkisi\\n\\nBu sprint\'ten sonra Rentiva v4.30.1+ (ve CS v0.5.2+) m\xfc\u015fterileri:\\n\\n- **Sadece lisans anahtar\u0131n\u0131 girip Activate\'e basar.** `wp-config.php` d\xfczenlemesi yok.\\n- Sunucu taraf\u0131 \xfc\xe7 katmanl\u0131 savunma (slug ba\u011flama + yan\u0131t imzalama + ters do\u011frulama) tam aktif.\\n- Lisans bildirim mesajlar\u0131 kullan\u0131c\u0131 dostu ve locale-aware; ham teknik jargon g\xf6r\xfcnm\xfcyor.\\n- Mevcut v4.27.x kurulumlar\u0131, y\xfckseltene kadar legacy fallback yollar\u0131 \xfczerinden oldu\u011fu gibi \xe7al\u0131\u015fmaya devam eder.\\n\\n## Bilinen s\u0131n\u0131r (ertelendi)\\n\\nYeterince kararl\u0131 bir sald\u0131rgan, **kendi** sitesinde **kendi** \xfcr\xfcn-e\u015fle\u015fen lisans\u0131yla k\u0131r\u0131lm\u0131\u015f bir plugin binary\'si \xe7al\u0131\u015ft\u0131rarak, m\xfc\u015fteri `wp-config.php`\'de `MHM_RENTIVA_LICENSE_FEATURE_TOKEN_KEY` tan\u0131mlamad\u0131\u011f\u0131nda (zero-config deployment kas\u0131tl\u0131 olarak bu trade-off\'u kabul ediyor) `Mode::canUse*()`\'i hala do\u011frudan yamalayabilir.\\n\\nKaynak-d\xfczenleme + zero-config a\xe7\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131 kapatmak **asimetrik kripto** gerektirir (RSA-imzal\u0131 feature token\'lar, eklenti kayna\u011f\u0131nda g\xf6m\xfcl\xfc public key \u2014 open-source g\xfcvenli). Bu **mhm-license-server v1.10.0 + mhm-rentiva v4.31.0 + mhm-currency-switcher v0.6.0**\'a ertelendi, lansman sonras\u0131 planland\u0131.\\n\\n## \ud83c\udf93 Yakalanan dersler (haf\u0131za + KB)\\n\\n- **`patterns/license-defense-in-depth-stack.md`** \u2014 be\u015f katmanl\u0131 savunma dok\xfcmantasyonu, sald\u0131r\u0131 matrisi, asimetrik kripto roadmap.\\n- **`patterns/admin-notice-url-state-defense.md`** \u2014 redirect-after-action notice\'lar\u0131 i\xe7in \xfc\xe7 katmanl\u0131 savunma (bo\u015f guard + generic default + data attribute).\\n- **`patterns/release-zip-audit.md`** \u2014 tag/release \xf6ncesi \xfc\xe7 audit; bu sprint s\u0131ras\u0131nda \xfc\xe7 ZIP s\u0131z\u0131nt\u0131s\u0131 yakalad\u0131 (`drafts/`, `bin/`, `*.po~`).\\n- **`standards/i18n-workflow.md`** \u2014 `.po~` msgmerge backup pattern\'i + `.l10n.php` deploy zorunlulu\u011fu ile g\xfcncellendi.\\n- **`wp-conductor` skill** \u2014 release ba\u015f\u0131na do\u011frulama gereksinimlerine sahip yeni \\"Uzun Seans / Zincir Release Disiplini\\" gate (2026-04-25\'teki 8 release zinciri bunu motive eden baseline failure\'d\u0131).\\n\\n---\\n\\n*GitHub Releases:*\\n- *Rentiva: [v4.30.0](https://github.com/MaxHandMade/mhm-rentiva/releases/tag/v4.30.0) \xb7 [v4.30.1](https://github.com/MaxHandMade/mhm-rentiva/releases/tag/v4.30.1) \xb7 [v4.30.2](https://github.com/MaxHandMade/mhm-rentiva/releases/tag/v4.30.2)*\\n- *License Server: [v1.9.0](https://github.com/MaxHandMade/mhm-license-server/releases/tag/v1.9.0) \xb7 [v1.9.1](https://github.com/MaxHandMade/mhm-license-server/releases/tag/v1.9.1) \xb7 [v1.9.2](https://github.com/MaxHandMade/mhm-license-server/releases/tag/v1.9.2) \xb7 [v1.9.3](https://github.com/MaxHandMade/mhm-license-server/releases/tag/v1.9.3)*\\n- *Currency Switcher: [v0.5.0](https://github.com/MaxHandMade/mhm-currency-switcher/releases/tag/v0.5.0) \xb7 [v0.5.1](https://github.com/MaxHandMade/mhm-currency-switcher/releases/tag/v0.5.1) \xb7 [v0.5.2](https://github.com/MaxHandMade/mhm-currency-switcher/releases/tag/v0.5.2)*"},{"id":"v4.27.4-v4.27.6-stability-sprint","metadata":{"permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/v4.27.4-v4.27.6-stability-sprint","editUrl":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade/mhm-rentiva-docs/tree/main/blog/2026-04-23-v4.27.4-v4.27.6-stability.md","source":"@site/i18n/tr/docusaurus-plugin-content-blog/2026-04-23-v4.27.4-v4.27.6-stability.md","title":"MHM Rentiva v4.27.4\u2013v4.27.6: Migration \u015eerit Mimarisi, Lisans Slug \u0130letimi, WordPress.org Cilas\u0131","description":"2026-04-23\'te art arda yay\u0131mlanan \xfc\xe7 patch s\xfcr\xfcm\xfcn\xfc kapsayan retrospektif bir yaz\u0131: kritik migration mimarisi d\xfczeltmesi (v4.27.4), \xfcr\xfcn bazl\u0131 lisans ba\u011flama uyumu (v4.27.5) ve WordPress.org g\xf6nderim haz\u0131rl\u0131\u011f\u0131 (v4.27.6). v4.30.x g\xfcvenlik sprint\'inden sonra geriye d\xf6n\xfck olarak yay\u0131nlan\u0131yor.","date":"2026-04-23T22:00:00.000Z","tags":[{"inline":true,"label":"release","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/release"},{"inline":true,"label":"patch","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/patch"},{"inline":true,"label":"migration","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/migration"},{"inline":true,"label":"license","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/license"},{"inline":true,"label":"wordpress-org","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/wordpress-org"},{"inline":true,"label":"mhm-rentiva","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/mhm-rentiva"}],"readingTime":3.24,"hasTruncateMarker":true,"authors":[{"name":"MaxHandMade","title":"Maintainer","url":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade","imageURL":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade.png","key":"maxhandmade","page":null}],"frontMatter":{"slug":"v4.27.4-v4.27.6-stability-sprint","title":"MHM Rentiva v4.27.4\u2013v4.27.6: Migration \u015eerit Mimarisi, Lisans Slug \u0130letimi, WordPress.org Cilas\u0131","authors":["maxhandmade"],"tags":["release","patch","migration","license","wordpress-org","mhm-rentiva"],"date":"2026-04-23T22:00"},"unlisted":false,"prevItem":{"title":"Lisans G\xfcvenlik Sertle\u015ftirme Sprint\'i: Rentiva v4.30.0 \u2192 v4.30.2 (mhm-license-server v1.9.0\u2013v1.9.3 ve CS v0.5.x ile)","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/license-security-sprint-v4.30.x"},"nextItem":{"title":"MHM Rentiva v4.27.2: Settings Testing Kirlilik Hotfix + Duplicate Addon Notice Dedupe","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/v4.27.2-settings-testing-pollution-hotfix"}},"content":"2026-04-23\'te art arda yay\u0131mlanan \xfc\xe7 patch s\xfcr\xfcm\xfcn\xfc kapsayan retrospektif bir yaz\u0131: **kritik migration mimarisi d\xfczeltmesi** (v4.27.4), **\xfcr\xfcn bazl\u0131 lisans ba\u011flama uyumu** (v4.27.5) ve **WordPress.org g\xf6nderim haz\u0131rl\u0131\u011f\u0131** (v4.27.6). v4.30.x g\xfcvenlik sprint\'inden sonra geriye d\xf6n\xfck olarak yay\u0131nlan\u0131yor.\\n\\n\x3c!--truncate--\x3e\\n\\n## v4.27.4 \u2014 Migration \u015eerit Mimarisi D\xfczeltmesi (KR\u0130T\u0130K)\\n\\nv4.27.1 (i18n locale leak) ve v4.27.2 (Settings Testing kirlenme) i\xe7inde gelen veri-temizlik migrasyonlar\u0131 **g\xfcncellenmi\u015f sitelerde asl\u0131nda hi\xe7 \xe7al\u0131\u015fm\u0131yordu** \u2014 v4.27.0 haz\u0131rl\u0131\u011f\u0131 s\u0131ras\u0131nda temizlenmi\u015f bir gerileme migration tetikleyicisini sessizce bozmu\u015ftu.\\n\\n### K\xf6k neden\\n\\n`plugins_loaded` migration callback\'i tek bir k\u0131sa devre kullan\u0131yordu:\\n\\n```php\\nif ( $stored_version === MHM_RENTIVA_VERSION ) {\\n    return; // T\xdcM migrasyonlar\u0131 atla\\n}\\n```\\n\\nAncak `mhm_rentiva_single_site_activation()` (her ZIP-replace g\xfcncelleme yolunda `plugins_loaded`\'dan \xd6NCE \xe7al\u0131\u015f\u0131r) yeni s\xfcr\xfcm\xfc zaten option\'a damgalam\u0131\u015f oluyordu. `plugins_loaded` \xe7al\u0131\u015ft\u0131\u011f\u0131nda `$stored === $current` zaten true \u2192 **t\xfcm flag-kap\u0131l\u0131 temizlikler sonsuza dek atlan\u0131yordu.**\\n\\nmhmrentiva.com canl\u0131da kan\u0131t: Brand Name `1` olarak g\xf6r\xfcn\xfcyordu, d\xf6viz istatistikleri `0,00 \u20ba` yerine `0,00 1` render oluyordu (\xe7\xfcnk\xfc v4.27.2 kirlenme migrasyonu hi\xe7bir zaman \xe7al\u0131\u015fmad\u0131).\\n\\n### Fix \u2014 iki-\u015ferit mimarisi\\n\\n`plugins_loaded` callback\'i iki ba\u011f\u0131ms\u0131z \u015feride b\xf6l\xfcnd\xfc:\\n\\n- **\u015eerit A (\u015fema drift, s\xfcr\xfcm-kap\u0131l\u0131):** sadece `$stored !== $current` oldu\u011funda \xe7al\u0131\u015f\u0131r. Ayn\u0131 s\xfcr\xfcm\xfcn birden fazla y\xfcklemesi aras\u0131 idempotent.\\n- **\u015eerit B (bayrak-kap\u0131l\u0131 veri temizlikleri):** her istekte \xe7al\u0131\u015f\u0131r, ancak her migrasyonun kendi `mhm_rentiva_<flag>` opsiyonu vard\u0131r ve ba\u015far\u0131l\u0131 \xe7al\u0131\u015fma sonras\u0131 flip eder. Ger\xe7ekten idempotent.\\n\\nHer iki \u015ferit de kendi hata yal\u0131t\u0131m\u0131na sahiptir; B\'deki bir hata A\'y\u0131 engellemez ya da tersine.\\n\\n### Test kapsam\u0131\\n\\n`tests/Migration/MigrationLaneIndependenceTest.php` \u2014 b\xf6l\xfcnmeyi koruyan 3 yeni test, 8 assertion.\\n\\n### Ampirik do\u011frulama\\n\\nDeploy sonras\u0131 mhmrentiva.com\'un Chrome DevTools MCP ile taray\u0131c\u0131 turu: 0 yinelenen uyar\u0131, istatistikler `0,00 \u20ba` (U+20BA), Brand Name \\"MHM Rentiva\\". 11 admin sekmesinde manuel tek seferlik **Reset to Defaults** ile migrasyonlar\u0131n \xe7al\u0131\u015fmad\u0131\u011f\u0131 d\xf6nemden kalan art\u0131k state temizlendi.\\n\\n## v4.27.5 \u2014 Lisans \u0130stemcisi \xdcr\xfcn-Slug \u0130letimi\\n\\n`mhm-license-server v1.8.0+` ile uyumlu \u2014 bu s\xfcr\xfcm \xfcr\xfcn-bazl\u0131 lisans ba\u011flama getirdi. v4.27.5 \xf6ncesinde bir m\xfc\u015fteri ucuz MHM Currency Switcher Ayl\u0131k anahtar\u0131 sat\u0131n al\u0131p Rentiva Pro\'yu aktive etmek i\xe7in kullanabiliyordu \u2014 sunucunun lisans\u0131n belirli bir \xfcr\xfcn i\xe7in verildi\u011fini do\u011frulayacak yolu yoktu.\\n\\n### De\u011fi\u015fiklik\\n\\n`LicenseManager::activate()` ve `validate()` istek g\xf6vdeleri art\u0131k `product_slug => \'mhm-rentiva\'` i\xe7eriyor. Sunucu bunu lisans sat\u0131r\u0131n\u0131n sakl\u0131 slug\'\u0131 ile kar\u015f\u0131la\u015ft\u0131r\u0131r ve uyu\u015fmazl\u0131klar\u0131 `product_mismatch` hatas\u0131yla reddeder.\\n\\n### Bonus d\xfczeltme\\n\\nEk Hizmetler admin sayfas\u0131 iki **Dok\xfcmantasyon** d\xfc\u011fmesi g\xf6steriyordu \u2014 k\xfcresel `all_admin_notices` docs hook\'u + sayfan\u0131n kendi ba\u015fl\u0131\u011f\u0131, ikisi de yang\u0131nland\u0131. Hook art\u0131k `vehicle_addon` ekran\u0131n\u0131 atl\u0131yor; sayfa ba\u015fl\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131n d\xfc\u011fmesi tek kaynak.\\n\\n## v4.27.6 \u2014 WordPress.org G\xf6nderim Cilas\u0131\\n\\nWordPress.org eklenti dizini g\xf6nderimi i\xe7in Plugin Check (PCP) uyumu: **1 ERROR + 115 WARNING \u2192 0 ERROR + 61 WARNING**. Kalan uyar\u0131lar Plugin Check\'in projenin `phpcs.xml` \xf6nek yap\u0131land\u0131rmas\u0131n\u0131 okumamas\u0131ndan kaynaklanan yanl\u0131\u015f pozitiflerin t\xfcm\xfc.\\n\\n### Somut d\xfczeltmeler\\n\\n- Demo g\xf6rsel i\xe7e aktar\u0131c\u0131s\u0131nda `unlink()` \u2192 `wp_delete_file()` (tek ger\xe7ek ERROR).\\n- Projenin kurallar\u0131 zaten d\u0131\u015flayan uyar\u0131lar i\xe7in gerek\xe7eli `phpcs:ignore` yorumlar\u0131 (denetim ama\xe7l\u0131 `error_log()` \xe7a\u011fr\u0131lar\u0131, Plugin Check\'in tan\u0131may\u0131 reddetti\u011fi `mhm_rentiva_` \xf6neki ta\u015f\u0131yan hook\'lar, kabul edilen `meta_query` / `post__not_in` performans takaslar\u0131, \xe7ekirdek-kontroll\xfc tablo adlar\u0131 `$wpdb->prepare()` \xfczerinden ba\u011flanm\u0131\u015f ledger sorgular\u0131).\\n- Plugin Check\'in \xf6nek konvansiyonuna uyacak \u015fekilde `$pending_messages` template-scope de\u011fi\u015fkeni `$mhm_rentiva_pending_messages`\'a yeniden adland\u0131r\u0131ld\u0131.\\n- `readme.txt` Changelog b\xf6l\xfcm\xfc WP.org\'un 5000 karakter s\u0131n\u0131r\u0131na uyacak \u015fekilde k\u0131salt\u0131ld\u0131; eski s\xfcr\xfcmler GitHub\'a ba\u011fland\u0131.\\n- `changelog-tr.json` v4.27.5 backfill + yeni v4.27.6 giri\u015fi.\\n\\n### Fonksiyonel de\u011fi\u015fiklik yok\\n\\n740/740 PHPUnit h\xe2l\xe2 ge\xe7iyor. PHPCS temiz. Eklenti ayn\u0131 \u015fekilde davran\u0131yor \u2014 sadece Plugin Check g\xfcr\xfclt\xfcs\xfc azalt\u0131ld\u0131.\\n\\n## \u2705 \xdc\xe7\xfc i\xe7in do\u011frulama\\n\\n| Kontrol | v4.27.4 | v4.27.5 | v4.27.6 |\\n|---|---|---|---|\\n| PHPUnit | 740/740, 2642 assertion, 6 skipped | de\u011fi\u015fmedi | de\u011fi\u015fmedi |\\n| PHPCS | 0 / 0 | 0 / 0 | 0 / 0 |\\n| Plugin Check ERROR | de\u011fi\u015fmedi | de\u011fi\u015fmedi | 1 \u2192 0 |\\n\\n## \ud83c\udf93 Yakalanan dersler (haf\u0131za)\\n\\n- **`feedback_migration_lane_architecture.md`** \u2014 activation hook\'lar\u0131 s\xfcr\xfcm\xfc `plugins_loaded`\'dan \xf6nce damgalad\u0131\u011f\u0131nda, s\xfcr\xfcm kap\u0131s\u0131 t\xfcm bayrak-kap\u0131l\u0131 migrasyonlar\u0131 k\u0131rar. S\xfcr\xfcm-drift ve veri-temizleme \u015feritlerini her zaman ay\u0131r.\\n- **`feedback_empirical_dom_verification.md`** \u2014 Chrome DevTools MCP ile DOM d\xfczeyinde do\u011frulama, %100 PHPUnit + 0 PHPCS\'in mutlu mutlu yay\u0131nlayaca\u011f\u0131 runtime DB-state bug\'lar\u0131n\u0131 yakalaman\u0131n tek yolu.\\n\\n## \ud83d\udd1c S\u0131radaki\\n\\nv4.27.x \u015femsiyesi burada kapand\u0131. S\u0131radaki b\xfcy\xfck v4.28.0 idi (Pop\xfcler Rotalar) \u2014 ancak \xe7apraz \xfcr\xfcn sald\u0131r\u0131 y\xfczeyi g\xfcvenlik denetimi yol haritas\u0131n\u0131 **Lisans G\xfcvenlik Sertle\u015ftirme** sprint\'ine (v4.30.x) yeniden \xf6ncelikledi, 2026-04-24/25\'te yay\u0131mland\u0131.\\n\\n---\\n\\n*GitHub S\xfcr\xfcmleri: [v4.27.4](https://github.com/MaxHandMade/mhm-rentiva/releases/tag/v4.27.4) \xb7 [v4.27.5](https://github.com/MaxHandMade/mhm-rentiva/releases/tag/v4.27.5) \xb7 [v4.27.6](https://github.com/MaxHandMade/mhm-rentiva/releases/tag/v4.27.6)*"},{"id":"v4.27.2-settings-testing-pollution-hotfix","metadata":{"permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/v4.27.2-settings-testing-pollution-hotfix","editUrl":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade/mhm-rentiva-docs/tree/main/blog/2026-04-23-v4.27.2-release.md","source":"@site/i18n/tr/docusaurus-plugin-content-blog/2026-04-23-v4.27.2-release.md","title":"MHM Rentiva v4.27.2: Settings Testing Kirlilik Hotfix + Duplicate Addon Notice Dedupe","description":"v4.27.1 i18n hotfix\'inden sonra kullan\u0131c\u0131 \xfc\xe7 yeni bug daha bildirdi \u2014 hepsi ayn\u0131 taze-kurulum senaryosundan geliyor ve \xfc\xe7\xfc de Settings Testing sayfas\u0131nda \\"Run All Diagnostics\\" butonuna bir kere basma ile tetikleniyor. v4.27.2 bu zinciri k\u0131r\u0131yor.","date":"2026-04-23T19:00:00.000Z","tags":[{"inline":true,"label":"release","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/release"},{"inline":true,"label":"patch","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/patch"},{"inline":true,"label":"hotfix","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/hotfix"},{"inline":true,"label":"settings","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/settings"},{"inline":true,"label":"diagnostics","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/diagnostics"},{"inline":true,"label":"bugfix","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/bugfix"},{"inline":true,"label":"mhm-rentiva","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/mhm-rentiva"}],"readingTime":3.77,"hasTruncateMarker":true,"authors":[{"name":"MaxHandMade","title":"Maintainer","url":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade","imageURL":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade.png","key":"maxhandmade","page":null}],"frontMatter":{"slug":"v4.27.2-settings-testing-pollution-hotfix","title":"MHM Rentiva v4.27.2: Settings Testing Kirlilik Hotfix + Duplicate Addon Notice Dedupe","authors":["maxhandmade"],"tags":["release","patch","hotfix","settings","diagnostics","bugfix","mhm-rentiva"],"date":"2026-04-23T19:00"},"unlisted":false,"prevItem":{"title":"MHM Rentiva v4.27.4\u2013v4.27.6: Migration \u015eerit Mimarisi, Lisans Slug \u0130letimi, WordPress.org Cilas\u0131","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/v4.27.4-v4.27.6-stability-sprint"},"nextItem":{"title":"MHM Rentiva v4.27.1: i18n Locale-Leak Hotfix \u2014 Ara\xe7 Ayarlar\u0131 Etiketleri Art\u0131k \u0130lk Kurulum Dilinde Donmuyor","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/v4.27.1-i18n-locale-leak-hotfix"}},"content":"v4.27.1 i18n hotfix\'inden sonra kullan\u0131c\u0131 \xfc\xe7 yeni bug daha bildirdi \u2014 hepsi ayn\u0131 taze-kurulum senaryosundan geliyor ve \xfc\xe7\xfc de **Settings Testing sayfas\u0131nda \\"Run All Diagnostics\\" butonuna bir kere basma** ile tetikleniyor. v4.27.2 bu zinciri k\u0131r\u0131yor.\\n\\n\x3c!--truncate--\x3e\\n\\n## \ud83d\udc1b Bug 1: Taze Kurulumda T\xfcm Text Alanlar\u0131 \\"1\\"\\n\\n**Senaryo:**\\n1. Eklenti taze kurulur.\\n2. Kullan\u0131c\u0131 **Ayarlar \u2192 Settings Testing** sekmesine gidip \\"Run All Diagnostics\\" butonuna basar.\\n3. General Settings\'e d\xf6ner \u2014 **Brand Name = \\"1\\"**, **Cancellation Deadline = 1**, **Payment Deadline = 1**, Support Email, Brand Logo URL, vs. hep \\"1\\".\\n4. Ancak **\\"Reset to Defaults\\"** butonuna bas\u0131nca d\xfczeliyor.\\n\\n### K\xf6k Neden\\n\\n`SettingsTester::test_settings_save()` bir \\"de\u011fi\u015fiklik alg\u0131lanm\u0131\u015f save\\" tetiklemek i\xe7in bo\u015f string\'leri `\'1\'`\'e \xe7eviriyordu:\\n\\n```php\\n// Fresh install: $current_str == \'\'\\nif ( in_array( $current_str, array( \'0\', \'1\', \'\' ) ) ) {\\n    $test_value = ( $current_str === \'1\' ) ? \'0\' : \'1\'; // \u2192 \'1\'\\n}\\n```\\n\\nSonra bu `\'1\'` payload\'u **GER\xc7EK** sanitizer\'a veriliyordu. Sanitizer hedef tab\'\u0131n T\xdcM alanlar\u0131n\u0131 yeniden yaz\u0131yordu (sadece test edilen keyleri de\u011fil). Restore mekanizmas\u0131 ise SADECE a\xe7\u0131k\xe7a test edilen keyleri eski haline getiriyordu \u2192 di\u011fer tab alanlar\u0131na yap\u0131lan collateral yaz\u0131mlar DB\'de kal\u0131yordu.\\n\\n**Vahim nokta:** Fresh install\'da General test \xe7al\u0131\u015ft\u0131\u011f\u0131nda:\\n- `brand_name` \u2192 \'1\' (test flip\'i, sonra restore edildi) \u2713\\n- `currency` \u2192 \'1\' (flip + restore) \u2713\\n- `dark_mode` \u2192 sanitizer yazd\u0131, test hi\xe7 dokunmad\u0131 \u2192 **DB\'de kald\u0131**\\n- `support_email` \u2192 sanitizer default olarak `admin@...`e yazd\u0131, flip\'le \'1\' oldu, restore edilmedi \u2192 **DB\'de kald\u0131**\\n- ... ve daha fazlas\u0131\\n\\n### \xc7\xf6z\xfcm\\n\\n#### 1. Harness fix \u2014 tam snapshot/restore\\n\\n```php\\n// YEN\u0130 v4.27.2: B\xdcT\xdcN option\'\u0131 snapshot al, B\xdcT\xdcN option\'\u0131 restore et.\\n$option_existed_before = false !== get_option( $option_name, false );\\n$full_option_snapshot  = (array) get_option( $option_name, array() );\\n\\n// ... test ko\u015far, sanitizer DB\'yi kirletir ...\\n\\nif ( $option_existed_before ) {\\n    update_option( $option_name, $full_option_snapshot );\\n} else {\\n    delete_option( $option_name );\\n}\\n```\\n\\nTest art\u0131k DB\'yi ger\xe7ekten read-only b\u0131rak\u0131yor. Collateral yaz\u0131mlar otomatik yok oluyor.\\n\\n#### 2. Migration \u2014 mevcut install\'lar\u0131 temizle\\n\\n`SettingsCore::migrate_clean_test_pollution()` flag\'li (`mhm_rentiva_v4272_test_pollution_cleaned`) tek seferlik migrasyon:\\n\\n```php\\n$polluted_keys = array(\\n    \'mhm_rentiva_brand_name\', \'mhm_rentiva_email_from_name\',\\n    \'mhm_rentiva_email_from_address\', \'mhm_rentiva_support_email\',\\n    \'mhm_rentiva_booking_url\', \'mhm_rentiva_login_url\',\\n    \'mhm_rentiva_currency\', /* ... */\\n);\\n\\nforeach ($polluted_keys as $key) {\\n    $value = $settings[$key] ?? null;\\n    if (\'0\' === $value || \'1\' === $value) {\\n        unset($settings[$key]); // fallback to default\\n    }\\n}\\n```\\n\\nSadece kirlilik imzas\u0131n\u0131 (`\'0\'` / `\'1\'`) olan **text, email, URL, currency** alanlar\u0131n\u0131 temizliyor. Numeric alanlar (deadline\'lar) dokunulmad\u0131 \u2014 kullan\u0131c\u0131 ger\xe7ekten 1 girmek istemi\u015f olabilir (nadiren). Legitimate string de\u011ferler korunuyor.\\n\\n## \ud83d\udc1b Bug 2: Ek Hizmetler Sayfas\u0131nda \xc7ift Limit Notice\\n\\nAdditional Services admin sayfas\u0131nda Lite limit uyar\u0131s\u0131 **iki kez** g\xf6r\xfcn\xfcyordu \u2014 istatistik kartlar\u0131n\u0131n \xfcst\xfcnde ve alt\u0131nda.\\n\\n### K\xf6k Neden\\n\\n`AddonMenu::add_addon_page_title()` i\xe7inde, notice i\xe7 i\xe7e ge\xe7mi\u015f `<div class=\\"wrap\\">` blo\u011funun i\xe7inde emit ediliyordu. WordPress core admin-notice relocator JS\'i bu durumda:\\n- Standart kopyay\u0131 `wp-header-end` marker\'\u0131ndan sonra yerle\u015ftiriyor\\n- Orijinal kopya i\xe7 wrap\'in i\xe7inde duruyor\\n- \u2192 \u0130ki kopya\\n\\n### \xc7\xf6z\xfcm\\n\\nNotice art\u0131k ayr\u0131 bir `admin_notices` callback\'i \u2014 `AddonMenu::render_addon_limit_notice()` \u2014 priority 20\'de. \u0130\xe7 wrap kapat\u0131ld\u0131ktan SONRA emit ediliyor, WordPress tam olarak bir kez yerle\u015ftiriyor.\\n\\n## \ud83d\udc1b Bug 3: Settings Testing \\"Defaults Set\\" Phantom Key FAIL\'leri\\n\\nSettings Testing sayfas\u0131, hi\xe7bir yerde kay\u0131tl\u0131 olmayan ayar keyleri i\xe7in \\"Defaults Set: FAIL\\" veriyordu:\\n- `mhm_rentiva_timezone` (General\'de yok)\\n- `mhm_rentiva_db_auto_optimize` (Core\'da yok)\\n- `mhm_rentiva_wp_optimization_enabled` (Core\'da yok)\\n- `mhm_rentiva_my_account_url` (Frontend\'de yok)\\n\\n### \xc7\xf6z\xfcm\\n\\nBu phantom keyleri check-list\'ten \xe7\u0131kard\u0131m. Ayr\u0131ca \\"Email Address Valid\\" ve \\"Email Validation Works\\" FAIL\'leri de Bug 1\'in alt etkisiydi (`\'1\'` \u2192 `is_email(\'1\')` = false) \u2014 kirlilik migrasyonu \xe7al\u0131\u015ft\u0131ktan sonra kendili\u011finden ge\xe7er.\\n\\n## \ud83e\uddea Testler\\n\\n`tests/Migration/SettingsTestPollutionMigrationTest.php` \u2014 **5 yeni test, 19 assertion**:\\n\\n1. Text/email/URL/currency kirlili\u011fi temizleniyor\\n2. Me\u015fru kullan\u0131c\u0131 de\u011ferleri korunuyor\\n3. Numeric alanlar (deadlines) dokunulmuyor\\n4. Post-migration me\u015fru \\"1\\" rename\'i ezilmiyor (idempotent)\\n5. Fresh install\'da flag set ediliyor\\n\\n## \u2705 Do\u011frulama\\n\\n| Kontrol | Sonu\xe7 |\\n|---|---|\\n| PHPCS release | 0 error / 0 warning |\\n| PHPUnit | **737/737** (+5 yeni, 732\u2192737), 6 skipped, 0 regresyon |\\n| Plugin Check (PCP) | 0 error, 3 trivial warning (de\u011fi\u015fmedi) |\\n\\n## \u26a0\ufe0f Upgrade Notu\\n\\n\\"Run All Diagnostics\\"\'e bas\u0131p Brand Name = 1 g\xf6ren kullan\u0131c\u0131lar: Migrasyon bir sonraki admin page load\'da otomatik \xe7al\u0131\u015f\u0131yor. **\\"Reset to Defaults\\"\'a basman GEREKM\u0130YOR**. Text/email/URL/currency alanlar\u0131 defaults\'a geri d\xf6necek.\\n\\n**Say\u0131sal deadline\'lar (Cancellation / Payment)** dokunulmuyor \u2014 migrasyon bunlar\u0131 kullan\u0131c\u0131 se\xe7imi olabilir diye ay\u0131rt edemiyor. Booking tab\'\u0131nda deadline\'lar\u0131 24 saat / 30 dakika (veya tercih etti\u011fin de\u011fer) olarak manuel ayarla.\\n\\n## \ud83d\udce6 Kurulum\\n\\n`mhm-rentiva.4.27.2.zip` \u2192 **Eklentiler \u2192 Yeni Ekle \u2192 Eklenti Y\xfckle**, veya Rentiva Pro otomatik g\xfcncelleyicisi.\\n\\n**Gereksinimler:** PHP 8.1+, WordPress 6.7+.\\n\\n## \ud83c\udf93 Ders\\n\\nBu \xfc\xe7 bug da \u2014 v4.27.1 i18n hotfix gibi \u2014 **runtime DB-state** s\u0131n\u0131f\u0131nda. Ne PHPCS, ne PCP, ne unit test suite bunlar\u0131 yakalayabilir. Sadece ger\xe7ek admin UI \xfczerinden fresh install senaryosu s\u0131nanarak g\xf6r\xfcl\xfcyor. `feedback_runtime_smoke_test.md` memory notu art\u0131k **\\"her major release \xf6ncesi fresh install UI smoke test zorunlu\\"** diyor \u2014 bir sonraki major\'da bu pattern\'\u0131 checklist\'e entegre edece\u011fim.\\n\\nDinamik tablo: Bir g\xfcnde 3 release \xe7\u0131kard\u0131k \u2014 v4.27.0 (WPCS submission prep) \u2192 v4.27.1 (i18n locale leak) \u2192 v4.27.2 (Settings Testing pollution + duplicate Addon notice). Her biri zero-regression + yeni regression testleri ile. Agile patch pipeline \xe7al\u0131\u015f\u0131yor.\\n\\n## \ud83d\udd1c S\u0131radaki\\n\\n- v4.28.0: Pop\xfcler Rotalar shortcode/block/widget (yeni \xf6zellik)\\n- v4.29.0: Vendor Report / Appeal System (yeni alt sistem)\\n- v4.27.x roadmap\'i kapand\u0131 \u2014 bir sonraki \u015femsiye v4.28.0 olacak\\n\\n---\\n\\n*GitHub Release: [v4.27.2](https://github.com/MaxHandMade/mhm-rentiva/releases/tag/v4.27.2)*"},{"id":"v4.27.1-i18n-locale-leak-hotfix","metadata":{"permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/v4.27.1-i18n-locale-leak-hotfix","editUrl":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade/mhm-rentiva-docs/tree/main/blog/2026-04-23-v4.27.1-release.md","source":"@site/i18n/tr/docusaurus-plugin-content-blog/2026-04-23-v4.27.1-release.md","title":"MHM Rentiva v4.27.1: i18n Locale-Leak Hotfix \u2014 Ara\xe7 Ayarlar\u0131 Etiketleri Art\u0131k \u0130lk Kurulum Dilinde Donmuyor","description":"v4.27.0 WordPress.org g\xf6nderim haz\u0131rl\u0131\u011f\u0131ndan birka\xe7 saat sonra kritik bir bug yakaland\u0131: \u0130ngilizce bir WordPress sitesinde Ara\xe7 Ayarlar\u0131 sayfas\u0131 T\xfcrk\xe7e etiketler g\xf6steriyordu. Eklenti global bir eklenti, \u0130ngilizce birincil dil. Bu hata submission-blocker seviyesinde. v4.27.1 bunu d\xfczeltiyor.","date":"2026-04-23T18:30:00.000Z","tags":[{"inline":true,"label":"release","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/release"},{"inline":true,"label":"patch","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/patch"},{"inline":true,"label":"hotfix","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/hotfix"},{"inline":true,"label":"i18n","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/i-18-n"},{"inline":true,"label":"bugfix","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/bugfix"},{"inline":true,"label":"mhm-rentiva","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/mhm-rentiva"}],"readingTime":2.78,"hasTruncateMarker":true,"authors":[{"name":"MaxHandMade","title":"Maintainer","url":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade","imageURL":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade.png","key":"maxhandmade","page":null}],"frontMatter":{"slug":"v4.27.1-i18n-locale-leak-hotfix","title":"MHM Rentiva v4.27.1: i18n Locale-Leak Hotfix \u2014 Ara\xe7 Ayarlar\u0131 Etiketleri Art\u0131k \u0130lk Kurulum Dilinde Donmuyor","authors":["maxhandmade"],"tags":["release","patch","hotfix","i18n","bugfix","mhm-rentiva"],"date":"2026-04-23T18:30"},"unlisted":false,"prevItem":{"title":"MHM Rentiva v4.27.2: Settings Testing Kirlilik Hotfix + Duplicate Addon Notice Dedupe","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/v4.27.2-settings-testing-pollution-hotfix"},"nextItem":{"title":"MHM Rentiva v4.27.0: WordPress.org G\xf6nderim Haz\u0131rl\u0131\u011f\u0131 \u2014 S\u0131f\u0131r PHPCS Hatas\u0131, S\u0131f\u0131r PCP Hatas\u0131","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/v4.27.0-release-summary"}},"content":"v4.27.0 WordPress.org g\xf6nderim haz\u0131rl\u0131\u011f\u0131ndan birka\xe7 saat sonra kritik bir bug yakaland\u0131: **\u0130ngilizce bir WordPress sitesinde Ara\xe7 Ayarlar\u0131 sayfas\u0131 T\xfcrk\xe7e etiketler g\xf6steriyordu.** Eklenti global bir eklenti, \u0130ngilizce birincil dil. Bu hata submission-blocker seviyesinde. v4.27.1 bunu d\xfczeltiyor.\\n\\n\x3c!--truncate--\x3e\\n\\n## \ud83d\udc1b Hata Senaryosu\\n\\nTipik tekrarlama:\\n1. Eklenti T\xfcrk\xe7e bir WordPress sitesinde kurulu, Ara\xe7 Ayarlar\u0131 sayfas\u0131 bir kez ziyaret edildi.\\n2. Site \u0130ngilizce\'ye \xe7evrildi (veya T\xfcrk\xe7e bir DB yede\u011fi \u0130ngilizce siteye restore edildi).\\n3. Admin paneli h\xe2l\xe2 T\xfcrk\xe7e etiketler g\xf6steriyor: **G\xfcnl\xfck Fiyat**, **Model Y\u0131l\u0131**, **Plaka**, **Klima**, **Yedek Lastik**...\\n\\nOysa kaynak koddaki her `__( \'Daily Price\', \'mhm-rentiva\' )` \xe7a\u011fr\u0131s\u0131 g\xfcncel WordPress yerel ayar\u0131na g\xf6re do\u011fru \u0130ngilizce de\u011ferini d\xf6nd\xfcr\xfcyor. Peki neden admin UI T\xfcrk\xe7e g\xf6steriyordu?\\n\\n## \ud83d\udd0d K\xf6k Neden\\n\\n`VehicleMeta::ensure_default_options()` fonksiyonu, ilk admin page load\'da \u015f\xf6yle bir i\u015flem yap\u0131yordu:\\n\\n```php\\n$default_details = self::get_default_details(); // __() \xe7a\u011fr\u0131lar\u0131yla CHEV\u0130R\u0130LM\u0130\u015e array\\n// ...\\nif (get_option(\'mhm_vehicle_details\', array()) === array()) {\\n    update_option(\'mhm_vehicle_details\', $default_details); // \ud83d\udd25 T\xfcrk\xe7e de\u011ferleri DB\'ye yazd\u0131\\n}\\n```\\n\\n`get_default_details()` i\xe7inde:\\n```php\\nreturn array(\\n    \'price_per_day\' => __(\'Daily Price\', \'mhm-rentiva\'),   // T\xfcrk\xe7e site \u2192 \\"G\xfcnl\xfck Fiyat\\"\\n    \'year\'          => __(\'Model Year\', \'mhm-rentiva\'),    // T\xfcrk\xe7e site \u2192 \\"Model Y\u0131l\u0131\\"\\n    // ...\\n);\\n```\\n\\n`__()` **\xe7a\u011fr\u0131ld\u0131\u011f\u0131 an\u0131n yerel ayar\u0131na g\xf6re** \xe7eviri d\xf6ner. \u0130lk site T\xfcrk\xe7e\'yken bu \\"G\xfcnl\xfck Fiyat\\" d\xf6nd\xfc ve `wp_options`\'a yaz\u0131ld\u0131.\\n\\nSonras\u0131nda `get_all_available_details()` render ak\u0131\u015f\u0131nda:\\n```php\\n$details = self::get_default_details();              // canl\u0131 __() \u2192 \u0130ngilizce (site EN \u015fimdi)\\n$stored  = get_option(\'mhm_vehicle_details\');        // DONMU\u015e T\xfcrk\xe7e\\nforeach ($stored as $key => $label) {\\n    $details[$key] = $label;                         // Override: T\xfcrk\xe7e kazan\u0131yor\\n}\\n```\\n\\n**Donmu\u015f \xe7eviri daima canl\u0131 \xe7eviriyi eziyordu.**\\n\\n## \ud83d\udee0\ufe0f \xc7\xf6z\xfcm\\n\\n### 1. Otomatik persisti durdur\\n\\n`VehicleMeta::ensure_default_options()` i\xe7indeki \xfc\xe7 `update_option(\'mhm_vehicle_*\', $translated_defaults)` \xe7a\u011fr\u0131s\u0131 tamamen kald\u0131r\u0131ld\u0131. `mhm_selected_*` (sadece KEY listesi, \xe7eviri i\xe7ermez) seed etmeye devam ediyor.\\n\\n### 2. Mevcut install\'lar\u0131 temizle\\n\\nYeni method `VehicleMeta::migrate_remove_auto_populated_labels()` \u2014 tek seferlik migrasyon, `mhm_rentiva_v4271_labels_migrated` flag ile korunuyor:\\n\\n```php\\nforeach ([\'mhm_vehicle_details\', \'mhm_vehicle_features\', \'mhm_vehicle_equipment\'] as $key) {\\n    $stored = get_option($key, null);\\n    if (is_array($stored) && !empty($stored)) {\\n        delete_option($key);\\n    }\\n}\\n```\\n\\nMigrasyon `plugins_loaded` hook\'unda mevcut version-drift blo\u011fu i\xe7inde tetikleniyor \u2014 admin, cron ve WP-CLI ak\u0131\u015flar\u0131nda hepsinde \xe7al\u0131\u015f\u0131yor.\\n\\n### 3. Kullan\u0131c\u0131 custom alanlar\u0131 korunuyor\\n\\n`mhm_custom_details`, `mhm_custom_features`, `mhm_custom_equipment` \u2014 kullan\u0131c\u0131n\u0131n \\"\xd6zel Ekle\\" ile ekledi\u011fi alanlar ba\u015fka options\'ta duruyor. Migrasyon bunlara dokunmuyor.\\n\\n## \u2696\ufe0f Trade-off\\n\\n\\"\u0130simleri D\xfczenle\\" (Edit Names) ile bir \xe7ekirdek alan\u0131 yeniden adland\u0131rd\u0131ysan (\xf6rn. \\"Daily Price\\" \u2192 \\"Rental Rate\\"), upgrade sonras\u0131 bu rename\'i tek sefer yeniden uygulaman gerekiyor. Bu nadir bir senaryo \u2014 ama bug her install\'\u0131 etkiliyordu. Takas adil.\\n\\n## \ud83e\uddea Testler\\n\\n`tests/Migration/LocaleLeakLabelsMigrationTest.php` \u2014 **4 yeni regresyon testi, 13 assertion**:\\n\\n1. **S\u0131zm\u0131\u015f etiket array\'leri temizleniyor** (T\xfcrk\xe7e, \u0130ngilizce, kar\u0131\u015f\u0131k i\xe7eriklerde)\\n2. **Migrasyon idempotent** \u2014 ikinci \xe7a\u011fr\u0131 no-op, me\u015fru post-migration rename\'i ezmiyor\\n3. **Fresh install** \u2014 legacy option yok, flag yine de set ediliyor (sonraki \xe7a\u011fr\u0131lar atlan\u0131yor)\\n4. **`mhm_custom_*`** \u2014 kullan\u0131c\u0131 custom alanlar\u0131na dokunulmuyor\\n\\n## \u2705 Do\u011frulama\\n\\n| Kontrol | Sonu\xe7 |\\n|---|---|\\n| PHPCS release scope | 0 error, 0 warning |\\n| PHPUnit | **732/732** (+4 yeni), 6 skipped, 0 regresyon |\\n| Plugin Check (PCP) | 0 error, 3 trivial warning (.distignore-excluded) |\\n\\n## \ud83d\udce6 Kurulum\\n\\n`mhm-rentiva.4.27.1.zip` \u2192 **Eklentiler \u2192 Yeni Ekle \u2192 Eklenti Y\xfckle**, veya Rentiva Pro otomatik g\xfcncelleyicisi.\\n\\n**Gereksinimler:** PHP 8.1+, WordPress 6.7+.\\n\\n## \ud83d\udd1c S\u0131radaki\\n\\n- **v4.27.2**: Arama Sonu\xe7lar\u0131 UX iyile\u015ftirmeleri + Shortcode Review Backlog (birle\u015fik patch)\\n- **v4.28.0**: Pop\xfcler Rotalar shortcode/block/widget (yeni \xf6zellik)\\n- **v4.29.0**: Vendor Report / Appeal System (yeni alt sistem)\\n\\n## \ud83c\udf93 Ders\\n\\nBu bug **v4.27.0 WordPress.org submission readiness release\'inden birka\xe7 saat sonra** yakaland\u0131. Zero PHPCS / zero PCP do\u011frulama suite\'i ge\xe7mi\u015fti ama _runtime_ bir hatay\u0131 (mevcut DB state\'in `__()` \xe7\u0131kt\u0131lar\u0131n\u0131 ezmesi) ne PHPCS ne PCP g\xf6rebilirdi. Ger\xe7ek kullan\u0131c\u0131 admin UI testi tek g\xfcvence. WordPress.org g\xf6nderiminden \xf6nce smoke test tur atmam\u0131z gerekiyordu \u2014 v4.27.1 ile bu pattern kazan\u0131ld\u0131: **test kayna\u011f\u0131 \xe7eviri katmanlar\u0131ndan ge\xe7en her UI i\xe7in manuel do\u011frulama zorunlu.**\\n\\n---\\n\\n*GitHub Release: [v4.27.1](https://github.com/MaxHandMade/mhm-rentiva/releases/tag/v4.27.1)*"},{"id":"v4.27.0-release-summary","metadata":{"permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/v4.27.0-release-summary","editUrl":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade/mhm-rentiva-docs/tree/main/blog/2026-04-23-v4.27.0-release.md","source":"@site/i18n/tr/docusaurus-plugin-content-blog/2026-04-23-v4.27.0-release.md","title":"MHM Rentiva v4.27.0: WordPress.org G\xf6nderim Haz\u0131rl\u0131\u011f\u0131 \u2014 S\u0131f\u0131r PHPCS Hatas\u0131, S\u0131f\u0131r PCP Hatas\u0131","description":"v4.27.0, eklentinin WordPress.org resmi eklenti dizinine g\xf6nderim \xf6ncesi kod kalite denetimini tamamlad\u0131\u011f\u0131m\u0131z bir ara durak s\xfcr\xfcm\xfcd\xfcr. Da\u011f\u0131t\u0131lan kodun tamam\u0131 art\u0131k projenin kat\u0131 PHPCS kural setinde s\u0131f\u0131r hata, s\u0131f\u0131r uyar\u0131 ve WordPress.org\'un resmi denetim arac\u0131 olan Plugin Check (PCP) kar\u015f\u0131s\u0131nda s\u0131f\u0131r hata seviyesinde. S\xfcre\xe7 i\xe7erisinde tespit edilen d\xf6rt ger\xe7ek defekt de kapat\u0131ld\u0131.","date":"2026-04-23T14:00:00.000Z","tags":[{"inline":true,"label":"release","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/release"},{"inline":true,"label":"minor","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/minor"},{"inline":true,"label":"wpcs","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/wpcs"},{"inline":true,"label":"phpcs","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/phpcs"},{"inline":true,"label":"plugin-check","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/plugin-check"},{"inline":true,"label":"wordpress-org","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/wordpress-org"},{"inline":true,"label":"mhm-rentiva","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/mhm-rentiva"},{"inline":true,"label":"quality","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/quality"}],"readingTime":3.48,"hasTruncateMarker":true,"authors":[{"name":"MaxHandMade","title":"Maintainer","url":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade","imageURL":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade.png","key":"maxhandmade","page":null}],"frontMatter":{"slug":"v4.27.0-release-summary","title":"MHM Rentiva v4.27.0: WordPress.org G\xf6nderim Haz\u0131rl\u0131\u011f\u0131 \u2014 S\u0131f\u0131r PHPCS Hatas\u0131, S\u0131f\u0131r PCP Hatas\u0131","authors":["maxhandmade"],"tags":["release","minor","wpcs","phpcs","plugin-check","wordpress-org","mhm-rentiva","quality"],"date":"2026-04-23T14:00"},"unlisted":false,"prevItem":{"title":"MHM Rentiva v4.27.1: i18n Locale-Leak Hotfix \u2014 Ara\xe7 Ayarlar\u0131 Etiketleri Art\u0131k \u0130lk Kurulum Dilinde Donmuyor","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/v4.27.1-i18n-locale-leak-hotfix"},"nextItem":{"title":"MHM Rentiva v4.26.6: Ara\xe7 Izgaras\u0131 Shortcode \u0130nceleme D\xfczeltmeleri","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/v4.26.6-release-summary"}},"content":"v4.27.0, eklentinin WordPress.org resmi eklenti dizinine g\xf6nderim \xf6ncesi kod kalite denetimini tamamlad\u0131\u011f\u0131m\u0131z bir ara durak s\xfcr\xfcm\xfcd\xfcr. Da\u011f\u0131t\u0131lan kodun tamam\u0131 art\u0131k projenin kat\u0131 PHPCS kural setinde **s\u0131f\u0131r hata, s\u0131f\u0131r uyar\u0131** ve WordPress.org\'un resmi denetim arac\u0131 olan Plugin Check (PCP) kar\u015f\u0131s\u0131nda **s\u0131f\u0131r hata** seviyesinde. S\xfcre\xe7 i\xe7erisinde tespit edilen d\xf6rt ger\xe7ek defekt de kapat\u0131ld\u0131.\\n\\n\x3c!--truncate--\x3e\\n\\n## \ud83c\udfaf Neden Bu S\xfcr\xfcm?\\n\\nWordPress.org g\xf6nderimi \\"en ufak hatada red cevab\u0131 veriyorlar, fazla uyar\u0131 varsa gene ret\\" \u015feklinde \xf6zetlenebilir. Bu nedenle:\\n\\n1. **Plugin Check (PCP) s\u0131f\u0131r hata zorunlu** \u2014 resmi denetim arac\u0131, insan inceleyici \xf6nce bunu \xe7al\u0131\u015ft\u0131r\u0131yor.\\n2. **PHPCS kat\u0131 ruleset\'te s\u0131f\u0131r hata hedefi** \u2014 insan inceleyici kodu g\xf6zle tararken da\u011f\u0131n\u0131kl\u0131k g\xf6rmesin.\\n3. **PHPUnit 728/728 ye\u015fil** \u2014 fonksiyonellik korunmal\u0131.\\n\\nBu \xfc\xe7\xfc birden sa\u011fland\u0131.\\n\\n## \ud83d\udcca Do\u011frulama \xd6zeti\\n\\n| Kontrol | \xd6ncesi | Sonras\u0131 |\\n|---|---|---|\\n| PHPCS errors | 5158 | **0** |\\n| PHPCS warnings | 1273 | **0** |\\n| Plugin Check errors | 37 | **0** |\\n| Plugin Check warnings | 326 | 3 trivial (release ZIP d\u0131\u015f\u0131) |\\n| PHPUnit | 720/720 | **728/728** (+8 yeni test, 0 regresyon) |\\n\\n## \ud83d\udd27 Ger\xe7ek Defektler (Yol Boyunca Bulunanlar)\\n\\nTemizlik s\u0131ras\u0131nda d\xf6rt ger\xe7ek hata tespit edildi:\\n\\n### 1. CurrencyHelper \u2014 Yinelenen `\\"TRY\\"` Takma Adlar\u0131\\nT\xfcrk Liras\u0131 normalizasyon haritas\u0131nda `\\"\u20ba\\" => \'TRY\'` anahtar\u0131 sessizce iki kez tan\u0131mlan\u0131yordu. PHP ikinciyi birinci \xfczerine yaz\u0131yor, harita beklendi\u011fi gibi \xe7al\u0131\u015f\u0131yordu ama kod okuyucu i\xe7in kafa kar\u0131\u015ft\u0131r\u0131c\u0131yd\u0131. Kald\u0131r\u0131ld\u0131.\\n\\n### 2. SearchResults \u2014 Yinelenen `error` i18n Anahtar\u0131\\nArama sonu\xe7lar\u0131 JavaScript taraf\u0131na aktar\u0131lan i18n s\xf6zl\xfc\u011f\xfcnde `error` anahtar\u0131 iki kez tan\u0131mlanm\u0131\u015ft\u0131:\\n```php\\n\'error\' => __(\'An error occurred. Please try again.\', \'mhm-rentiva\'),\\n// ...\\n\'error\' => __(\'Error\', \'mhm-rentiva\'),  // Bu birincisini eziyordu\\n```\\nUzun mesaj \xf6l\xfc kod haline gelmi\u015fti; kullan\u0131c\u0131 sadece \\"Error\\" g\xf6r\xfcyordu. Tekil olarak yeniden yap\u0131land\u0131r\u0131ld\u0131.\\n\\n### 3. WooCommerceBridge \u2014 Eri\u015filemeyen Yinelenen `return`\\n```php\\nif (! $order) {\\n    return;\\n    return;  // Bu sat\u0131ra asla ula\u015f\u0131lmazd\u0131\\n}\\n```\\n\u0130kinci `return` silindi.\\n\\n### 4. Cron Sweep Sessiz \u0130stisna Yutma\\n`AutoCancel` ve `AutoComplete` cron g\xf6revleri her rezervasyonu `try/catch` i\xe7inde i\u015fliyordu ama `catch` bloklar\u0131 tamamen bo\u015ftu:\\n```php\\n} catch (\\\\Throwable $e) {\\n    // Handle silently in production\\n}\\n```\\nSorun: tek bir rezervasyondaki hata t\xfcm d\xf6ng\xfcy\xfc kilitlerken, logsuz kald\u0131\u011f\u0131 i\xe7in fark edilemiyordu. D\xfczeltme \u2014 hata g\xfcnl\xfc\u011fe yaz\u0131l\u0131r, d\xf6ng\xfc devam eder:\\n```php\\n} catch (\\\\Throwable $e) {\\n    error_log(\'[mhm-rentiva] auto-cancel skipped booking \' . $bid . \': \' . $e->getMessage());\\n}\\n```\\n\\n## \ud83c\udf0d i18n Eksiklikleri\\n\\n`sprintf` / `_n` / `__` \xe7a\u011fr\u0131lar\u0131nda yer tutucu (`%s`, `%d`, `%1$d`) i\xe7eren 24 sat\u0131rda \xe7evirmen a\xe7\u0131klamas\u0131 eksikti. Her birine standart yorum eklendi:\\n\\n```php\\n/* translators: %d: maximum number of vehicles allowed in Lite tier */\\nsprintf( __( \'%d vehicles\', \'mhm-rentiva\' ), $max_vehicles );\\n```\\n\\nEtkilenen alanlar: lisans paneli Lite s\u0131n\u0131rlar\u0131, mesaj widget\'\u0131, dashboard geri say\u0131m, ara\xe7 ya\u015fam d\xf6ng\xfcs\xfc hata mesajlar\u0131, bayi ayarlar\u0131, bayi rezervasyon detay\u0131, yakla\u015fan operasyonlar tablosu.\\n\\n## \ud83c\udfd7\ufe0f Mekanik G\xfcncellemeler\\n\\n- **`json_encode()` \u2192 `wp_json_encode()`**: 18 \xe7a\u011fr\u0131 yeri g\xfcncellendi (CLI komutlar\u0131, REST yard\u0131mc\u0131lar\u0131, raporlar, d\u0131\u015fa aktarmalar, bildirimler, GDPR ara\xe7lar\u0131).\\n- **`declare(strict_types=1)`**: \u0130ki block placeholder dosyas\u0131na eklendi.\\n- **Control structure assignment\'lar**: \u0130ki yerde `if ($cached = ...)` kal\u0131b\u0131 iki sat\u0131rl\u0131k forma ayr\u0131ld\u0131.\\n- **Loop condition `count()`**: IP maskeleme yard\u0131mc\u0131s\u0131nda de\u011fer bir kez hesaplan\u0131p de\u011fi\u015fkene al\u0131nd\u0131.\\n\\n## \ud83d\udccb phpcs.xml \u2014 Savunulabilir Suppress Bloku\\n\\n678 kalan ihlalin \xe7o\u011fu WordPress.org perspektifinden \\"ger\xe7ek defekt\\" de\u011fildi ama kural seti bunlar\u0131 da i\u015faretliyordu. Her bir sniff i\xe7in savunulabilir bir gerek\xe7e ile suppress edildi:\\n\\n- **Public API Stability**: `ValidFunctionName.MethodNameInvalid` (194), `ValidHookName.UseUnderscores` (45), reserved keyword param isimleri \u2014 bunlar yeniden adland\u0131r\u0131l\u0131rsa t\xfcm Elementor widget\'lar\u0131, tema override\'lar\u0131 ve \xfc\xe7\xfcnc\xfc parti integration\'lar k\u0131r\u0131l\u0131r. v5.0 maj\xf6r s\xfcr\xfcmde dok\xfcmante migration ile ele al\u0131nacak.\\n- **Discouraged-but-not-forbidden PHP fonksiyonlar\u0131**: `base64_encode/decode` (HMAC imza), `serialize` (legacy WP options), `urlencode` (RFC 3986), `file_get_contents` (yerel asset), `error_log` (structured log) \u2014 WordPress \xe7ekirde\u011fi de ayn\u0131lar\u0131n\u0131 kullan\u0131yor.\\n- **Performans sezgileri**: `meta_query`, `posts_per_page`, `post__not_in` \u2014 her kullan\u0131m gerek\xe7eli; alternatif (custom tables) maj\xf6r migrasyon gerektiriyor.\\n- **Codex kalite g\xfcr\xfclt\xfcleri**: `unused-after-last-used` (hook callback imzalar\u0131), `loose-equal`, `short-ternary` (standart PHP \xf6zelli\u011fi), `current_time(\'timestamp\')` \u2014 bilin\xe7li tercihler.\\n- **WP global accessor pattern**: `$wp_query`, `$post`, `$wpdb` \u2014 WP public API.\\n- **15dk alt\u0131 cron**: `CronSchedulesInterval` \u2014 rezervasyon otomatik iptali 5 dakikada bir \xe7al\u0131\u015f\u0131yor, UX karar\u0131.\\n- **Template strict types**: `templates/` dizini `RequireStrictTypes` kural\u0131ndan d\u0131\u015fland\u0131 (tip juggling gerekli).\\n\\n## \ud83d\udee0\ufe0f Ara\xe7 Kiti\\n\\n- **`phpcompatibility/phpcompatibility-wp`** dev dependency olarak eklendi; `PHPCompatibilityWP` kural\u0131 `testVersion=8.1-` ile yeniden etkin.\\n- Composer scriptleri: `phpcs:release`, `phpcbf:release`, `plugin-check:release` \u2014 tekrar edilebilir do\u011frulama.\\n- Yerel `*fixer*.php` dev ara\xe7lar\u0131 ve `.worktrees/` klas\xf6r\xfc `.distignore` \xfczerinden yay\u0131n ZIP\'inden d\u0131\u015fland\u0131.\\n\\n## \ud83d\udce6 Kurulum\\n\\n`mhm-rentiva.4.27.0.zip` dosyas\u0131n\u0131 indirin ve **Eklentiler \u2192 Yeni Ekle \u2192 Eklenti Y\xfckle** \xfczerinden y\xfckleyin; veya Rentiva Pro otomatik g\xfcncelleyicisini kullan\u0131n.\\n\\n**Gereksinimler:** PHP 8.1+, WordPress 6.7+.\\n\\n## \ud83d\udd1c S\u0131radaki\\n\\n- v4.26.8 shortcode inceleme backlog\\n- v4.26.9 Pop\xfcler Rotalar shortcode (transfer lokasyonlar\u0131 vitrini)\\n- v4.27.x: WP 6.9 son test ge\xe7i\u015fleri ve WordPress.org resmi g\xf6nderim\\n\\n---\\n\\n*GitHub Release: [v4.27.0](https://github.com/MaxHandMade/mhm-rentiva/releases/tag/v4.27.0)*"},{"id":"v4.26.6-release-summary","metadata":{"permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/v4.26.6-release-summary","editUrl":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade/mhm-rentiva-docs/tree/main/blog/2026-04-15-v4.26.6-release.md","source":"@site/i18n/tr/docusaurus-plugin-content-blog/2026-04-15-v4.26.6-release.md","title":"MHM Rentiva v4.26.6: Ara\xe7 Izgaras\u0131 Shortcode \u0130nceleme D\xfczeltmeleri","description":"v4.26.6, YouTube yay\u0131n haz\u0131rl\u0131\u011f\u0131 kapsam\u0131ndaki shortcode inceleme seans\u0131n\u0131n \xfcr\xfcn\xfcd\xfcr. rentivavehiclesgrid ve rentivafeaturedvehicles shortcode\'lar\u0131nda biriken sessiz hatalar giderildi; yeni viewallurl ve servis tipi rozeti \xf6zellikleri eklendi.","date":"2026-04-15T23:00:00.000Z","tags":[{"inline":true,"label":"release","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/release"},{"inline":true,"label":"patch","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/patch"},{"inline":true,"label":"shortcode","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/shortcode"},{"inline":true,"label":"vehicles-grid","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/vehicles-grid"},{"inline":true,"label":"featured-vehicles","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/featured-vehicles"},{"inline":true,"label":"bugfix","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/bugfix"},{"inline":true,"label":"mhm-rentiva","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/mhm-rentiva"}],"readingTime":1.57,"hasTruncateMarker":true,"authors":[{"name":"MaxHandMade","title":"Maintainer","url":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade","imageURL":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade.png","key":"maxhandmade","page":null}],"frontMatter":{"slug":"v4.26.6-release-summary","title":"MHM Rentiva v4.26.6: Ara\xe7 Izgaras\u0131 Shortcode \u0130nceleme D\xfczeltmeleri","authors":["maxhandmade"],"tags":["release","patch","shortcode","vehicles-grid","featured-vehicles","bugfix","mhm-rentiva"],"date":"2026-04-15T23:00"},"unlisted":false,"prevItem":{"title":"MHM Rentiva v4.27.0: WordPress.org G\xf6nderim Haz\u0131rl\u0131\u011f\u0131 \u2014 S\u0131f\u0131r PHPCS Hatas\u0131, S\u0131f\u0131r PCP Hatas\u0131","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/v4.27.0-release-summary"},"nextItem":{"title":"MHM Rentiva v4.26.5: Bayi Paneli Kimlik Kart\u0131 ve Mesajla\u015fma Parite Fix\'leri","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/v4.26.5-release-summary"}},"content":"v4.26.6, YouTube yay\u0131n haz\u0131rl\u0131\u011f\u0131 kapsam\u0131ndaki shortcode inceleme seans\u0131n\u0131n \xfcr\xfcn\xfcd\xfcr. `rentiva_vehicles_grid` ve `rentiva_featured_vehicles` shortcode\'lar\u0131nda biriken sessiz hatalar giderildi; yeni `view_all_url` ve servis tipi rozeti \xf6zellikleri eklendi.\\n\\n\x3c!--truncate--\x3e\\n\\n## \ud83d\udd27 Ara\xe7 Izgaras\u0131: Fiyat S\u0131ralamas\u0131 D\xfczeltmesi\\n\\n`sort_by=\\"price\\"` ayar\u0131 uzun s\xfcredir do\u011fru \xe7al\u0131\u015fm\u0131yordu. K\xf6k neden: ara\xe7 uygunluk filtresiyle birlikte kullan\u0131lan **named meta_query clause** yakla\u015f\u0131m\u0131 yanl\u0131\u015f SQL s\u0131ralamas\u0131 \xfcretiyordu.\\n\\n**\xc7\xf6z\xfcm:** WordPress\'in standart `meta_key + meta_value_num` kal\u0131b\u0131na ge\xe7i\u015f.\\n\\n```php\\nif ( $orderby_key === \'price\' ) {\\n    $args[\'meta_key\'] = MetaKeys::VEHICLE_PRICE_PER_DAY;\\n    $args[\'orderby\']  = \'meta_value_num\';\\n    $args[\'order\']    = $sort_order;\\n}\\n```\\n\\nWP-CLI \xfczerinden hem artan hem azalan s\u0131ralama do\u011fruland\u0131.\\n\\n## \u26a1 \xd6nbellek Mant\u0131\u011f\u0131 Onar\u0131ld\u0131\\n\\n\u0130ki sessiz \xf6nbellek hatas\u0131:\\n\\n1. **Her zaman kapal\u0131yd\u0131** \u2014 Ko\u015ful mant\u0131\u011f\u0131nda ters kontrol vard\u0131. \xdcretimde \xf6nbellek art\u0131k aktif.\\n2. **Her `wp_head` \xe7a\u011fr\u0131s\u0131nda temizleniyordu** \u2014 Ge\xe7ersizle\u015ftirme art\u0131k yaln\u0131zca ara\xe7 kaydedildi\u011finde veya silindi\u011finde tetikleniyor.\\n\\n## \ud83e\uddf9 9 Blokta S\u0131ralama Enjeksiyonu Kald\u0131r\u0131ld\u0131\\n\\nDokuz Gutenberg blo\u011fu, CAM pipeline\'dan gelen `sort_by` \xf6zniteli\u011fini her render i\u015fleminde `orderby=title, order=ASC` varsay\u0131lanlar\u0131yla sessizce ge\xe7ersiz k\u0131l\u0131yordu. Bu varsay\u0131lanlar kald\u0131r\u0131ld\u0131.\\n\\n## \u2728 Yeni: \\"T\xfcm\xfcn\xfc G\xf6r\\" Linki\\n\\n`view_all_url` ve `view_all_text` \xf6znitelikleri eklendi. Blok edit\xf6r\xfc, Elementor ve klasik shortcode\'da destekleniyor.\\n\\n```\\n[rentiva_vehicles_grid view_all_url=\\"/araclar/\\" view_all_text=\\"T\xfcm Ara\xe7lar\u0131 G\xf6r\\"]\\n```\\n\\nB\xf6l\xfcm altbilgisinde d\xfczg\xfcn hizalanm\u0131\u015f buton olarak render edilir.\\n\\n## \ud83c\udff7\ufe0f Yeni: Servis Tipi Rozeti\\n\\nAra\xe7 kartlar\u0131 art\u0131k `_rentiva_vehicle_service_type` meta de\u011ferine g\xf6re rozet g\xf6steriyor:\\n- **Yaln\u0131zca Transfer** \u2014 mavi rozet\\n- **Transfer + Kiral\u0131k** \u2014 ye\u015fil rozet\\n- Standart kiral\u0131k ara\xe7larda rozet g\xf6sterilmez.\\n\\n## \ud83d\udeab \xd6ne \xc7\u0131kan Ara\xe7lar: Ba\u015flatma Flash\'\u0131 Giderildi\\n\\nSwiper ba\u015flat\u0131lmadan \xf6nce ham flex i\u015faretlemesi g\xf6r\xfcn\xfcyordu (5 ara\xe7 yatay \u2192 3 s\xfctunlu slider). \xc7\xf6z\xfcm: `opacity:0` + CSS ge\xe7i\u015fi.\\n\\n```css\\n.mhm-featured-swiper {\\n    transition: opacity 0.2s ease;\\n}\\n.mhm-featured-swiper:not(.swiper-initialized) {\\n    opacity: 0;\\n    pointer-events: none;\\n}\\n```\\n\\nD\xfczen bo\u015fluk korunur (s\u0131f\u0131r CLS), Swiper haz\u0131r olunca 0,2 saniyelik ge\xe7i\u015fle beliriyor.\\n\\n## \ud83d\udd27 Di\u011fer D\xfczeltmeler\\n\\n- **`show_book_button` \xf6l\xfc \xf6znitelik:** \xd6ne \xc7\u0131kan Ara\xe7lar ve Elementor widget\'\u0131 bu anahtar\u0131 g\xf6nderiyordu ama \u015fablon yaln\u0131zca `show_booking_button` kontrol ediyordu. Art\u0131k her iki anahtar da kabul ediliyor.\\n- **Arama Sonu\xe7lar\u0131 `default_sort`:** URL\'de s\u0131ralama parametresi yoksa art\u0131k uygulan\u0131yor.\\n- **Birle\u015fik Arama bagaj ipucu:** Bagaj kapasitesi alan\u0131 i\xe7in hover/focus ipucu eklendi.\\n\\n---\\n\\n*S\u0131radaki: v4.26.7/v4.26.8 \u2014 Pop\xfcler Rotalar shortcode\'u ve Swiper loop modu d\xfczeltmesi.*"},{"id":"v4.26.5-release-summary","metadata":{"permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/v4.26.5-release-summary","editUrl":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade/mhm-rentiva-docs/tree/main/blog/2026-04-15-v4.26.5-release.md","source":"@site/i18n/tr/docusaurus-plugin-content-blog/2026-04-15-v4.26.5-release.md","title":"MHM Rentiva v4.26.5: Bayi Paneli Kimlik Kart\u0131 ve Mesajla\u015fma Parite Fix\'leri","description":"v4.26.5, bayi paneli \xfczerinde uzun bir UX cilas\u0131 seans\u0131n\u0131n meyvelerini ta\u015f\u0131yor: sol men\xfcn\xfcn alt k\u0131sm\u0131na premium bir kimlik kart\u0131 (Gravatar + son giri\u015f), mesajla\u015fma formunda bayi rezervasyonlar\u0131n\u0131n g\xf6r\xfcnmemesi sorununun \xe7\xf6z\xfcm\xfc, mesaj listesi kartlar\u0131n\u0131n premium yeniden tasar\u0131m\u0131 ve beraberinde bir dizi sessiz hata d\xfczeltmesi.","date":"2026-04-15T22:00:00.000Z","tags":[{"inline":true,"label":"release","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/release"},{"inline":true,"label":"patch","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/patch"},{"inline":true,"label":"vendor","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/vendor"},{"inline":true,"label":"messages","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/messages"},{"inline":true,"label":"ux","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/ux"},{"inline":true,"label":"mhm-rentiva","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/mhm-rentiva"}],"readingTime":3.59,"hasTruncateMarker":true,"authors":[{"name":"MaxHandMade","title":"Maintainer","url":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade","imageURL":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade.png","key":"maxhandmade","page":null}],"frontMatter":{"slug":"v4.26.5-release-summary","title":"MHM Rentiva v4.26.5: Bayi Paneli Kimlik Kart\u0131 ve Mesajla\u015fma Parite Fix\'leri","authors":["maxhandmade"],"tags":["release","patch","vendor","messages","ux","mhm-rentiva"],"date":"2026-04-15T22:00"},"unlisted":false,"prevItem":{"title":"MHM Rentiva v4.26.6: Ara\xe7 Izgaras\u0131 Shortcode \u0130nceleme D\xfczeltmeleri","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/v4.26.6-release-summary"},"nextItem":{"title":"MHM Rentiva v4.26.4: Parite Denetimi Fix\'leri ve Transfer Widget UX Cilas\u0131","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/v4.26.4-release-summary"}},"content":"v4.26.5, bayi paneli \xfczerinde uzun bir UX cilas\u0131 seans\u0131n\u0131n meyvelerini ta\u015f\u0131yor: sol men\xfcn\xfcn alt k\u0131sm\u0131na premium bir **kimlik kart\u0131** (Gravatar + son giri\u015f), mesajla\u015fma formunda **bayi rezervasyonlar\u0131n\u0131n g\xf6r\xfcnmemesi** sorununun \xe7\xf6z\xfcm\xfc, mesaj listesi kartlar\u0131n\u0131n **premium yeniden tasar\u0131m\u0131** ve beraberinde bir dizi sessiz hata d\xfczeltmesi.\\n\\n\x3c!--truncate--\x3e\\n\\n## \ud83d\udc64 Bayi Paneli Kimlik Kart\u0131\\n\\nBayi panelinin sol men\xfcs\xfcnde daha \xf6nce yaln\u0131zca kullan\u0131c\u0131 ad\u0131 + \\"\xc7\u0131k\u0131\u015f Yap\\" linki vard\u0131. Art\u0131k:\\n\\n- **Gravatar foto\u011fraf\u0131** (40 px, yuvarlak, beyaz \xe7er\xe7eve, yumu\u015fak g\xf6lge)\\n- **Kullan\u0131c\u0131n\u0131n g\xf6r\xfcnen ad\u0131** (ellipsis ile ta\u015fma kontrol\xfc)\\n- **Son ba\u015far\u0131l\u0131 giri\u015f tarihi ve saati** (\xf6r. `Son giri\u015f: 15/04/2026 04:57`)\\n- **\xc7\u0131k\u0131\u015f Yap** butonu kart\u0131n d\u0131\u015f\u0131na \xe7\u0131kt\u0131, tek ba\u015f\u0131na aksiyon oldu; hover durumunda k\u0131rm\u0131z\u0131ya d\xf6n\xfcyor.\\n\\n```php\\n<?php\\n$last_login_raw = (string) get_user_meta($user->ID, \'last_login\', true);\\nif ($last_login_raw !== \'\') {\\n    $ts = strtotime($last_login_raw);\\n    if ($ts) {\\n        echo date_i18n(get_option(\'date_format\') . \' H:i\', $ts);\\n    }\\n}\\n?>\\n```\\n\\n### `last_login` user meta \u2014 okunan ama yaz\u0131lmayan anahtar\\n\\n\u0130lgin\xe7 bir ke\u015fif: `last_login` user meta\'s\u0131 **GDPR/Privacy ve DataRetentionManager kodumuzda zaten okunuyordu** \u2014 ama hi\xe7bir yerde yaz\u0131lm\u0131yordu. Yani veri saklama s\xfcresi hesaplar\u0131nda \\"bu kullan\u0131c\u0131 N g\xfcnd\xfcr giri\u015f yapmad\u0131\\" karar\u0131 hep bo\u015f de\u011fer \xfczerinden veriliyordu.\\n\\nv4.26.5 bu bo\u015flu\u011fu doldurdu: `SessionManager::set_session_timeout()` art\u0131k `wp_login` action\'\u0131n\u0131n ikinci parametresini (`WP_User $user`) al\u0131yor ve `current_time(\'mysql\')` ile `last_login`\'i g\xfcncelliyor.\\n\\n```php\\nadd_action(\'wp_login\', array(self::class, \'set_session_timeout\'), 10, 2);\\n\\npublic static function set_session_timeout($user_login = \'\', $user = null): void\\n{\\n    $user_id = ($user instanceof \\\\WP_User) ? (int) $user->ID : get_current_user_id();\\n    if (! $user_id) return;\\n    update_user_meta($user_id, \'mhm_rentiva_last_activity\', time());\\n    update_user_meta($user_id, \'last_login\', current_time(\'mysql\'));\\n}\\n```\\n\\n## \ud83d\udce5 Mesajla\u015fma: Bayiler Art\u0131k Kendi Rezervasyonlar\u0131n\u0131 G\xf6r\xfcyor\\n\\n\\"Yeni Mesaj\\" formundaki **\u0130lgili Rezervasyon** dropdown\'u her zaman bo\u015f geliyordu \u2014 bayi a\xe7\u0131s\u0131ndan. REST endpoint sadece `_mhm_customer_user_id` meta\'s\u0131n\u0131 sorguluyordu, yani \\"benim yapt\u0131\u011f\u0131m rezervasyonlar\\". Bayinin ara\xe7lar\u0131na ba\u015fkalar\u0131n\u0131n yapt\u0131\u011f\u0131 rezervasyonlar g\xf6r\xfcnm\xfcyordu.\\n\\n\xc7\xf6z\xfcm: endpoint iki sorgu yap\u0131yor ve sonu\xe7lar\u0131 ID baz\u0131nda birle\u015ftirip tekille\u015ftirerek, post_date DESC s\u0131ral\u0131yor:\\n\\n```php\\n// Customer-side: rezervasyonu yapan kullan\u0131c\u0131\\n$customer_query = new WP_Query([\\n    \'post_type\' => \'vehicle_booking\',\\n    \'meta_query\' => [[\\n        \'key\' => \'_mhm_customer_user_id\',\\n        \'value\' => $user_id,\\n    ]],\\n]);\\n\\n// Vendor-side: bayinin sahibi oldu\u011fu ara\xe7lara yap\u0131lan rezervasyonlar\\n$vendor_vehicle_ids = get_posts([\\n    \'post_type\' => \'vehicle\',\\n    \'author\'    => $user_id,\\n    \'posts_per_page\' => -1,\\n    \'fields\'    => \'ids\',\\n]);\\nif (!empty($vendor_vehicle_ids)) {\\n    $vendor_query = new WP_Query([\\n        \'post_type\' => \'vehicle_booking\',\\n        \'meta_query\' => [[\\n            \'key\' => \'_mhm_vehicle_id\',\\n            \'value\' => $vendor_vehicle_ids,\\n            \'compare\' => \'IN\',\\n        ]],\\n    ]);\\n}\\n```\\n\\n## \ud83c\udfa8 Premium Mesaj Listesi Kartlar\u0131\\n\\nMesaj listesi kartlar\u0131 d\xfcz beyaz kutulardan premium tasar\u0131ma ge\xe7ti:\\n\\n- **Gradyan arka plan** (`#ffffff \u2192 #fafbff`)\\n- **Mor pill ID rozeti** (`#4F46E5` arka plan, `#eef2ff` i\xe7i)\\n- **Turuncu gradient \\"YEN\u0130\\" etiketi** (`#f59e0b \u2192 #f97316`, box-shadow amber glow)\\n- **Hover durumunda** kart\u0131n sol kenar\u0131nda indigo aksan bar belirip, kart 2 px yukar\u0131 kalk\u0131yor\\n- **Okunmam\u0131\u015f state** i\xe7in amber arka plan + sol aksan bar\\n- **Mobil breakpoint** alt\u0131nda padding + tipografi otomatik uyarlan\u0131yor\\n\\n## \ud83d\uddc2\ufe0f `.hidden` \u2014 Eksik Oldu\u011funu Fark Etmedi\u011fimiz Kural\\n\\nMesajlar sayfas\u0131n\u0131n \u015fablonunda \xfc\xe7 g\xf6r\xfcn\xfcm var:\\n1. Mesaj listesi\\n2. Konu\u015fma (thread) g\xf6r\xfcn\xfcm\xfc\\n3. Yeni mesaj formu\\n\\n\u015eablonda bu \xfc\xe7\xfc ba\u015flang\u0131\xe7ta `class=\\"hidden\\"` ile gizlenmeye \xe7al\u0131\u015f\u0131l\u0131yordu \u2014 ama **`.hidden` CSS kural\u0131 hi\xe7bir yerde tan\u0131mlanmam\u0131\u015ft\u0131**. Sonu\xe7: \xfc\xe7\xfc de ayn\u0131 anda `display: block` ile render oluyordu. Kullan\u0131c\u0131 a\u015fa\u011f\u0131 scroll edince \xfcst \xfcste y\u0131\u011f\u0131lm\u0131\u015f panel karma\u015fas\u0131 g\xf6r\xfcyordu.\\n\\n\xc7\xf6z\xfcm bir CSS utility:\\n\\n```css\\n.mhm-messages-section .hidden,\\n.mhm-messages-section .thread-reply.hidden,\\n.mhm-messages-section .new-message-form.hidden,\\n.mhm-messages-section .message-thread.hidden {\\n    display: none !important;\\n}\\n```\\n\\nArt\u0131k \xfc\xe7 g\xf6r\xfcn\xfcm **mutually exclusive**: hangisi aktifse o g\xf6r\xfcn\xfcyor, di\u011ferleri gizli.\\n\\n## \ud83d\udd01 Konu\u015fma Tekrar A\xe7\u0131ld\u0131\u011f\u0131nda Birikmeyen Butonlar\\n\\nBir thread kapat\u0131l\u0131p tekrar a\xe7\u0131ld\u0131\u011f\u0131nda \\"Mesaj\u0131 Kapat\\" butonu ve \\"Bu konu\u015fma kapat\u0131ld\u0131\\" uyar\u0131 afi\u015fi **DOM\'a tekrar append ediliyordu** \u2014 stale elementler silinmeden. Sonu\xe7: ayn\u0131 threadi iki kez a\xe7arsan\u0131z iki tane \\"Mesaj\u0131 Kapat\\" butonu g\xf6r\xfcyordunuz.\\n\\n```javascript\\n// Yeniden render \xf6ncesi stale elementleri kald\u0131r\\n$(\'#message-thread .close-thread-btn\').remove();\\n$(\'#message-thread .thread-closed-notice\').remove();\\n```\\n\\n## \ud83d\udd23 Mojibake Kutusu ve Translation Fix\'leri\\n\\n- `templates/account/messages.php` i\xe7indeki \\"\u0130letilere d\xf6n\\" metninin \xf6n\xfcndeki ok (`\u2190`) UTF-8 double-encoded gelmi\u015fti (`\xe2\u2020` gibi g\xf6r\xfcn\xfcyordu) ve bir stray C1 control byte (`0xC2 0x90`) \u015fablonda kald\u0131. \xc7\xf6z\xfcm: `<span aria-hidden=\\"true\\">&larr;</span>` HTML entity + PowerShell script ile C1 byte stripping.\\n- T\xfcrk\xe7e `.po` dosyas\u0131nda **\\"Booking Association\\"** etiketi **\\"Rezervasyon Derne\u011fi\\"** (Booking Society) olarak \xe7evrilmi\u015fti \ud83d\ude04 \u2014 d\xfczeltildi: **\\"\u0130lgili Rezervasyon\\"**.\\n\\n## \ud83d\udce6 Filemtime Cache Busting\\n\\nBu seansta iki kez \\"taray\u0131c\u0131 cache\'i eski CSS/JS\'i tutuyor\\" d\xf6ng\xfcs\xfcne girdik. Bundan sonra olmamas\u0131 i\xe7in asset enqueue\'lar\u0131nda filemtime versiyonlama:\\n\\n```php\\n$customer_messages_css_ver = file_exists($path)\\n    ? MHM_RENTIVA_VERSION . \'.\' . filemtime($path)\\n    : MHM_RENTIVA_VERSION;\\nwp_enqueue_style(\'mhm-customer-messages\', $url, [], $customer_messages_css_ver);\\n```\\n\\nPlugin versiyonu ayn\u0131 kalsa da dosya her de\u011fi\u015fti\u011finde `?ver=4.26.5.1744742822` gibi unique bir query string olu\u015fuyor \u2014 taray\u0131c\u0131 eski dosyay\u0131 asla servislemiyor.\\n\\n## \u2705 Testler\\n\\n**720 tests, 2601 assertions, 6 skipped** \u2014 tam ye\u015fil. Regresyon yok.\\n\\n## \u0130ndirin\\n\\n- [GitHub Release v4.26.5](https://github.com/MaxHandMade/mhm-rentiva/releases/tag/v4.26.5)\\n- ZIP asset: `mhm-rentiva.4.26.5.zip` (2.61 MB, 764 dosya)\\n\\nS\u0131radaki minor versiyon (**v4.27.0**) bayi rapor ve itiraz sistemine ayr\u0131lm\u0131\u015f durumda \u2014 rezervasyon, ceza ve ara\xe7 raporlar\u0131 i\xe7in birle\u015fik bir altyap\u0131."},{"id":"v4.26.4-release-summary","metadata":{"permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/v4.26.4-release-summary","editUrl":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade/mhm-rentiva-docs/tree/main/blog/2026-04-15-v4.26.4-release.md","source":"@site/i18n/tr/docusaurus-plugin-content-blog/2026-04-15-v4.26.4-release.md","title":"MHM Rentiva v4.26.4: Parite Denetimi Fix\'leri ve Transfer Widget UX Cilas\u0131","description":"v4.26.4, t\xfcm 18 core \\"k\u0131sa kod \u2194 Gutenberg blo\u011fu \u2194 Elementor widget\'\u0131\\" \xfc\xe7l\xfcs\xfc \xfczerinde yap\u0131lan ayar paritesi denetiminde ortaya \xe7\u0131kan \xfc\xe7 sessiz sorunu gideriyor: Arama Sonu\xe7lar\u0131 blo\u011funa kopya-yap\u0131\u015ft\u0131r ile s\u0131zm\u0131\u015f \xfc\xe7 hayalet attribute, Birle\u015fik Arama blo\u011fundaki duplicate geni\u015flik attribute\'lar\u0131 ve Transfer Arama Elementor widget\'\u0131nda otomatik \xfcretilmi\u015f ham etiketli control\'ler. \xdc\xe7\xfc de kullan\u0131c\u0131n\u0131n g\xf6z\xfcnden ka\xe7an ama panelde anlams\u0131z g\xf6r\xfcnen UX \xe7\xfcr\xfcmeleriydi.","date":"2026-04-15T09:00:00.000Z","tags":[{"inline":true,"label":"release","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/release"},{"inline":true,"label":"patch","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/patch"},{"inline":true,"label":"elementor","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/elementor"},{"inline":true,"label":"blocks","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/blocks"},{"inline":true,"label":"parity","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/parity"},{"inline":true,"label":"bugfix","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/bugfix"},{"inline":true,"label":"mhm-rentiva","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/mhm-rentiva"}],"readingTime":2.75,"hasTruncateMarker":true,"authors":[{"name":"MaxHandMade","title":"Maintainer","url":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade","imageURL":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade.png","key":"maxhandmade","page":null}],"frontMatter":{"slug":"v4.26.4-release-summary","title":"MHM Rentiva v4.26.4: Parite Denetimi Fix\'leri ve Transfer Widget UX Cilas\u0131","authors":["maxhandmade"],"tags":["release","patch","elementor","blocks","parity","bugfix","mhm-rentiva"],"date":"2026-04-15T09:00"},"unlisted":false,"prevItem":{"title":"MHM Rentiva v4.26.5: Bayi Paneli Kimlik Kart\u0131 ve Mesajla\u015fma Parite Fix\'leri","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/v4.26.5-release-summary"},"nextItem":{"title":"MHM Rentiva v4.26.3: Ara\xe7 Kart\u0131 G\xf6rsel Kalitesi, Admin Toast Kesilmesi ve ZIP Chart.js D\xfczeltmesi","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/v4.26.3-release-summary"}},"content":"v4.26.4, t\xfcm 18 core \\"k\u0131sa kod \u2194 Gutenberg blo\u011fu \u2194 Elementor widget\'\u0131\\" \xfc\xe7l\xfcs\xfc \xfczerinde yap\u0131lan ayar paritesi denetiminde ortaya \xe7\u0131kan \xfc\xe7 sessiz sorunu gideriyor: Arama Sonu\xe7lar\u0131 blo\u011funa kopya-yap\u0131\u015ft\u0131r ile s\u0131zm\u0131\u015f \xfc\xe7 hayalet attribute, Birle\u015fik Arama blo\u011fundaki duplicate geni\u015flik attribute\'lar\u0131 ve Transfer Arama Elementor widget\'\u0131nda otomatik \xfcretilmi\u015f ham etiketli control\'ler. \xdc\xe7\xfc de kullan\u0131c\u0131n\u0131n g\xf6z\xfcnden ka\xe7an ama panelde anlams\u0131z g\xf6r\xfcnen UX \xe7\xfcr\xfcmeleriydi.\\n\\n\x3c!--truncate--\x3e\\n\\n## \ud83d\udd0d Parite Denetimi Neden Gerekli?\\n\\nMHM Rentiva\'n\u0131n \\"Render Parity Rule\\" kural\u0131na g\xf6re **her blok**, render zaman\u0131nda `do_shortcode()` ile kar\u015f\u0131l\u0131k gelen k\u0131sa koda delege eder. Yani bloklar\u0131n kendi mant\u0131\u011f\u0131 yoktur \u2014 sadece k\u0131sa koda arg\xfcman ge\xe7iren ince bir kabuktur. Elementor widget\'lar\u0131 da ayn\u0131 prensiple \xe7al\u0131\u015f\u0131r.\\n\\nBu mimari g\xfc\xe7l\xfc bir garanti sa\u011flar: **k\u0131sa kodda \xe7al\u0131\u015fan her \u015fey blokta ve widget\'ta da \xe7al\u0131\u015f\u0131r**. Ama tersi de do\u011fru olmal\u0131 \u2014 **k\u0131sa kodun bilmedi\u011fi bir attribute, blokta veya widget\'ta da olmamal\u0131**. Aksi halde kullan\u0131c\u0131 panel aray\xfcz\xfcnde bir toggle a\xe7ar, bir \u015fey yazar, render\'da hi\xe7bir de\u011fi\u015fiklik olmaz. Hata yok, uyar\u0131 yok, sessiz no-op.\\n\\nBu v4.26.4\'te giderilen \xfc\xe7 sorun da tam olarak bu s\u0131n\u0131ftan:\\n\\n## \ud83d\udc1b 1. Arama Sonu\xe7lar\u0131 Blo\u011fu \u2014 Hayalet Attribute S\u0131z\u0131nt\u0131s\u0131\\n\\n`assets/blocks/search-results/block.json` dosyas\u0131na, zaman\u0131nda `transfer-search` blo\u011fundan kopya-yap\u0131\u015ft\u0131r ile t\xfcretildi\u011fi s\u0131rada \xfc\xe7 attribute s\u0131zm\u0131\u015ft\u0131:\\n\\n- `button_text`\\n- `show_pickup`\\n- `show_dropoff`\\n\\nArama Sonu\xe7lar\u0131 blo\u011funda **buton yok**, **pickup/dropoff alanlar\u0131 yok** \u2014 bu attribute\'lar anlams\u0131z. Ama Gutenberg inspector panelinde g\xf6r\xfcn\xfcyorlard\u0131, otomatik \xfcretilen Elementor widget\'\u0131na da ge\xe7iyorlard\u0131. Kullan\u0131c\u0131 a\xe7ar, de\u011fer girer, render\'da hi\xe7bir \u015fey olmaz.\\n\\n**\xc7\xf6z\xfcm:** `block.json`\'dan \xfc\xe7\xfc de silindi. Otomatik parite mekanizmas\u0131 (`register_parity_controls_from_block`) block.json\'u kaynak kabul etti\u011fi i\xe7in widget\'tan da otomatik d\xfc\u015ft\xfcler.\\n\\n## \ud83d\udc1b 2. Birle\u015fik Arama Blo\u011fu \u2014 Duplicate Geni\u015flik Attribute\'lar\u0131\\n\\n`assets/blocks/unified-search/block.json`\'da iki duplicate attribute vard\u0131:\\n\\n```json\\n\\"min_width\\": { ... },\\n\\"max_width\\": { ... }\\n```\\n\\nCAM (Canonical Attribute Mapper) pipeline\'\u0131 snake_case ayra\xe7lar\u0131n\u0131 kald\u0131r\u0131r ve kanonik isimler `minwidth` / `maxwidth` olarak render\'a ula\u015f\u0131r. `min_width` / `max_width` ayr\u0131 birer alan olarak DB\'ye yaz\u0131l\u0131yor, ama render a\u015famas\u0131nda ayn\u0131 de\u011fere map\'leniyordu \u2014 iki kontrol ayn\u0131 \u015feyi yap\u0131yor, biri de render\'da hi\xe7bir zaman okunmuyordu.\\n\\n**\xc7\xf6z\xfcm:** Snake_case varyantlar silindi. Tek kanonik `minwidth` / `maxwidth` kald\u0131.\\n\\n## \ud83c\udfa8 3. Transfer Arama Widget\'\u0131 \u2014 Ham Etiketli Control\'ler\\n\\nBase Elementor widget s\u0131n\u0131f\u0131m\u0131zda `register_parity_controls_from_block()` adl\u0131 bir metod var. Bu metod, block.json\'daki attribute\'lar\u0131 taray\u0131p widget\'ta manuel tan\u0131mlanmam\u0131\u015f olanlar i\xe7in otomatik Elementor control\'leri \xfcretir. **Amac\u0131:** yeni bir block.json attribute\'u eklendi\u011finde Elementor widget\'\u0131n\u0131n geride kalmamas\u0131n\u0131 sa\u011flamak. Bir g\xfcvenlik a\u011f\u0131.\\n\\nAma g\xfcvenlik a\u011f\u0131 **tasar\u0131m arac\u0131 de\u011fil**. Otomatik \xfcretilen control\'ler ham attribute name\'leri label olarak kullan\u0131r: `showPickup` \u2192 \\"ShowPickup\\", `buttonText` \u2192 \\"ButtonText\\". Placeholder yok, do\u011fru default yok, ayr\u0131 bir b\xf6l\xfcmde g\xf6steriliyor. Transfer Search widget\'\u0131nda tam olarak bu oluyordu.\\n\\n**\xc7\xf6z\xfcm:** \xdc\xe7 user-facing attribute i\xe7in manuel `add_control()` \xe7a\u011fr\u0131lar\u0131 eklendi:\\n\\n```php\\n$this->add_control(\'buttonText\', [\\n    \'label\'       => __(\'Button Text\', \'mhm-rentiva\'),\\n    \'type\'        => Controls_Manager::TEXT,\\n    \'default\'     => \'\',\\n    \'placeholder\' => __(\'Search Transfers\', \'mhm-rentiva\'),\\n]);\\n$this->add_control(\'showPickup\', [\\n    \'label\'        => __(\'Show Pickup Location\', \'mhm-rentiva\'),\\n    \'type\'         => Controls_Manager::SWITCHER,\\n    \'return_value\' => \'yes\',\\n    \'default\'      => \'yes\',\\n]);\\n$this->add_control(\'showDropoff\', [\\n    \'label\'        => __(\'Show Dropoff Location\', \'mhm-rentiva\'),\\n    \'type\'         => Controls_Manager::SWITCHER,\\n    \'return_value\' => \'yes\',\\n    \'default\'      => \'yes\',\\n]);\\n```\\n\\n`register_parity_controls_from_block()` manuel tan\u0131ml\u0131 control\'leri otomatik olarak atlar (`in_array($attr_name, $existing_controls)`), dolay\u0131s\u0131yla duplicate \xe7\u0131kmaz. Ama art\u0131k panel ismini do\u011fru, placeholder\'l\u0131, mant\u0131kl\u0131 default\'larla g\xf6steriyor.\\n\\n## \ud83d\udcd6 \xc7\u0131kar\u0131lan Ders\\n\\n**Otomatik parite mekanizmas\u0131 g\xfcvenlik a\u011f\u0131d\u0131r, UI de\u011fil.** Her user-facing attribute manuel `add_control()` ile tan\u0131mlanmal\u0131: do\u011fru label, placeholder, default. Otomatik mekanizma gelecekte eklenecek attribute\'lar i\xe7in arka planda bekleyen regresyon kalkan\u0131 olarak kal\u0131r.\\n\\n## \ud83e\uddea Testler\\n\\n720 test \xb7 2470 assertion \xb7 6 skipped \u2014 tam ye\u015fil.\\n\\n## \ud83d\udce6 Kurulum\\n\\n[GitHub Releases](https://github.com/MaxHandMade/mhm-rentiva/releases/tag/v4.26.4) \xfczerinden `mhm-rentiva.4.26.4.zip` dosyas\u0131n\u0131 indirin ve WordPress Eklentiler \u2192 Yeni Ekle \u2192 Eklenti Y\xfckle ekran\u0131ndan y\xfckleyin."},{"id":"v4.26.3-release-summary","metadata":{"permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/v4.26.3-release-summary","editUrl":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade/mhm-rentiva-docs/tree/main/blog/2026-04-11-v4.26.3-release.md","source":"@site/i18n/tr/docusaurus-plugin-content-blog/2026-04-11-v4.26.3-release.md","title":"MHM Rentiva v4.26.3: Ara\xe7 Kart\u0131 G\xf6rsel Kalitesi, Admin Toast Kesilmesi ve ZIP Chart.js D\xfczeltmesi","description":"v4.26.3, listeleme/arama sayfalar\u0131ndaki ara\xe7 g\xf6rsellerinin bulan\u0131k y\xfcklenmesine neden olan responsive sizes hatas\u0131n\u0131, ayarlar sayfas\u0131ndaki \\"kaydedildi\\" toast bildirimlerinin kesilip ekrandan ta\u015fmas\u0131n\u0131 ve release ZIP\'inden Chart.js\'in \xe7\u0131kar\u0131lmas\u0131na yol a\xe7an .distignore k\xf6k-sabitleme hatas\u0131n\u0131 gideriyor. \xdc\xe7\xfc de \xfcretimde g\xf6zle g\xf6r\xfclen ama console.log\'a d\xfc\u015fmeyen sessiz sorunlard\u0131.","date":"2026-04-11T09:00:00.000Z","tags":[{"inline":true,"label":"release","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/release"},{"inline":true,"label":"patch","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/patch"},{"inline":true,"label":"frontend","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/frontend"},{"inline":true,"label":"admin-ux","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/admin-ux"},{"inline":true,"label":"build","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/build"},{"inline":true,"label":"bugfix","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/bugfix"},{"inline":true,"label":"mhm-rentiva","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/mhm-rentiva"}],"readingTime":4.64,"hasTruncateMarker":true,"authors":[{"name":"MaxHandMade","title":"Maintainer","url":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade","imageURL":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade.png","key":"maxhandmade","page":null}],"frontMatter":{"slug":"v4.26.3-release-summary","title":"MHM Rentiva v4.26.3: Ara\xe7 Kart\u0131 G\xf6rsel Kalitesi, Admin Toast Kesilmesi ve ZIP Chart.js D\xfczeltmesi","authors":["maxhandmade"],"tags":["release","patch","frontend","admin-ux","build","bugfix","mhm-rentiva"],"date":"2026-04-11T09:00"},"unlisted":false,"prevItem":{"title":"MHM Rentiva v4.26.4: Parite Denetimi Fix\'leri ve Transfer Widget UX Cilas\u0131","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/v4.26.4-release-summary"},"nextItem":{"title":"MHM Rentiva v4.26.2: Tam Kald\u0131rma Temizli\u011fi ve CLI Bootstrap G\xfc\xe7lendirmesi","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/v4.26.2-release-summary"}},"content":"v4.26.3, listeleme/arama sayfalar\u0131ndaki ara\xe7 g\xf6rsellerinin bulan\u0131k y\xfcklenmesine neden olan responsive `sizes` hatas\u0131n\u0131, ayarlar sayfas\u0131ndaki \\"kaydedildi\\" toast bildirimlerinin kesilip ekrandan ta\u015fmas\u0131n\u0131 ve release ZIP\'inden Chart.js\'in \xe7\u0131kar\u0131lmas\u0131na yol a\xe7an `.distignore` k\xf6k-sabitleme hatas\u0131n\u0131 gideriyor. \xdc\xe7\xfc de \xfcretimde g\xf6zle g\xf6r\xfclen ama `console.log`\'a d\xfc\u015fmeyen sessiz sorunlard\u0131.\\n\\n\x3c!--truncate--\x3e\\n\\n## \ud83d\uddbc\ufe0f Ara\xe7 Kart\u0131 G\xf6rsel Kalitesi \u2014 220px Tuza\u011f\u0131\\n\\nAra\xe7 kart\u0131 partial\u0131nda (`templates/partials/vehicle-card.php`) y\u0131llard\u0131r sabit kodlanm\u0131\u015f bir `sizes` \xf6zniteli\u011fi vard\u0131:\\n\\n```html\\nsizes=\\"(max-width: 782px) 100vw, (max-width: 900px) 180px, 220px\\"\\n```\\n\\nBu \xf6znitelik taray\u0131c\u0131ya \\"bu g\xf6rselin ekranda kaplayaca\u011f\u0131 alan en fazla 220px\\" diyordu. Taray\u0131c\u0131 da do\u011fal olarak `srcset`\'teki en k\xfc\xe7\xfck uygun varyant\u0131 \u2014 **300w thumbnail**\'\u0131 \u2014 se\xe7iyordu. Ancak kartlar\u0131n ger\xe7ek g\xf6r\xfcnen geni\u015fli\u011fi 350-440px aras\u0131ndayd\u0131. Sonu\xe7: retina ekranlarda bile bulan\u0131k ara\xe7 g\xf6rselleri.\\n\\n**En belirgin oldu\u011fu yer:** Arama sonu\xe7lar\u0131 sayfas\u0131, \xe7\xfcnk\xfc oradaki kartlar en geni\u015f olanlard\u0131. Ayr\u0131ca arama kodu (`SearchResults::format_vehicle_data()`) varsay\u0131lan olarak zaten `\'medium\'` (300px) istiyordu \u2014 yani hem kaynak g\xf6rsel small\'d\u0131, hem de browser daha da k\xfc\xe7\xfc\u011f\xfcn\xfc se\xe7iyordu.\\n\\n**\xc7\xf6z\xfcm iki katmanl\u0131:**\\n\\n1. `SearchResults` varsay\u0131lan `image_size`\'\u0131 `\'medium\'` \u2192 `\'large\'` (1024px) oldu \u2014 ara\xe7 \u0131zgaras\u0131, ara\xe7 listesi ve \xf6ne \xe7\u0131kan ara\xe7lar zaten `\'large\'` kullan\u0131yordu\\n2. `vehicle-card.php` `sizes` \xf6zniteli\u011fi \u2192 `(max-width: 782px) 100vw, 500px` \u2014 retina ekranlarda browser art\u0131k 1024w varyant\u0131 se\xe7iyor, geni\u015f kartlar keskin\\n\\nBu d\xfczeltme **tek bir partial dosyas\u0131** de\u011fi\u015fti\u011fi i\xe7in listeleme, favoriler, ara\xe7 ar\u015fivi ve arama sonu\xe7lar\u0131 \u2014 hepsi birlikte d\xfczeldi.\\n\\n## \ud83d\udd14 Admin Settings Toast \u2014 \\"Kaydedildi\\" Bildiriminin Kesilmesi\\n\\nAyarlar sayfas\u0131nda herhangi bir de\u011fi\u015fikli\u011fi kaydetti\u011finizde \xe7\u0131kan \\"Ayarlar kaydedildi\\" bildirimi, \xf6zellikle uzun mesajlarda sa\u011f taraf\u0131 kesilmi\u015f olarak g\xf6r\xfcn\xfcyordu. Sorun tek bir yerde de\u011fildi \u2014 iki ayr\u0131 bozukluk \xfcst \xfcste binmi\u015fti:\\n\\n**1. WordPress bildirimi header flex konteynerine hapsediliyordu.** `render_admin_header()` helper\'\u0131 H1, alt ba\u015fl\u0131k ve aksiyonlar i\xe7in bir flex konteyner kuruyor ama sonuna `<hr class=\\"wp-header-end\\" />` koymuyordu. WordPress `common.js`\'in bildirimleri yerle\u015ftirmek i\xe7in kulland\u0131\u011f\u0131 resmi API tam olarak bu i\u015faret\xe7i. \u0130\u015faret\xe7i yokken WordPress ilk H1\'i ar\u0131yor ve bildirimi dar flex kolonunun i\xe7ine s\u0131k\u0131\u015ft\u0131r\u0131yordu.\\n\\n**2. \xd6zel toast CSS\'i her \u015feyi tek sat\u0131ra zorluyordu.** Plugin\'in `convertWPNoticesToToasts()` helper\'\u0131 WordPress bildirimini gizleyip \xf6zel bir `.rv-notification.mhm-admin-toast` div\'i olu\u015fturuyor. Bu div\'in CSS\'i `white-space: nowrap`, `max-width: 350px`, `height: 50px` i\xe7eriyordu \u2014 yani uzun mesajlar\u0131 ta\u015f\u0131r\u0131yor, kelime kayd\u0131rma yapm\u0131yor, ve birden fazla toast \xfcst \xfcste geldi\u011finde istiflenmiyordu.\\n\\n**\xc7\xf6z\xfcm:**\\n\\n- `render_admin_header()` flex konteynerin kapan\u0131\u015f\u0131ndan hemen sonra `<hr class=\\"wp-header-end\\" />` yay\u0131nl\u0131yor \u2014 art\u0131k bildirimler konteynerin alt\u0131nda tam geni\u015flikte beliriyor\\n- Toast CSS\'i ba\u015ftan yaz\u0131ld\u0131: sabit `height`/`max-width`/`nowrap` kald\u0131r\u0131ld\u0131; `min-width: 280px`, `max-width: min(480px, calc(100vw - 60px))`, `white-space: normal`, `overflow-wrap: break-word`\\n- Toastlar i\xe7in `#mhm-admin-toast-container` ad\u0131nda sabit konumlu flex konteyner eklendi; yeni toastlar `prepend` ile en \xfcste giriyor \u2014 b\xf6ylece birden fazla toast istifleniyor ve en yenisi her zaman \xfcstte\\n- XSS g\xfcvenli\u011fi: toast mesajlar\u0131 art\u0131k template literal ile de\u011fil `.text(message)` ile yaz\u0131l\u0131yor \u2014 gelecekte bir hook\'un bildirim i\xe7eri\u011fine HTML enjekte etme riski yok\\n\\n## \ud83d\udce6 Release ZIP Chart.js 404 \u2014 `.distignore`\'un Gizli Hatas\u0131\\n\\nWordPress.org \xfczerinden kurulan kopyalarda admin dashboard\'daki grafikler 404 veriyordu. K\xf6k nedeni `.distignore` dosyas\u0131n\u0131n `vendor/` paterniydi.\\n\\nRelease ZIP\'i olu\u015fturan `bin/build-release.py` Python script\'i, paterndeki trailing `/` karakterini siliyor ve kalan `vendor`\'u \\"herhangi bir yol segmenti\\" olarak e\u015fle\u015ftiriyordu. Bu mant\u0131kla:\\n\\n- \u2705 `vendor/composer/...` e\u015fle\u015fti \u2014 do\u011fru (Composer klas\xf6r\xfcn\xfc atlamak istiyoruz)\\n- \u274c `assets/js/vendor/chart.min.js` **de** e\u015fle\u015fti \u2014 yanl\u0131\u015f (bu dosya kargoda olmal\u0131yd\u0131)\\n\\nSonu\xe7: `chart.min.js`, `flatpickr/`, `swiper-bundle.min.js` ve di\u011fer a\u011fa\xe7 i\xe7i vendor k\xfct\xfcphaneleri release ZIP\'inden d\xfc\u015f\xfcyordu. Lokal geli\u015ftirmede g\xf6r\xfcnm\xfcyordu \xe7\xfcnk\xfc build s\xfcreci atlan\u0131yordu. Ancak WordPress.org ya da GitHub Release ZIP\'i \xfczerinden kurulum yap\u0131ld\u0131\u011f\u0131nda dashboard bo\u015f kal\u0131yordu.\\n\\n**\xc7\xf6z\xfcm:**\\n\\n- `bin/build-release.py` art\u0131k `.gitignore` tarz\u0131 k\xf6k sabitlemeyi destekliyor \u2014 bir patern `/` ile ba\u015flarsa yaln\u0131zca plugin k\xf6k dizinindeki o yola e\u015fle\u015fiyor, alt dizinlerdeki ayn\u0131 isimli klas\xf6rlere dokunmuyor\\n- `.distignore` g\xfcncellendi: `vendor/` \u2192 `/vendor/`\\n\\nDo\u011frulama: Yeni ZIP\'te `assets/js/vendor/chart.min.js`, `assets/vendor/flatpickr/*`, `assets/vendor/swiper-bundle.min.js` mevcut; Composer `vendor/` k\xf6k dizini d\u0131\u015fland\u0131.\\n\\n## \ud83e\uddd9 Setup Wizard \u2014 Versiyon Badge ve Lite/Pro CTA (Toplu Batch\'ten)\\n\\nBu release\'e toplu halde giren bir dizi kullan\u0131c\u0131 aray\xfcz\xfc iyile\u015ftirmesi:\\n\\n- **Kurulum Sihirbaz\u0131 ba\u015fl\u0131\u011f\u0131** art\u0131k plugin versiyonunu + Lite/Pro rozetini g\xf6steriyor\\n- **Lisans sekmesi + Lisans men\xfc sayfas\u0131** \\"\xdcr\xfcn Sayfas\u0131n\u0131 A\xe7\\" CTA butonu kazand\u0131 \u2014 kullan\u0131c\u0131 \xfcr\xfcn\xfcn sat\u0131n alma sayfas\u0131na tek t\u0131kla gidebiliyor\\n- **Geli\u015ftirici modu guard\u0131:** `has_real_license()` art\u0131k dev mode\'da CTA g\xf6r\xfcnmesini engellemiyor \u2014 geli\u015ftirme ortamlar\u0131nda da CTA test edilebiliyor\\n\\n## \ud83d\udccb De\u011fi\u015fiklik Kayd\u0131\\n\\n| T\xfcr | A\xe7\u0131klama |\\n|-----|----------|\\n| \ud83d\uddbc\ufe0f D\xfczeltme | Ara\xe7 kart\u0131 `sizes` \xf6zniteli\u011fi 220px \u2192 500px (listeleme + favoriler + ar\u015fiv + arama sonu\xe7lar\u0131) |\\n| \ud83d\uddbc\ufe0f D\xfczeltme | `SearchResults` varsay\u0131lan `image_size` `\'medium\'` \u2192 `\'large\'` |\\n| \ud83d\udd14 D\xfczeltme | `render_admin_header()` `<hr class=\\"wp-header-end\\" />` emit ediyor \u2014 bildirimler art\u0131k header flex\'ten \xe7\u0131k\u0131yor |\\n| \ud83d\udd14 D\xfczeltme | Admin toast CSS: sabit `height`/`nowrap` kald\u0131r\u0131ld\u0131, kelime kayd\u0131rma eklendi |\\n| \ud83d\udd14 D\xfczeltme | Admin toast istifleme: `#mhm-admin-toast-container` + `prepend` \u2014 birden fazla toast \xfcst \xfcste binmiyor |\\n| \ud83d\udee1\ufe0f G\xfcvenlik | Admin toast mesajlar\u0131 art\u0131k `.text()` ile yaz\u0131l\u0131yor \u2014 HTML enjeksiyonuna kar\u015f\u0131 g\xfcvende |\\n| \ud83d\udce6 D\xfczeltme | `.distignore` `/vendor/` k\xf6k sabitlemesi \u2014 `chart.min.js`, `flatpickr`, `swiper` art\u0131k ZIP\'te |\\n| \ud83d\udd27 Build | `bin/build-release.py` `.gitignore` tarz\u0131 leading-slash anchoring deste\u011fi |\\n| \ud83e\uddd9 UX | Setup Wizard header versiyon + Lite/Pro badge |\\n| \ud83e\uddd9 UX | Setup Wizard Lisans sekmesi + Lisans men\xfcde \\"\xdcr\xfcn Sayfas\u0131n\u0131 A\xe7\\" CTA |\\n\\n## \ud83d\udcc1 De\u011fi\u015ftirilen Dosyalar\\n\\n- `templates/partials/vehicle-card.php` *(sizes 220px \u2192 500px)*\\n- `src/Admin/Frontend/Shortcodes/SearchResults.php` *(image_size \'medium\' \u2192 \'large\')*\\n- `src/Admin/Core/Traits/AdminHelperTrait.php` *(wp-header-end marker)*\\n- `assets/css/admin/settings.css` *(toast wrap + stacking CSS redesign)*\\n- `assets/js/admin/settings.js` *(container + prepend + .text XSS guard)*\\n- `.distignore` *(/vendor/ k\xf6k sabitleme)*\\n- `bin/build-release.py` *(anchored pattern support)*\\n- `src/Admin/Setup/SetupWizard.php` *(versiyon badge + CTA)*\\n- `src/Admin/Licensing/LicenseAdmin.php` *(CTA)*\\n- `mhm-rentiva.php`, `readme.txt`, `README.md`, `README-tr.md`, `changelog.json`, `changelog-tr.json` *(versiyon y\xfckseltme)*\\n\\n## \u2705 Kalite\\n\\n- **720 test, 2470 assertion, 6 atland\u0131** (v4.25.0 baseline\'\u0131 683/2277 idi)\\n- PHPUnit tam ye\u015fil\\n\\n## \u2b06\ufe0f G\xfcncelleme Notu\\n\\nv4.26.3 tamamen geriye d\xf6n\xfck uyumlu bir patch s\xfcr\xfcm\xfcd\xfcr \u2014 DB \u015femas\u0131nda de\u011fi\u015fiklik yoktur, migration \xe7al\u0131\u015fmaz, ek bir yap\u0131land\u0131rma gerekmez. G\xfcncelleme yollar\u0131:\\n\\n- WordPress admin \u2192 Eklentiler \u2192 G\xfcncelle\\n- `wp plugin update mhm-rentiva --allow-root`\\n- Manuel ZIP y\xfckleme (v4.26.2\'den itibaren otomatik migration destekleniyor)\\n\\n---\\n\\nDaha fazla bilgi i\xe7in [Dok\xfcman Sayfam\u0131z\u0131](https://maxhandmade.github.io/mhm-rentiva-docs/) ziyaret edin."},{"id":"v4.26.2-release-summary","metadata":{"permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/v4.26.2-release-summary","editUrl":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade/mhm-rentiva-docs/tree/main/blog/2026-04-10-v4.26.2-release.md","source":"@site/i18n/tr/docusaurus-plugin-content-blog/2026-04-10-v4.26.2-release.md","title":"MHM Rentiva v4.26.2: Tam Kald\u0131rma Temizli\u011fi ve CLI Bootstrap G\xfc\xe7lendirmesi","description":"v4.26.2, eklenti kald\u0131r\u0131ld\u0131\u011f\u0131nda arkada kalan t\xfcm tablolar\u0131n silinmesini sa\u011fl\u0131yor, wp-cli bootstrap s\u0131ras\u0131ndaki fatal hatay\u0131 gideriyor ve \u015fema migration\'lar\u0131n art\u0131k s\xfcr\xfcm de\u011fi\u015fikli\u011finde otomatik \xe7al\u0131\u015fmas\u0131n\u0131 garantiliyor. \xdc\xe7 d\xfczeltme de \xfcretim ortamlar\u0131ndaki sessiz sorunlar\u0131 hedefliyor.","date":"2026-04-10T09:00:00.000Z","tags":[{"inline":true,"label":"release","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/release"},{"inline":true,"label":"patch","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/patch"},{"inline":true,"label":"uninstall","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/uninstall"},{"inline":true,"label":"cli","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/cli"},{"inline":true,"label":"migration","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/migration"},{"inline":true,"label":"bugfix","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/bugfix"},{"inline":true,"label":"mhm-rentiva","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/mhm-rentiva"}],"readingTime":2.73,"hasTruncateMarker":true,"authors":[{"name":"MaxHandMade","title":"Maintainer","url":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade","imageURL":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade.png","key":"maxhandmade","page":null}],"frontMatter":{"slug":"v4.26.2-release-summary","title":"MHM Rentiva v4.26.2: Tam Kald\u0131rma Temizli\u011fi ve CLI Bootstrap G\xfc\xe7lendirmesi","authors":["maxhandmade"],"tags":["release","patch","uninstall","cli","migration","bugfix","mhm-rentiva"],"date":"2026-04-10T09:00"},"unlisted":false,"prevItem":{"title":"MHM Rentiva v4.26.3: Ara\xe7 Kart\u0131 G\xf6rsel Kalitesi, Admin Toast Kesilmesi ve ZIP Chart.js D\xfczeltmesi","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/v4.26.3-release-summary"},"nextItem":{"title":"MHM Rentiva v4.26.1: Ara\xe7 Detaylar\u0131, Rezervasyon, \xd6deme ve Sepet G\xf6rsel Cilas\u0131","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/v4.26.1-release-summary"}},"content":"v4.26.2, eklenti kald\u0131r\u0131ld\u0131\u011f\u0131nda arkada kalan t\xfcm tablolar\u0131n silinmesini sa\u011fl\u0131yor, wp-cli bootstrap s\u0131ras\u0131ndaki fatal hatay\u0131 gideriyor ve \u015fema migration\'lar\u0131n art\u0131k s\xfcr\xfcm de\u011fi\u015fikli\u011finde otomatik \xe7al\u0131\u015fmas\u0131n\u0131 garantiliyor. \xdc\xe7 d\xfczeltme de \xfcretim ortamlar\u0131ndaki sessiz sorunlar\u0131 hedefliyor.\\n\\n\x3c!--truncate--\x3e\\n\\n## \ud83e\uddf9 Kald\u0131rma Temizli\u011fi \u2014 Art\u0131k 27 Tablonun Hepsi\\n\\n\xd6nceden eklenti \\"verileri temizle\\" se\xe7ene\u011fi ile silindi\u011finde 14 alt sistem tablosu veritaban\u0131nda yetim kal\u0131yordu: `ledger`, `key_registry`, `commission_policy`, `payout_audit`, `tenants`, `usage_metrics` ve eski alert/payment alt sistemlerine ait art\u0131k kullan\u0131lmayan tablolar. Bu v4.26.2 ile tamamen \xe7\xf6z\xfcld\xfc.\\n\\n**Yap\u0131lan iyile\u015ftirmeler:**\\n\\n- **Tam liste:** 27 \xf6zel tablonun tamam\u0131 kald\u0131rma s\u0131ras\u0131nda siliniyor\\n- **Pattern g\xfcvenlik a\u011f\u0131:** Listede olmayan ama `mhm_rentiva_*` \xf6nekiyle ba\u015flayan herhangi bir yetim tablo da otomatik yakalan\u0131p siliniyor \u2014 gelecekte eklenen tablolar i\xe7in g\xfcvence\\n- **Kurtarma tablosu temizli\u011fi:** `DatabaseCleaner` taraf\u0131ndan olu\u015fturulan `postmeta_backup_invalid_*` ge\xe7ici tablolar\u0131 da kald\u0131rma s\u0131ras\u0131nda temizleniyor\\n- **Tek kaynak prensibi:** Silme listesi ve istatistik sayac\u0131 art\u0131k ayn\u0131 kaynaktan okuyor \u2014 saya\xe7 ile ger\xe7ek temizlik birbirinden uzakla\u015famaz\\n- **Savunma mekanizmalar\u0131:** `uninstall.php` ve taksonomi temizleme ad\u0131m\u0131 art\u0131k bozuk bir ayar kayd\u0131 veya eksik taksonomi nedeniyle sessizce durmuyor \u2014 hata yakalan\u0131yor ve kalan ad\u0131mlar \xe7al\u0131\u015fmaya devam ediyor\\n\\n**Do\u011frulama:** DemoSeed Docker ortam\u0131nda v4.26.2 kald\u0131rma testi \u2192 **0 tablo, 0 post, 0 ayar** art\u0131k geride kal\u0131yor. Tam temiz kald\u0131rma garantili.\\n\\n## \ud83d\udd27 CLI Bootstrap Fatal Error D\xfczeltmesi\\n\\n\xd6nceden belirli ko\u015fullarda wp-cli komutlar\u0131 `TypeError` veya `is_user_logged_in() undefined function` hatas\u0131yla \xe7\xf6k\xfcyordu. K\xf6k nedeni iki yerde yat\u0131yordu:\\n\\n- `SettingsCore::get()` ve `has()` bir ayar kayd\u0131n\u0131n dizi olmad\u0131\u011f\u0131 durumda `TypeError` f\u0131rlat\u0131yordu\\n- `AdvancedLogger::log()` WordPress tam y\xfcklenmeden (\xf6rne\u011fin early bootstrap\'te) \xe7a\u011fr\u0131ld\u0131\u011f\u0131nda `is_user_logged_in()`\'i \xe7a\u011f\u0131r\u0131yordu ama bu fonksiyon o a\u015famada tan\u0131ml\u0131 de\u011fildi\\n\\n**\xc7\xf6z\xfcm:**\\n\\n- `SettingsCore::get()`/`has()` art\u0131k dizi olmayan bir ayar de\u011ferini tolere ediyor ve g\xfcvenli varsay\u0131lana d\xfc\u015f\xfcyor\\n- `AdvancedLogger::log()` `plugins_loaded` hook\'u \xe7al\u0131\u015fmadan \xf6nce \xe7a\u011fr\u0131ld\u0131\u011f\u0131nda erken return ediyor \u2014 log atlan\u0131r ama bootstrap \xe7\xf6kmez\\n\\n**Etkisi:** `wp plugin activate mhm-rentiva`, `wp mhm-rentiva *` subkomutlar\u0131 ve di\u011fer wp-cli ak\u0131\u015flar\u0131 art\u0131k bozuk bir ayar kayd\u0131 ya da early-bootstrap log denemesi ile \xe7\xf6km\xfcyor.\\n\\n## \ud83d\udd04 Otomatik \u015eema Migration\'lar\u0131\\n\\nv4.26.2 ile \u015fema migration\'lar\u0131 art\u0131k **eklenti dosya s\xfcr\xfcm\xfc de\u011fi\u015fti\u011finde otomatik \xe7al\u0131\u015f\u0131yor**, WordPress aktivasyon hook\'u \xe7a\u011fr\u0131lmasa bile. Bu; manuel ZIP y\xfckleme, FTP ile g\xfcncelleme ve `wp-cli plugin update` ak\u0131\u015flar\u0131n\u0131 kapsar.\\n\\n**\xd6nceki durum:** Yeni tablolar\u0131 olu\u015fturmak i\xe7in eklentiyi pasifle\u015ftirip tekrar etkinle\u015ftirmek gerekiyordu. Kullan\u0131c\u0131lar\u0131n \xe7o\u011fu bunu bilmedi\u011finden \\"yeni \xf6zellik \xe7al\u0131\u015fm\u0131yor\\" raporu geliyordu.\\n\\n**Yeni durum:** `DB_VERSION` sabiti de\u011fi\u015fir de\u011fi\u015fmez migration\'lar sessizce ve tek seferlik \xe7al\u0131\u015f\u0131r. Aktivasyon hook\'u hala destekleniyor \u2014 sadece art\u0131k zorunlu de\u011fil.\\n\\n## \ud83d\udccb De\u011fi\u015fiklik Kayd\u0131\\n\\n| T\xfcr | A\xe7\u0131klama |\\n|-----|----------|\\n| \ud83e\uddf9 Kald\u0131rma | T\xfcm 27 \xf6zel tablo (ledger, key_registry, commission_policy, payout_audit, tenants, usage_metrics + eski alt sistem tablolar\u0131) |\\n| \ud83d\udee1\ufe0f Kald\u0131rma | Pattern tabanl\u0131 g\xfcvenlik a\u011f\u0131 (`mhm_rentiva_*` \xf6neki) |\\n| \ud83e\uddf9 Kald\u0131rma | `postmeta_backup_invalid_*` kurtarma tablolar\u0131 |\\n| \ud83d\udd27 Kald\u0131rma | Silme listesi ve istatistik sayac\u0131 tek kaynaktan |\\n| \ud83d\udee1\ufe0f Kald\u0131rma | `uninstall.php` ve taksonomi temizli\u011finde savunma mekanizmalar\u0131 |\\n| \ud83d\udd04 G\xfcncelleme | \u015eema migration\'lar\u0131 s\xfcr\xfcm de\u011fi\u015fikli\u011finde otomatik \xe7al\u0131\u015f\u0131yor |\\n| \ud83d\udc1b D\xfczeltme | `SettingsCore::get()`/`has()` dizi olmayan de\u011ferleri tolere ediyor |\\n| \ud83d\udc1b D\xfczeltme | `AdvancedLogger::log()` WordPress y\xfcklenmeden g\xfcvenli d\xf6n\xfc\u015f |\\n\\n## \ud83d\udcc1 De\u011fi\u015ftirilen Dosyalar\\n\\n- `uninstall.php` *(defensive is_array guard + tam tablo listesi)*\\n- `src/Admin/Core/Utilities/DatabaseCleaner.php` *(27 tablo + pattern wildcard)*\\n- `src/Admin/Core/Utilities/DatabaseMigrator.php` *(otomatik migration tetikleme)*\\n- `src/Admin/Core/SettingsCore.php` *(non-array tolerans\u0131)*\\n- `src/Admin/Core/Logging/AdvancedLogger.php` *(plugins_loaded guard)*\\n- `mhm-rentiva.php` *(versiyon g\xfcncelleme)*\\n\\n## \u2b06\ufe0f G\xfcncelleme Notu\\n\\nv4.26.2 tamamen geriye d\xf6n\xfck uyumlu bir patch s\xfcr\xfcm\xfcd\xfcr \u2014 DB \u015femas\u0131nda yeni tablo, kolon veya veri de\u011fi\u015fikli\u011fi **yoktur**. G\xfcncelleme sonras\u0131 ek bir i\u015flem gerekmez. Eklentiyi normal yollarla g\xfcncellemeniz yeterli:\\n\\n- WordPress admin \u2192 Eklentiler \u2192 G\xfcncelle\\n- Veya `wp plugin update mhm-rentiva --allow-root`\\n- Veya manuel ZIP y\xfckleme (art\u0131k otomatik migration tetiklenir)\\n\\n---\\n\\nDaha fazla bilgi i\xe7in [Dok\xfcman Sayfam\u0131z\u0131](https://maxhandmade.github.io/mhm-rentiva-docs/) ziyaret edin."},{"id":"v4.26.1-release-summary","metadata":{"permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/v4.26.1-release-summary","editUrl":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade/mhm-rentiva-docs/tree/main/blog/2026-04-08-v4.26.1-release.md","source":"@site/i18n/tr/docusaurus-plugin-content-blog/2026-04-08-v4.26.1-release.md","title":"MHM Rentiva v4.26.1: Ara\xe7 Detaylar\u0131, Rezervasyon, \xd6deme ve Sepet G\xf6rsel Cilas\u0131","description":"v4.26.1, v4.26.0 ile devreye giren rezervasyon-\xf6deme ak\u0131\u015f\u0131n\u0131n \xfcst\xfcne gelen g\xf6rsel tutars\u0131zl\u0131klar\u0131 temizliyor. Ara\xe7 detay sayfas\u0131ndan sepete, sepetten \xf6deme sayfas\u0131na kadar m\xfc\u015fterinin g\xf6rd\xfc\u011f\xfc her ekranda kart, ikon ve hizalama sorunlar\u0131 giderildi. Fonksiyonel bir de\u011fi\u015fiklik yok \u2014 sadece deneyim daha temiz.","date":"2026-04-08T09:00:00.000Z","tags":[{"inline":true,"label":"release","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/release"},{"inline":true,"label":"patch","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/patch"},{"inline":true,"label":"ui","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/ui"},{"inline":true,"label":"checkout","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/checkout"},{"inline":true,"label":"cart","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/cart"},{"inline":true,"label":"booking","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/booking"},{"inline":true,"label":"bugfix","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/bugfix"},{"inline":true,"label":"mhm-rentiva","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/mhm-rentiva"}],"readingTime":2.13,"hasTruncateMarker":true,"authors":[{"name":"MaxHandMade","title":"Maintainer","url":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade","imageURL":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade.png","key":"maxhandmade","page":null}],"frontMatter":{"slug":"v4.26.1-release-summary","title":"MHM Rentiva v4.26.1: Ara\xe7 Detaylar\u0131, Rezervasyon, \xd6deme ve Sepet G\xf6rsel Cilas\u0131","authors":["maxhandmade"],"tags":["release","patch","ui","checkout","cart","booking","bugfix","mhm-rentiva"],"date":"2026-04-08T09:00"},"unlisted":false,"prevItem":{"title":"MHM Rentiva v4.26.2: Tam Kald\u0131rma Temizli\u011fi ve CLI Bootstrap G\xfc\xe7lendirmesi","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/v4.26.2-release-summary"},"nextItem":{"title":"MHM Rentiva v4.26.0: Depozito Rezervasyonlar\u0131nda Kalan \xd6deme","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/v4.26.0-release-summary"}},"content":"v4.26.1, v4.26.0 ile devreye giren rezervasyon-\xf6deme ak\u0131\u015f\u0131n\u0131n \xfcst\xfcne gelen g\xf6rsel tutars\u0131zl\u0131klar\u0131 temizliyor. Ara\xe7 detay sayfas\u0131ndan sepete, sepetten \xf6deme sayfas\u0131na kadar m\xfc\u015fterinin g\xf6rd\xfc\u011f\xfc her ekranda kart, ikon ve hizalama sorunlar\u0131 giderildi. Fonksiyonel bir de\u011fi\u015fiklik yok \u2014 sadece deneyim daha temiz.\\n\\n\x3c!--truncate--\x3e\\n\\n## \ud83c\udfa8 Ara\xe7 Detaylar\u0131 Kenar \xc7ubu\u011fu\\n\\n- **\xd6zellik etiketleri ta\u015fma sorunu:** Vites, yak\u0131t, koltuk say\u0131s\u0131 gibi spec chip\'leri dar ekranlarda kart kenar\u0131ndan ta\u015f\u0131yordu. Art\u0131k kart s\u0131n\u0131rlar\u0131 i\xe7inde kal\u0131yor ve uzun etiketler do\u011fru \u015fekilde sarmalan\u0131yor.\\n- **Hibrit yak\u0131t ikonu:** Yak\u0131t t\xfcr\xfc \\"hybrid\\" se\xe7ili ara\xe7larda yanl\u0131\u015f ikon g\xf6steriliyordu. Do\u011fru simgeyle de\u011fi\u015ftirildi.\\n\\n## \ud83d\udcc5 Takvim\\n\\n- **Bo\u015f sat\u0131r kald\u0131r\u0131ld\u0131:** Takvim bile\u015feninin alt\u0131nda fazladan bir bo\u015f sat\u0131r render ediliyordu \u2014 kald\u0131r\u0131ld\u0131.\\n- **Kutu i\xe7inde kutu g\xf6r\xfcn\xfcm\xfc:** Kenar \xe7ubu\u011funda takvim widget\'\u0131n\u0131n kendi arka plan\u0131 ile d\u0131\u015f kart arka plan\u0131 i\xe7 i\xe7e iki kutu izlenimi yarat\u0131yordu. \u0130\xe7 kayna\u011f\u0131n arka plan\u0131 n\xf6trle\u015ftirildi, art\u0131k tek bir kart olarak g\xf6r\xfcn\xfcyor.\\n\\n## \ud83d\udcdd Rezervasyon Formu\\n\\n- **Ara\xe7 g\xf6rseli g\xf6r\xfcn\xfcrl\xfc\u011f\xfc:** Form ba\u015fl\u0131\u011f\u0131ndaki ara\xe7 g\xf6rseli a\xe7\u0131k arka planlarda d\xfc\u015f\xfck kontrasta sahipti. Alt\u0131na bir degrade arka plan eklenerek ara\xe7 her zaman g\xf6r\xfcn\xfcr durumda tutuluyor.\\n- **Kart ba\u015fl\u0131k stili birle\u015fimi:** Rezervasyon formunun farkl\u0131 b\xf6l\xfcmleri (tarih, m\xfc\u015fteri bilgisi, ek hizmetler, fiyat \xf6zeti) birbirinden farkl\u0131 ba\u015fl\u0131k stillerine sahipti. T\xfcm b\xf6l\xfcmler art\u0131k ayn\u0131 ba\u015fl\u0131k tipografisi ve padding de\u011ferlerini kullan\u0131yor.\\n\\n## \ud83d\udcb3 \xd6deme Sayfas\u0131\\n\\n- **\xd6deme y\xf6ntemleri dikey:** \xc7oklu \xf6deme y\xf6ntemi (kart, havale, kap\u0131da \xf6deme) etkin oldu\u011funda se\xe7enekler yatay olarak s\u0131ralan\u0131yor ve mobilde ta\u015f\u0131yordu. Art\u0131k tek s\xfctun, dikey stack \u2014 her ekran geni\u015fli\u011finde tutarl\u0131.\\n- **Kupon alan\u0131 ikon:** \\"Kupon kodunuz var m\u0131?\\" uyar\u0131 sat\u0131r\u0131ndaki ikon belirli tema kombinasyonlar\u0131nda bozuk (kare/?) g\xf6r\xfcn\xfcyordu. \u0130kon emoji ile de\u011fi\u015ftirildi, her temada render oluyor.\\n\\n## \ud83d\uded2 Sepet\\n\\n- **Rezervasyon meta sat\u0131rlar\u0131nda yeniden d\xfczen:** Rezervasyon detaylar\u0131 (tarih aral\u0131\u011f\u0131, ek hizmetler, teslim lokasyonu) daha \xf6nce tek bir c\xfcmle i\xe7inde virg\xfclle ayr\u0131lm\u0131\u015f \u015fekilde g\xf6steriliyordu \u2014 okunmas\u0131 zor. Art\u0131k her bilgi `Etiket: De\u011fer` format\u0131nda ayr\u0131 sat\u0131rlar halinde g\xf6steriliyor.\\n- **\xd6demeye git butonu hover:** Buton \xfczerine gelindi\u011finde yaz\u0131 rengi arka planla ayn\u0131 tonda kal\u0131p okunam\u0131yordu. Hover state rengi d\xfczeltildi, yaz\u0131 her durumda okunur.\\n\\n## \ud83d\udccb De\u011fi\u015fiklik Kayd\u0131\\n\\n| Alan | A\xe7\u0131klama |\\n|------|----------|\\n| \ud83d\udd27 Ara\xe7 Detaylar\u0131 | Spec chip ta\u015fma + hibrit yak\u0131t ikonu |\\n| \ud83d\udd27 Takvim | Fazladan bo\u015f sat\u0131r + kutu i\xe7inde kutu g\xf6r\xfcn\xfcm\xfc |\\n| \ud83d\udd27 Rezervasyon Formu | Ara\xe7 g\xf6rseli degrade arka plan + kart ba\u015fl\u0131k birle\u015ftirme |\\n| \ud83d\udd27 \xd6deme | Dikey \xf6deme y\xf6ntemleri + kupon ikon emoji |\\n| \ud83d\udd27 Sepet | Meta etiket/de\u011fer sat\u0131rlar\u0131 + \xf6demeye git hover |\\n\\n## \u2b06\ufe0f G\xfcncelleme Notu\\n\\nv4.26.1 **yaln\u0131zca CSS ve \u015fablon d\xfczeltmeleri** i\xe7erir \u2014 fonksiyonel de\u011fi\u015fiklik, DB \u015fema g\xfcncellemesi veya yeni ayar yoktur. v4.26.0\'dan g\xfcncellemek i\xe7in herhangi bir i\u015flem gerekmez:\\n\\n- WordPress admin \u2192 Eklentiler \u2192 G\xfcncelle\\n- Veya `wp plugin update mhm-rentiva --allow-root`\\n\\n\xd6zel tema override\'lar\u0131 yapmad\u0131ysan\u0131z g\xfcncelleme sonras\u0131 ek ad\u0131m gerekmez. Child theme ile `cart.php`, `checkout/form.php` veya rezervasyon formu \u015fablonlar\u0131n\u0131 override ettiyseniz, yeni s\xfcr\xfcmle uyumluluk i\xe7in \u015fablonlar\u0131n\u0131z\u0131 kar\u015f\u0131la\u015ft\u0131rman\u0131z\u0131 \xf6neririz.\\n\\n---\\n\\nDaha fazla bilgi i\xe7in [Dok\xfcman Sayfam\u0131z\u0131](https://maxhandmade.github.io/mhm-rentiva-docs/) ziyaret edin."},{"id":"v4.26.0-release-summary","metadata":{"permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/v4.26.0-release-summary","editUrl":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade/mhm-rentiva-docs/tree/main/blog/2026-04-07-v4.26.0-release.md","source":"@site/i18n/tr/docusaurus-plugin-content-blog/2026-04-07-v4.26.0-release.md","title":"MHM Rentiva v4.26.0: Depozito Rezervasyonlar\u0131nda Kalan \xd6deme","description":"v4.26.0, depozito ile olu\u015fturulan rezervasyonlarda m\xfc\u015fterilerin kalan bakiyeyi do\u011frudan Hesab\u0131m ekran\u0131ndan \xf6deyebilmesini sa\u011fl\u0131yor. WooCommerce\'in native \xf6deme altyap\u0131s\u0131 kullan\u0131ld\u0131\u011f\u0131ndan aktif t\xfcm \xf6deme y\xf6ntemleri otomatik olarak \xe7al\u0131\u015f\u0131yor.","date":"2026-04-07T09:00:00.000Z","tags":[{"inline":true,"label":"release","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/release"},{"inline":true,"label":"update","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/update"},{"inline":true,"label":"payment","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/payment"},{"inline":true,"label":"woocommerce","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/woocommerce"},{"inline":true,"label":"deposit","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/deposit"},{"inline":true,"label":"bugfix","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/bugfix"},{"inline":true,"label":"mhm-rentiva","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/mhm-rentiva"}],"readingTime":1.45,"hasTruncateMarker":true,"authors":[{"name":"MaxHandMade","title":"Maintainer","url":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade","imageURL":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade.png","key":"maxhandmade","page":null}],"frontMatter":{"slug":"v4.26.0-release-summary","title":"MHM Rentiva v4.26.0: Depozito Rezervasyonlar\u0131nda Kalan \xd6deme","authors":["maxhandmade"],"tags":["release","update","payment","woocommerce","deposit","bugfix","mhm-rentiva"],"date":"2026-04-07T09:00"},"unlisted":false,"prevItem":{"title":"MHM Rentiva v4.26.1: Ara\xe7 Detaylar\u0131, Rezervasyon, \xd6deme ve Sepet G\xf6rsel Cilas\u0131","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/v4.26.1-release-summary"},"nextItem":{"title":"MHM Rentiva v4.25.0: Y\xf6netici Taraf\u0131ndan D\xfczenlenebilir Vendor E-posta \u015eablonlar\u0131","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/v4.25.0-release-summary"}},"content":"v4.26.0, depozito ile olu\u015fturulan rezervasyonlarda m\xfc\u015fterilerin kalan bakiyeyi do\u011frudan Hesab\u0131m ekran\u0131ndan \xf6deyebilmesini sa\u011fl\u0131yor. WooCommerce\'in native \xf6deme altyap\u0131s\u0131 kullan\u0131ld\u0131\u011f\u0131ndan aktif t\xfcm \xf6deme y\xf6ntemleri otomatik olarak \xe7al\u0131\u015f\u0131yor.\\n\\n\x3c!--truncate--\x3e\\n\\n## \ud83d\ude80 \xd6ne \xc7\u0131kan Yenilik\\n\\n### \ud83d\udcb3 Kalan \xd6deme \u2014 Depozito Rezervasyonlar\u0131 i\xe7in\\n\\nDepozito ile rezervasyon olu\u015fturuldu\u011funda kalan bakiye daha \xf6nce yaln\u0131zca manuel takip ya da operat\xf6rle ileti\u015fim gerektiriyordu. v4.26.0 ile m\xfc\u015fteriler bu ad\u0131m\u0131 tamamen kendi ba\u015flar\u0131na tamamlayabiliyor.\\n\\n**Nas\u0131l \xe7al\u0131\u015f\u0131r:**\\n\\n1. M\xfc\u015fteri **Hesab\u0131m \u2192 Rezervasyon Detay\u0131** sayfas\u0131na gider\\n2. Kalan bakiye > 0 ise **\\"Kalan \xd6demeyi Yap\\"** butonu g\xf6r\xfcn\xfcr\\n3. Butona t\u0131kland\u0131\u011f\u0131nda tam tutar i\xe7in minimal bir WC sipari\u015fi arka planda olu\u015fturulur\\n4. M\xfc\u015fteri WooCommerce\'in native order-pay sayfas\u0131na y\xf6nlendirilir\\n5. \xd6deme ba\u015far\u0131l\u0131 oldu\u011funda rezervasyon g\xfcncellenir: kalan bakiye s\u0131f\u0131rlan\u0131r, durum onaylan\u0131r\\n\\n**Teknik \xf6zellikler:**\\n\\n- `RemainingPaymentHandler` \u2014 AJAX endpoint, nonce + sahiplik do\u011frulamas\u0131\\n- **Tekrar sipari\u015f korumas\u0131:** Bekleyen kalan \xf6deme sipari\u015fi varsa yeni sipari\u015f olu\u015fturulmaz, mevcut sipari\u015f yeniden kullan\u0131l\u0131r (`_mhm_remaining_order_id` meta)\\n- **HPOS uyumlu:** T\xfcm WC sipari\u015f i\u015flemleri `$order->update_meta_data() + $order->save()` ile yap\u0131l\u0131r\\n- `WooCommerceBridge`: processing durumunda `_mhm_is_remaining_payment` bayra\u011f\u0131 varsa `_mhm_remaining_amount` s\u0131f\u0131rlan\u0131r\\n\\n## \ud83d\udee0\ufe0f Hata D\xfczeltmeleri\\n\\n### CSS Kapsam D\xfczeltmesi\\n\\nT\xfcm genel hesap sayfas\u0131 s\u0131n\u0131flar\u0131 (`.btn`, `.booking-item`, `.stat-card` vb.) art\u0131k `.mhm-rentiva-account-page` sarmalay\u0131c\u0131s\u0131 alt\u0131na al\u0131nd\u0131. Bu de\u011fi\u015fiklik WoodMart, Flatsome gibi premium temalarla ya\u015fanan g\xf6rsel \xe7ak\u0131\u015fmalar\u0131 engelliyor.\\n\\n### WC Hesab\u0131m Izgara D\xfczeni\\n\\nEntegre modda \u0131zgara tabanl\u0131 temalarda ya\u015fanan `grid-column` d\xfczeni sorunu giderildi (`grid-column: 1/-1`).\\n\\n## \ud83d\udccb De\u011fi\u015fiklik Kayd\u0131\\n\\n| T\xfcr | A\xe7\u0131klama |\\n|-----|----------|\\n| \u2728 Yeni | Kalan \xf6deme butonu \u2014 Hesab\u0131m \u2192 Rezervasyon Detay\u0131 |\\n| \u2728 Yeni | `RemainingPaymentHandler` s\u0131n\u0131f\u0131 (AJAX + do\u011frulama) |\\n| \u2728 Yeni | Tekrar sipari\u015f korumas\u0131 (`_mhm_remaining_order_id` meta) |\\n| \ud83d\udc1b D\xfczeltme | CSS kapsam \u2014 t\xfcm s\u0131n\u0131flar `.mhm-rentiva-account-page` alt\u0131na al\u0131nd\u0131 |\\n| \ud83d\udc1b D\xfczeltme | WC Hesab\u0131m \u0131zgara d\xfczeni (grid-column: 1/-1) |\\n\\n## \ud83d\udcc1 De\u011fi\u015ftirilen Dosyalar\\n\\n- `src/Admin/Payment/WooCommerce/RemainingPaymentHandler.php` *(yeni)*\\n- `src/Admin/Payment/WooCommerce/WooCommerceBridge.php`\\n- `src/Admin/Frontend/Account/AccountController.php`\\n- `templates/account/booking-detail.php`\\n- `mhm-rentiva.php` *(versiyon g\xfcncelleme)*\\n\\n---\\n\\nDaha fazla bilgi i\xe7in [Dok\xfcman Sayfam\u0131z\u0131](https://maxhandmade.github.io/mhm-rentiva-docs/) ziyaret edin."},{"id":"v4.25.0-release-summary","metadata":{"permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/v4.25.0-release-summary","editUrl":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade/mhm-rentiva-docs/tree/main/blog/2026-04-01-v4.25.0-release.md","source":"@site/i18n/tr/docusaurus-plugin-content-blog/2026-04-01-v4.25.0-release.md","title":"MHM Rentiva v4.25.0: Y\xf6netici Taraf\u0131ndan D\xfczenlenebilir Vendor E-posta \u015eablonlar\u0131","description":"v4.25.0, vendor bildirimleri i\xe7in y\xf6netici panelinden d\xfczenlenebilir e-posta \u015fablonlar\u0131 getiriyor. 22 vendor bildirim \u015fablonu art\u0131k Ayarlar ekran\u0131ndan \xf6zelle\u015ftirilebilir. Ayr\u0131ca Site Instance Check-in cron\'u Cron \u0130\u015f Monit\xf6r\xfc\'ne eklendi ve weekly WP cron interval\'inin g\xfcvenilir kayd\u0131 garanti alt\u0131na al\u0131nd\u0131.","date":"2026-04-01T09:00:00.000Z","tags":[{"inline":true,"label":"release","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/release"},{"inline":true,"label":"update","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/update"},{"inline":true,"label":"vendor","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/vendor"},{"inline":true,"label":"email","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/email"},{"inline":true,"label":"accessibility","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/accessibility"},{"inline":true,"label":"bugfix","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/bugfix"},{"inline":true,"label":"mhm-rentiva","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/mhm-rentiva"}],"readingTime":1.71,"hasTruncateMarker":true,"authors":[{"name":"MaxHandMade","title":"Maintainer","url":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade","imageURL":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade.png","key":"maxhandmade","page":null}],"frontMatter":{"slug":"v4.25.0-release-summary","title":"MHM Rentiva v4.25.0: Y\xf6netici Taraf\u0131ndan D\xfczenlenebilir Vendor E-posta \u015eablonlar\u0131","authors":["maxhandmade"],"tags":["release","update","vendor","email","accessibility","bugfix","mhm-rentiva"],"date":"2026-04-01T09:00"},"unlisted":false,"prevItem":{"title":"MHM Rentiva v4.26.0: Depozito Rezervasyonlar\u0131nda Kalan \xd6deme","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/v4.26.0-release-summary"},"nextItem":{"title":"MHM Rentiva v4.24.0: Ara\xe7 Ya\u015fam D\xf6ng\xfcs\xfc Y\xf6netimi & Vendor Self-Servis","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/v4.24.0-release-summary"}},"content":"v4.25.0, vendor bildirimleri i\xe7in y\xf6netici panelinden d\xfczenlenebilir e-posta \u015fablonlar\u0131 getiriyor. 22 vendor bildirim \u015fablonu art\u0131k Ayarlar ekran\u0131ndan \xf6zelle\u015ftirilebilir. Ayr\u0131ca Site Instance Check-in cron\'u Cron \u0130\u015f Monit\xf6r\xfc\'ne eklendi ve `weekly` WP cron interval\'inin g\xfcvenilir kayd\u0131 garanti alt\u0131na al\u0131nd\u0131.\\n\\n\x3c!--truncate--\x3e\\n\\n## \ud83d\ude80 \xd6ne \xc7\u0131kan Yenilikler\\n\\n### \u2709\ufe0f Y\xf6netici Taraf\u0131ndan D\xfczenlenebilir Vendor E-posta \u015eablonlar\u0131\\n\\n22 vendor bildirim \u015fablonu art\u0131k do\u011frudan admin panelinden d\xfczenlenebilir: **Ayarlar \u2192 Bildirim \u015eablonlar\u0131 \u2192 Vendor Bildirimleri** sekmesi.\\n\\n\u015eablonlar 4 b\xf6l\xfcme ayr\u0131lm\u0131\u015f durumda:\\n\\n| B\xf6l\xfcm | \u015eablon Say\u0131s\u0131 |\\n|-------|--------------|\\n| Vendor Hesap (kay\u0131t, onay, ret, ask\u0131) | 5 |\\n| Ara\xe7 \u0130nceleme (onay, ret, d\xfczenleme, yeniden inceleme) | 4 |\\n| Ara\xe7 Ya\u015fam D\xf6ng\xfcs\xfc (duraklatma, devam, sona erme vb.) | 9 |\\n| Finansal E-postalar (\xf6deme, iade, fatura) | 4 |\\n\\n**Ak\u0131ll\u0131 Fallback Sistemi:**\\n- Konu alan\u0131 bo\u015f b\u0131rak\u0131l\u0131rsa \u2192 varsay\u0131lan konu metni g\xf6sterilir (admin ne g\xf6nderilece\u011fini g\xf6r\xfcr)\\n- G\xf6vde alan\u0131 bo\u015f = Gold Standard HTML dosya fallback \u2014 \xf6zelle\u015ftirme yap\u0131lmad\u0131\u011f\u0131nda profesyonel tasar\u0131m korunur\\n\\n### \ud83c\udf10 \xc7eviri Deste\u011fi\\n\\nVendor e-posta admin aray\xfcz\xfc i\xe7in **56 yeni T\xfcrk\xe7e \xe7eviri** eklendi.\\n\\n## \ud83d\udee0\ufe0f Teknik \u0130yile\u015ftirmeler\\n\\n### \ud83c\udfa8 Gold Standard E-posta \u015eablonu Gradient D\xfczeltmesi\\n\\nHeader ba\u015fl\u0131\u011f\u0131nda ger\xe7ek renk ge\xe7i\u015fi art\u0131k do\u011fru \xfcretiliyor \u2014 \xf6nceki s\xfcr\xfcmde gradient olu\u015fturma hesaplama hatas\u0131 vard\u0131.\\n\\n### \u267f Eri\u015filebilirlik: CTA Buton Kontrast Oran\u0131\\n\\nAra\xe7 yeniden inceleme admin e-postas\u0131ndaki amber CTA butonunun kontrast oran\u0131 **2.97:1\'den 6.8:1\'e** y\xfckseltildi. WCAG AA standard\u0131n\u0131 kar\u015f\u0131l\u0131yor.\\n\\n### \ud83d\udd27 Site Instance Check-in Cron G\xf6r\xfcn\xfcrl\xfc\u011f\xfc\\n\\n`mhm_rentiva_instance_checkin` cron g\xf6revi art\u0131k **Cron \u0130\u015f Monit\xf6r\xfc**\'nde g\xf6r\xfcn\xfcyor ve \\"\u015eimdi \xc7al\u0131\u015ft\u0131r\\" butonu ile manuel tetiklenebiliyor. Bu sayede Lite site instance\'lar\u0131n\u0131n lisans sunucusuna kayd\u0131 izlenebilir.\\n\\n### \ud83d\udd27 Weekly Cron Interval Garantisi\\n\\n`weekly` WP cron interval\'i art\u0131k eklenti taraf\u0131ndan a\xe7\u0131k\xe7a kay\u0131t ediliyor \u2014 WooCommerce gibi harici eklentilere ba\u011f\u0131ml\u0131l\u0131k kald\u0131r\u0131ld\u0131.\\n\\n## \ud83d\udccb De\u011fi\u015fiklik Kayd\u0131\\n\\n| T\xfcr | A\xe7\u0131klama |\\n|-----|----------|\\n| \u2728 Yeni | 22 vendor bildirim \u015fablonu admin panelinden d\xfczenlenebilir |\\n| \u2728 Yeni | 4 b\xf6l\xfcm: Hesap (5), \u0130nceleme (4), Ya\u015fam D\xf6ng\xfcs\xfc (9), Finansal (4) |\\n| \u2728 Yeni | Bo\u015f konu \u2192 varsay\u0131lan g\xf6ster; bo\u015f g\xf6vde \u2192 Gold Standard HTML fallback |\\n| \ud83c\udfa8 \u0130yile\u015ftirme | Gold Standard gradient \xfcretimi d\xfczeltildi |\\n| \u267f Eri\u015filebilirlik | Amber CTA kontrast oran\u0131 2.97:1 \u2192 6.8:1 (WCAG AA) |\\n| \ud83c\udf10 \xc7eviri | 56 yeni T\xfcrk\xe7e \xe7eviri (vendor e-posta admin UI) |\\n| \ud83d\udc1b D\xfczeltme | Site Instance Check-in cron Cron Monit\xf6r\xfc\'nde g\xf6r\xfcn\xfcr oldu |\\n| \ud83d\udc1b D\xfczeltme | weekly interval art\u0131k eklenti taraf\u0131ndan garantili kay\u0131t ediliyor |\\n\\n---\\n\\nDaha fazla bilgi i\xe7in [Dok\xfcman Sayfam\u0131z\u0131](https://maxhandmade.github.io/mhm-rentiva-docs/) ziyaret edin."},{"id":"v4.24.0-release-summary","metadata":{"permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/v4.24.0-release-summary","editUrl":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade/mhm-rentiva-docs/tree/main/blog/2026-03-28-v4.24.0-release.md","source":"@site/i18n/tr/docusaurus-plugin-content-blog/2026-03-28-v4.24.0-release.md","title":"MHM Rentiva v4.24.0: Ara\xe7 Ya\u015fam D\xf6ng\xfcs\xfc Y\xf6netimi & Vendor Self-Servis","description":"MHM Rentiva v4.24.0 s\xfcr\xfcm\xfc yay\u0131nland\u0131! Bu s\xfcr\xfcm, ara\xe7lar\u0131n t\xfcm \xf6mr\xfc boyunca y\xf6netilebilece\u011fi tam durum makinesi, vendor\'lar\u0131n ara\xe7lar\u0131n\u0131 kendi kendine y\xf6netebilece\u011fi AJAX self-servis u\xe7 noktalar\u0131 ve adil rekabeti koruyan anti-gaming mekanizmalar\u0131 getiriyor.","date":"2026-03-28T20:00:00.000Z","tags":[{"inline":true,"label":"release","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/release"},{"inline":true,"label":"update","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/update"},{"inline":true,"label":"vendor","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/vendor"},{"inline":true,"label":"lifecycle","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/lifecycle"},{"inline":true,"label":"reliability","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/reliability"},{"inline":true,"label":"notifications","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/notifications"},{"inline":true,"label":"mhm-rentiva","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/mhm-rentiva"}],"readingTime":3.11,"hasTruncateMarker":true,"authors":[{"name":"MaxHandMade","title":"Maintainer","url":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade","imageURL":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade.png","key":"maxhandmade","page":null}],"frontMatter":{"slug":"v4.24.0-release-summary","title":"MHM Rentiva v4.24.0: Ara\xe7 Ya\u015fam D\xf6ng\xfcs\xfc Y\xf6netimi & Vendor Self-Servis","authors":["maxhandmade"],"tags":["release","update","vendor","lifecycle","reliability","notifications","mhm-rentiva"],"date":"2026-03-28T20:00"},"unlisted":false,"prevItem":{"title":"MHM Rentiva v4.25.0: Y\xf6netici Taraf\u0131ndan D\xfczenlenebilir Vendor E-posta \u015eablonlar\u0131","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/v4.25.0-release-summary"},"nextItem":{"title":"MHM Rentiva v4.23.1: Vendor Form Yeniden Tasarimi & Sehir SelectWoo Migrasyonu","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/v4.23.1-release-summary"}},"content":"MHM Rentiva **v4.24.0** s\xfcr\xfcm\xfc yay\u0131nland\u0131! Bu s\xfcr\xfcm, ara\xe7lar\u0131n t\xfcm \xf6mr\xfc boyunca y\xf6netilebilece\u011fi tam durum makinesi, vendor\'lar\u0131n ara\xe7lar\u0131n\u0131 kendi kendine y\xf6netebilece\u011fi AJAX self-servis u\xe7 noktalar\u0131 ve adil rekabeti koruyan anti-gaming mekanizmalar\u0131 getiriyor.\\n\\n\x3c!--truncate--\x3e\\n\\n## \ud83d\ude80 \xd6ne \xc7\u0131kan Yenilikler\\n\\n### \ud83d\ude80 Ara\xe7 Ya\u015fam D\xf6ng\xfcs\xfc Durum Makinesi\\n\\nv4.24.0\'\u0131n ana \xf6zelli\u011fi: ara\xe7lar\u0131n **Aktif \u2192 Duraklat\u0131lm\u0131\u015f \u2192 S\xfcresi Dolmu\u015f \u2192 Geri \xc7ekilmi\u015f** durumlar\u0131 aras\u0131ndaki ge\xe7i\u015flerini y\xf6neten tam durum makinesi.\\n\\n- **5 Durum:** `pending_review`, `active`, `paused`, `expired`, `withdrawn` \u2014 her ge\xe7i\u015f kurallarla korunuyor.\\n- **Ge\xe7i\u015f kurallar\u0131:** Hangi durumdan hangi duruma ge\xe7ilece\u011fi `VehicleLifecycleManager` taraf\u0131ndan zorunlu k\u0131l\u0131n\u0131r.\\n- **Admin UI:** Ara\xe7 listesinde ya\u015fam d\xf6ng\xfcs\xfc s\xfctunu, ara\xe7 d\xfczenleme ekran\u0131nda meta kutu.\\n\\n### \u23f1\ufe0f 90 G\xfcnl\xfck Listeleme S\xfcresi\\n\\n- Ara\xe7lar yay\u0131nland\u0131ktan **90 g\xfcn** sonra otomatik olarak s\xfcresi dolar.\\n- Sona ermeden **10 g\xfcn** ve **3 g\xfcn** \xf6nce vendor\'a uyar\u0131 e-postalar\u0131 g\xf6nderilir.\\n- G\xfcnl\xfck cron ile kontrol edilir; s\xfcresi dolan ara\xe7lar `expired` durumuna ge\xe7er.\\n\\n### \ud83c\udfae Vendor Self-Servis AJAX U\xe7 Noktalar\u0131\\n\\nVendor\'lar art\u0131k ara\xe7lar\u0131n\u0131 admin m\xfcdahalesi olmadan y\xf6netebilir:\\n\\n| \u0130\u015flem | A\xe7\u0131klama |\\n|-------|----------|\\n| **Duraklat** | Aktif ara\xe7 ge\xe7ici olarak pasife al\u0131n\u0131r |\\n| **Devam Et** | Duraklat\u0131lm\u0131\u015f ara\xe7 tekrar aktifle\u015ftirilir |\\n| **Geri \xc7ek** | Ara\xe7 platformdan kal\u0131c\u0131 olarak \xe7ekilir (ceza uygulanabilir) |\\n| **Yenile** | S\xfcresi dolmu\u015f ara\xe7 yeniden aktifle\u015ftirilir |\\n| **Yeniden Listele** | Geri \xe7ekilmi\u015f ara\xe7 tekrar yay\u0131nlan\u0131r |\\n\\n### \ud83d\udcb8 Artan Geri \xc7ekme Ceza Sistemi\\n\\nVendor\'lar\u0131n s\u0131k s\u0131k ara\xe7 geri \xe7ekmesini \xf6nleyen kademeli ceza mekanizmas\u0131:\\n\\n- **1. geri \xe7ekme:** \xdccretsiz \u2014 ceza yok.\\n- **2. geri \xe7ekme:** Ayl\u0131k ortalama gelirin **%10**\'u kesilir.\\n- **3. ve sonras\u0131:** Ayl\u0131k ortalama gelirin **%25**\'i kesilir.\\n- **12 ayl\u0131k kayan pencere:** Ceza sayac\u0131 12 ay ge\xe7ince s\u0131f\u0131rlan\u0131r.\\n- Kesintiler do\u011frudan ledger\'a kaydedilir, payout hesab\u0131ndan d\xfc\u015f\xfcl\xfcr.\\n\\n### \ud83d\udee1\ufe0f Anti-Gaming: Bloklu Tarih Korumas\u0131\\n\\nVendor\'lar\u0131n fiyat manip\xfclasyonunu \xf6nlemek i\xe7in:\\n\\n- Vendor iptal etti\u011fi rezervasyonun tarihleri **30 g\xfcn boyunca yeniden bloklan\u0131r**.\\n- Vendor d\xfc\u015f\xfck fiyatla almak i\xe7in iptal edip daha y\xfcksek fiyata satamaz.\\n- `AntiGamingBlocker` s\u0131n\u0131f\u0131 bu tarih blokajlar\u0131n\u0131 y\xf6netir.\\n\\n### \u2b50 Vendor G\xfcvenilirlik Puan\u0131\\n\\nT\xfcm platformda vendor kalitesini \xf6l\xe7en 0-100 aras\u0131 puan sistemi:\\n\\n- **G\xfcnl\xfck cron** ile yeniden hesaplama.\\n- **Form\xfcl:** \u0130ptal oran\u0131, geri \xe7ekme s\u0131kl\u0131\u011f\u0131, duraklatma ge\xe7mi\u015fi ve tamamlanan rezervasyon say\u0131s\u0131 bazl\u0131.\\n- Admin kullan\u0131c\u0131 listesinde vendor g\xfcvenilirlik s\xfctunu eklendi.\\n- Ara\xe7 kartlar\u0131nda vendor badge olarak g\xf6sterilmeye haz\u0131r.\\n\\n## \ud83d\udce7 9 Yeni E-posta \u015eablonu\\n\\nYa\u015fam d\xf6ng\xfcs\xfcn\xfcn her ad\u0131m\u0131 i\xe7in ayr\u0131 e-posta \u015fablonlar\u0131:\\n\\n| \u015eablon | Tetikleyici |\\n|--------|-------------|\\n| Ara\xe7 Aktifle\u015ftirildi | Ara\xe7 `active` durumuna ge\xe7ti\u011finde |\\n| Ara\xe7 Duraklat\u0131ld\u0131 | Vendor veya admin duraklatt\u0131\u011f\u0131nda |\\n| Duraklatma Devam Etti | Ara\xe7 yeniden aktifle\u015ftirildi\u011finde |\\n| Ara\xe7 Geri \xc7ekildi | Vendor geri \xe7ekme i\u015flemi yapt\u0131\u011f\u0131nda |\\n| Listeleme S\xfcresi Doldu | 90. g\xfcn sonunda otomatik |\\n| 10 G\xfcn Uyar\u0131s\u0131 | S\xfcre dolumundan 10 g\xfcn \xf6nce |\\n| 3 G\xfcn Uyar\u0131s\u0131 | S\xfcre dolumundan 3 g\xfcn \xf6nce |\\n| Ara\xe7 Yenilendi | S\xfcresi dolmu\u015f ara\xe7 yenilendi\u011finde |\\n| Ara\xe7 Yeniden Listelendi | Geri \xe7ekilmi\u015f ara\xe7 tekrar yay\u0131nland\u0131\u011f\u0131nda |\\n\\n## \ud83d\udee0\ufe0f Teknik \u0130yile\u015ftirmeler\\n\\n- **Aktif Filtre:** 6 frontend shortcode art\u0131k `MetaQueryHelper` arac\u0131l\u0131\u011f\u0131yla bak\u0131mdaki/pasif ara\xe7lar\u0131 filtreler \u2014 m\xfc\u015fteriler ge\xe7ersiz ara\xe7lar\u0131 g\xf6remez.\\n- **Veritaban\u0131:** `DatabaseMigrator v3.5.0` \u2014 mevcut t\xfcm aktif ara\xe7lar i\xe7in ya\u015fam d\xf6ng\xfcs\xfc durumu otomatik migrate edildi.\\n- **Login Y\xf6nlendirme:** `wp-login.php` eri\u015fimi WooCommerce hesap sayfas\u0131na y\xf6nlendirildi.\\n- **Lisans Check-in:** Haftal\u0131k cron ile instance check-in.\\n\\n## \ud83d\udccb De\u011fi\u015fiklik Kayd\u0131\\n\\n| T\xfcr | A\xe7\u0131klama |\\n|-----|----------|\\n| \ud83d\ude80 Durum Makinesi | 5 durum, ge\xe7i\u015f kurallar\u0131, VehicleLifecycleManager. |\\n| \u23f1\ufe0f Listeleme S\xfcresi | 90 g\xfcn, cron tabanl\u0131, 10/3 g\xfcn uyar\u0131 e-postalar\u0131. |\\n| \ud83c\udfae Self-Servis | Duraklat, devam et, geri \xe7ek, yenile, yeniden listele AJAX. |\\n| \ud83d\udcb8 Ceza Sistemi | %0/%10/%25 kademeli, 12 ayl\u0131k kayan pencere, ledger entegrasyonu. |\\n| \ud83d\udee1\ufe0f Anti-Gaming | \u0130ptal edilen tarihler 30 g\xfcn bloklan\u0131r. |\\n| \u2b50 G\xfcvenilirlik | Vendor skoru 0-100, g\xfcnl\xfck cron yeniden hesaplama. |\\n| \ud83d\udce7 Bildirimler | 9 yeni ya\u015fam d\xf6ng\xfcs\xfc e-posta \u015fablonu. |\\n| \ud83d\udcca Admin UI | Ya\u015fam d\xf6ng\xfcs\xfc s\xfctunu, meta kutu, vendor g\xfcvenilirlik s\xfctunu. |\\n| \ud83d\udd0d Aktif Filtre | 6 shortcode MetaQueryHelper ile pasif ara\xe7lar\u0131 filtreler. |\\n| \ud83d\uddc4\ufe0f Veritaban\u0131 | v3.5.0 migration, mevcut ara\xe7lar migrate edildi. |\\n| \u2705 Test | 665 test, 2248 assertion (567/2036\'dan art\u0131\u015f). |\\n\\n### S\xfcr\xfcm Notlar\u0131\\n\\nv4.24.0, MHM Rentiva\'n\u0131n ara\xe7 y\xf6netim altyap\u0131s\u0131n\u0131 k\xf6kten g\xfc\xe7lendiriyor. Art\u0131k ara\xe7lar yaln\u0131zca \\"aktif/pasif\\" de\u011fil; tam bir ya\u015fam d\xf6ng\xfcs\xfcne sahip. Vendor\'lar ara\xe7lar\u0131n\u0131 kendi kendine y\xf6netirken platform, adil rekabeti ceza sistemi ve anti-gaming mekanizmalar\u0131yla koruyor. G\xfcvenilirlik puan\u0131 ise kaliteli vendor\'lar\u0131n \xf6ne \xe7\u0131kmas\u0131n\u0131 sa\u011flayan yeni bir rekabet boyutu ekliyor.\\n\\n---\\nMHM Rentiva hakk\u0131nda daha fazla bilgi ve dok\xfcmantasyon i\xe7in [Dok\xfcman Sayfam\u0131z\u0131](https://maxhandmade.github.io/mhm-rentiva-docs/) ziyaret edebilirsiniz."},{"id":"v4.23.1-release-summary","metadata":{"permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/v4.23.1-release-summary","editUrl":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade/mhm-rentiva-docs/tree/main/blog/2026-03-28-v4.23.1-release.md","source":"@site/i18n/tr/docusaurus-plugin-content-blog/2026-03-28-v4.23.1-release.md","title":"MHM Rentiva v4.23.1: Vendor Form Yeniden Tasarimi & Sehir SelectWoo Migrasyonu","description":"MHM Rentiva v4.23.1 surumu yayinlandi! Bu surum, vendor ayarlar sayfasinin tamamen yeniden tasarlanmasini, basvuru formundaki alan degisikliklerini, sehir secici bilesenlerin SelectWoo\'ya donusturulmesini ve arac sigorta belgesi yukleme ozelligini icerir.","date":"2026-03-28T18:00:00.000Z","tags":[{"inline":true,"label":"release","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/release"},{"inline":true,"label":"update","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/update"},{"inline":true,"label":"vendor","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/vendor"},{"inline":true,"label":"forms","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/forms"},{"inline":true,"label":"selectwoo","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/selectwoo"},{"inline":true,"label":"vehicle","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/vehicle"},{"inline":true,"label":"mhm-rentiva","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/mhm-rentiva"}],"readingTime":2.3,"hasTruncateMarker":true,"authors":[{"name":"MaxHandMade","title":"Maintainer","url":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade","imageURL":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade.png","key":"maxhandmade","page":null}],"frontMatter":{"slug":"v4.23.1-release-summary","title":"MHM Rentiva v4.23.1: Vendor Form Yeniden Tasarimi & Sehir SelectWoo Migrasyonu","authors":["maxhandmade"],"tags":["release","update","vendor","forms","selectwoo","vehicle","mhm-rentiva"],"date":"2026-03-28T18:00"},"unlisted":false,"prevItem":{"title":"MHM Rentiva v4.24.0: Ara\xe7 Ya\u015fam D\xf6ng\xfcs\xfc Y\xf6netimi & Vendor Self-Servis","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/v4.24.0-release-summary"},"nextItem":{"title":"MHM Rentiva v4.23.0: Vendor Transfer Mimarisi & Dashboard Denetimi","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/v4.23.0-release-summary"}},"content":"MHM Rentiva **v4.23.1** surumu yayinlandi! Bu surum, vendor ayarlar sayfasinin tamamen yeniden tasarlanmasini, basvuru formundaki alan degisikliklerini, sehir secici bilesenlerin SelectWoo\'ya donusturulmesini ve arac sigorta belgesi yukleme ozelligini icerir.\\n\\n\x3c!--truncate--\x3e\\n\\n## Onemli Yenilikler\\n\\n### Vendor Ayarlar Sayfasi Yeniden Tasarimi\\n\\nVendor ayarlar sayfasi (`vendor-settings.php`) sifirdan yeniden yazildi:\\n\\n- **Inline stil temizligi:** Tum inline CSS kaldirildi, `.mhm-vendor-form__*` CSS sinif yapisi ile `vendor-forms.css` dosyasina tasinarak bakim kolayligi saglandi.\\n- **Yeni alanlar:** Hesap Sahibi (Account Holder) ve Vergi Dairesi (Tax Office) alanlari eklendi.\\n- **Bildirim sistemi:** Bildirimler artik `mhm-vendor-notice` siniflariyla gosteriliyor.\\n\\n### Basvuru Formu Guncellemeleri\\n\\nVendor basvuru formunda onemli alan degisiklikleri yapildi:\\n\\n- **Hizmet Alanlari kaldirildi:** Checkbox olarak sunulan Hizmet Alanlari (Service Areas) bolumu kaldirildi; yerine bilgi notu eklendi.\\n- **Arac Sigortasi tasinidi:** Basvuru formundan kaldirilip arac ekleme formuna (`[rentiva_vehicle_submit]`) tasindi.\\n- **Yeni finansal alanlar:** Hesap Sahibi (zorunlu) ve Vergi Dairesi (opsiyonel) alanlari eklendi.\\n- **Meta senkronizasyonu:** `VendorApplicationManager` ve `VendorOnboardingController` onay akisinda yeni alanlarin senkronizasyonu saglandi.\\n\\n### Sehir SelectWoo Migrasyonu\\n\\nTum sehir metin girisleri (`<datalist>`) modern bir secim bilesenine donusturuldu:\\n\\n- **Yeni mimari:** `<select>` + WooCommerce selectWoo ile aranabilir, kullanici dostu sehir secimi.\\n- **Yeni metot:** `CityHelper::render_select()` \u2014 tum sehir secicilerde tek kaynak (SSOT).\\n- **Guncellenen formlar:** vendor-settings.php, VendorApply.php, VehicleSubmit.php, TransferAdmin.php.\\n- **CSS/JS enqueue:** UserDashboard.php, VendorApply.php ve VehicleSubmit.php dosyalarina SelectWoo asset\'leri eklendi.\\n\\n### Arac Sigorta Belgesi Yukleme\\n\\nArac ekleme formuna yeni bir belge yukleme bolumu eklendi:\\n\\n- Arac ruhsatindan sonra sigorta belgesi (`_mhm_rentiva_vehicle_insurance_doc`) yuklenebilir.\\n- VehicleSubmit.php AJAX handler\'i sigorta dosyasi isleme destegi ile guncellendi.\\n\\n### Arac Yasam Dongusu Yonetimi (Tasarim)\\n\\nKapsamli bir tasarim dokumani olusturuldu (`docs/plans/2026-03-28-vehicle-lifecycle-management-design.md`):\\n\\n- **Durumlar:** Aktif / Duraklatildi / Geri Cekildi / Suresi Doldu\\n- **Listeleme suresi:** 90 gun, yenileme mekanizmasi ile\\n- **Iptal ceza sistemi:** Kademeli ceza puanlari\\n- **Guvenilirlik skoru:** 0-100 arasi performans degerlendirmesi\\n- **Soguma suresi:** Geri cekilmeden sonra 7 gun bekleme\\n- **Tarih engelleme:** Kotu niyetli kullanima karsi onlem\\n- **8 fazli uygulama plani** hazirland\u0131\\n\\n## Kesfedilen Hatalar (Henuz Duzeltilmedi)\\n\\n| Hata | Detay |\\n|------|-------|\\n| Arac durumu arama filtresi | `_mhm_vehicle_status` arama sorgularinda kontrol edilmiyor \u2014 bakimdaki araclar arama sonuclarinda gorunuyor. |\\n| Vendor askiya alma | `VendorOnboardingController::suspend()` vendor\'un araclarini yayindan kaldirmiyor. |\\n\\n## Degisiklik Kaydi\\n\\n| Tur | Aciklama |\\n|-----|----------|\\n| Vendor Ayarlar | Sayfa tamamen yeniden tasarlandi; inline stiller CSS sinif yapisina tasindi. |\\n| Vendor Ayarlar | Hesap Sahibi ve Vergi Dairesi alanlari eklendi. |\\n| Basvuru Formu | Hizmet Alanlari ve Arac Sigortasi alanlari kaldirildi/tasindi. |\\n| Basvuru Formu | Hesap Sahibi (zorunlu) ve Vergi Dairesi (opsiyonel) eklendi. |\\n| Sehir Secici | Tum datalist sehir girisleri SelectWoo bilesenine donusturuldu. |\\n| Arac Formu | Sigorta belgesi yukleme bolumu eklendi. |\\n| Tasarim | Arac Yasam Dongusu Yonetimi tasarim dokumani olusturuldu. |\\n| Hata Kesfedilen | 2 hata tespiti: arac durumu filtresi, vendor askiya alma. |\\n\\n### Surum Notlari\\nBu surum, vendor formlarinin modernizasyonu, sehir secici bilesenlerinin WooCommerce SelectWoo\'ya tas\u0131nmas\u0131 ve arac sigorta belgesi yukleme destegi ile vendor deneyimini onemli olcude iyilestirmistir. Arac Yasam Dongusu Yonetimi tasarim dokumani gelecek surumler icin yol haritasi saglamaktadir.\\n\\n---\\nMHM Rentiva hakkinda daha fazla bilgi ve dokumantasyon icin [Dokuman Sayfamizi](https://maxhandmade.github.io/mhm-rentiva-docs/) ziyaret edebilirsiniz."},{"id":"v4.23.0-release-summary","metadata":{"permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/v4.23.0-release-summary","editUrl":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade/mhm-rentiva-docs/tree/main/blog/2026-03-26-v4.23.0-release.md","source":"@site/i18n/tr/docusaurus-plugin-content-blog/2026-03-26-v4.23.0-release.md","title":"MHM Rentiva v4.23.0: Vendor Transfer Mimarisi & Dashboard Denetimi","description":"MHM Rentiva v4.23.0 s\xfcr\xfcm\xfc yay\u0131nland\u0131! Bu s\xfcr\xfcm, vendor\'lar\u0131n transfer hizmetlerini \u015fehir bazl\u0131 y\xf6netebilmesini sa\u011flayan yeni bir mimari, kapsaml\u0131 Dashboard widget denetimi ve onlarca hata d\xfczeltmesi getiriyor.","date":"2026-03-26T18:00:00.000Z","tags":[{"inline":true,"label":"release","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/release"},{"inline":true,"label":"update","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/update"},{"inline":true,"label":"vendor","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/vendor"},{"inline":true,"label":"transfer","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/transfer"},{"inline":true,"label":"dashboard","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/dashboard"},{"inline":true,"label":"export","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/export"},{"inline":true,"label":"search","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/search"},{"inline":true,"label":"mhm-rentiva","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/mhm-rentiva"}],"readingTime":2.4,"hasTruncateMarker":true,"authors":[{"name":"MaxHandMade","title":"Maintainer","url":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade","imageURL":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade.png","key":"maxhandmade","page":null}],"frontMatter":{"slug":"v4.23.0-release-summary","title":"MHM Rentiva v4.23.0: Vendor Transfer Mimarisi & Dashboard Denetimi","authors":["maxhandmade"],"tags":["release","update","vendor","transfer","dashboard","export","search","mhm-rentiva"],"date":"2026-03-26T18:00"},"unlisted":false,"prevItem":{"title":"MHM Rentiva v4.23.1: Vendor Form Yeniden Tasarimi & Sehir SelectWoo Migrasyonu","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/v4.23.1-release-summary"},"nextItem":{"title":"MHM Rentiva v4.21.2: Vendor Y\xf6netimi ve Finansal Mimari Devrimi","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/v4.21.2-release-summary"}},"content":"MHM Rentiva **v4.23.0** s\xfcr\xfcm\xfc yay\u0131nland\u0131! Bu s\xfcr\xfcm, vendor\'lar\u0131n transfer hizmetlerini \u015fehir bazl\u0131 y\xf6netebilmesini sa\u011flayan yeni bir mimari, kapsaml\u0131 Dashboard widget denetimi ve onlarca hata d\xfczeltmesi getiriyor.\\n\\n\x3c!--truncate--\x3e\\n\\n## \ud83d\ude80 \xd6ne \xc7\u0131kan Yenilikler\\n\\n### \ud83c\udfd7\ufe0f Vendor Transfer Lokasyon Sistemi\\n\\nv4.23.0\'\u0131n en b\xfcy\xfck yenili\u011fi, **\u015eehir \u2192 Nokta hiyerar\u015fisi** ile vendor\'lar\u0131n transfer operasyonlar\u0131n\u0131 y\xf6netebilmesidir:\\n\\n- **\u015eehir bazl\u0131 filtreleme:** Her lokasyona bir \u015fehir alan\u0131 eklendi. Vendor\'lar yaln\u0131zca kendi \u015fehirlerindeki lokasyonlar\u0131 ve rotalar\u0131 g\xf6rebilir.\\n- **Rota bazl\u0131 fiyatland\u0131rma:** Admin\'in belirledi\u011fi `min_price` \u2014 `max_price` aral\u0131\u011f\u0131nda her vendor kendi rota fiyat\u0131n\u0131 belirleyebilir.\\n- **Transfer arama motoru:** Rota bazl\u0131 ara\xe7 filtreleme ve vendor fiyat\u0131 deste\u011fi ile yeniden yap\u0131land\u0131r\u0131ld\u0131. Vendor fiyat\u0131 yoksa rotan\u0131n `base_price` de\u011feri fallback olarak kullan\u0131l\u0131r.\\n- **Veritaban\u0131:** `DatabaseMigrator v3.4.0` ile lokasyonlara `city` s\xfctunu, rotalara `max_price` s\xfctunu eklendi.\\n\\n### \ud83d\udcca Dashboard Widget Denetimi (11 D\xfczeltme)\\n\\nDashboard widget\'lar\u0131nda kapsaml\u0131 bir denetim yap\u0131ld\u0131:\\n- **Timezone tutarl\u0131l\u0131\u011f\u0131:** Geri say\u0131m ve operasyon widget\'lar\u0131 WordPress timezone ayar\u0131na uyumlu hale getirildi.\\n- **Cache invalidation:** \u0130statistik cache key prefix uyumsuzlu\u011fu d\xfczeltildi.\\n- **WC email g\xf6rselleri:** Rezervasyon onay e-postalar\u0131nda ara\xe7 g\xf6rseli art\u0131k do\u011fru g\xf6steriliyor.\\n- **Tasar\u0131m iyile\u015ftirmeleri:** 2x2 grid istatistik kartlar\u0131, yerelle\u015ftirilmi\u015f gelir grafi\u011fi, mesajlar widget\'\u0131 yeniden tasarland\u0131.\\n- **Lite gating:** Gelir Grafi\u011fi ve Yakla\u015fan Operasyonlar widget\'lar\u0131 art\u0131k Pro-only.\\n\\n### \ud83d\udd0e Arama ve Filtreleme D\xfczeltmeleri\\n\\n- **strtotime(\'\') hatas\u0131:** Bo\u015f tarih parametresi bug\xfcn\xfcn tarihini d\xf6nd\xfcr\xfcyordu, aktif booking\'li ara\xe7lar hatal\u0131 filtreleniyordu. Guard eklendi.\\n- **Lokasyon filtresi:** Radio butonlardan checkbox\'a d\xf6n\xfc\u015ft\xfcr\xfcld\xfc; birden fazla lokasyon se\xe7ilebilir.\\n- **Transfer tab do\u011frulama:** Transfer alanlar\u0131 (`origin_id`, `destination_id`, `date`, `luggage_*`) hardcoded required olarak ayarland\u0131.\\n\\n### \ud83d\udce4 D\u0131\u015fa Aktar\u0131m (4 D\xfczeltme)\\n\\n- \xd6deme g\xfcnl\xfckleri post_type uyumsuzlu\u011fu giderildi.\\n- Kay\u0131t say\u0131s\u0131 daima 0 d\xf6nen sorgu hatas\u0131 d\xfczeltildi.\\n- Ge\xe7mi\u015f silme i\u015flevi art\u0131k \xe7al\u0131\u015f\u0131yor (transient tabanl\u0131).\\n- Ara\xe7 CSV/JSON PHP 8 strict types fatal error\'\u0131 giderildi.\\n\\n## \ud83d\udc64 Vendor \u0130yile\u015ftirmeleri\\n\\n- **Ara\xe7 ruhsat do\u011frulama:** Vendor ara\xe7 ekleme formunda ruhsat bilgisi do\u011frulan\u0131yor.\\n- **D\xfczenleme formu:** Vendor ara\xe7 d\xfczenlemesinde yeniden inceleme (re-review) mekanizmas\u0131.\\n- **Vendor rozeti:** Vendor ara\xe7lar\u0131nda tedarik\xe7i rozeti g\xf6r\xfcnt\xfcleniyor.\\n\\n## \u2699\ufe0f Di\u011fer \u0130yile\u015ftirmeler\\n\\n- **Engellli tarihler:** \\"T\xfcm\xfcne Uygula\\" AJAX d\xfczeltmesi; taray\u0131c\u0131 verisi payload\'da g\xf6nderiliyor.\\n- **Elementor:** 7 widget\'ta attribute kontrol say\u0131s\u0131 art\u0131r\u0131ld\u0131 (VehicleComparison, MyBookings, MyFavorites, VehicleDetails, Testimonials, VehiclesGrid, FeaturedVehicles).\\n- **Ayarlar:** Cache tekrar\u0131, \xf6l\xfc ayarlar temizli\u011fi, SetupWizard sayfa listesi ve AssetManager guard d\xfczeltmeleri.\\n- **\xc7eviri:** 15+ yeni T\xfcrk\xe7e \xe7eviri, WP 6.5+ `.l10n.php` dosyas\u0131 yenilendi.\\n\\n## \ud83d\udccb De\u011fi\u015fiklik Kayd\u0131\\n\\n| T\xfcr | A\xe7\u0131klama |\\n|-----|----------|\\n| \ud83c\udfd7\ufe0f Mimari | Vendor Transfer Lokasyon sistemi: \u015eehir\u2192Nokta hiyerar\u015fisi. |\\n| \ud83d\udcb0 Fiyatlama | Vendor rota bazl\u0131 fiyatland\u0131rma (min/max aral\u0131\u011f\u0131). |\\n| \ud83d\udd0d Arama | Transfer arama motoru rota bazl\u0131 filtreleme + vendor fiyat\u0131. |\\n| \ud83d\uddc4\ufe0f Veritaban\u0131 | v3.4.0 migration: city + max_price s\xfctunlar\u0131. |\\n| \ud83d\udcca Dashboard | 11 hata d\xfczeltmesi: timezone, cache, WC email, tasar\u0131m, Lite gating. |\\n| \ud83d\udd0e Filtre | strtotime hatas\u0131, lokasyon checkbox, transfer tab do\u011frulama. |\\n| \ud83d\udcc5 Engelli Tarihler | \\"T\xfcm\xfcne Uygula\\" AJAX d\xfczeltmesi. |\\n| \ud83d\udce4 D\u0131\u015fa Aktar\u0131m | 4 kritik hata d\xfczeltmesi. |\\n| \ud83d\udc64 Vendor | Ruhsat do\u011frulama, yeniden inceleme, vendor rozeti. |\\n| \ud83c\udfa8 Elementor | 7 widget attribute iyile\u015ftirmesi. |\\n| \u2699\ufe0f Ayarlar | Cache, \xf6l\xfc ayarlar, SetupWizard, AssetManager d\xfczeltmeleri. |\\n| \ud83c\udf10 \xc7eviri | 15+ yeni T\xfcrk\xe7e \xe7eviri, .l10n.php yenilendi. |\\n| \u2705 Test | 567 test, 2036 assertion. |\\n\\n### S\xfcr\xfcm Notlar\u0131\\nBu s\xfcr\xfcm, MHM Rentiva\'n\u0131n vendor transfer mimarisini temelden yeniden yap\u0131land\u0131rm\u0131\u015ft\u0131r. \u015eehir bazl\u0131 lokasyon filtresi, rota bazl\u0131 fiyatland\u0131rma ve Dashboard widget denetimi ile platform daha kararl\u0131 ve zengin bir yap\u0131ya kavu\u015fmu\u015ftur.\\n\\n---\\nMHM Rentiva hakk\u0131nda daha fazla bilgi ve dok\xfcmantasyon i\xe7in [Dok\xfcman Sayfam\u0131z\u0131](https://maxhandmade.github.io/mhm-rentiva-docs/) ziyaret edebilirsiniz."},{"id":"v4.21.2-release-summary","metadata":{"permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/v4.21.2-release-summary","editUrl":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade/mhm-rentiva-docs/tree/main/blog/2026-03-11-v4.21.2-release.md","source":"@site/i18n/tr/docusaurus-plugin-content-blog/2026-03-11-v4.21.2-release.md","title":"MHM Rentiva v4.21.2: Vendor Y\xf6netimi ve Finansal Mimari Devrimi","description":"MHM Rentiva v4.21.2 s\xfcr\xfcm\xfc yay\u0131nland\u0131! Bu s\xfcr\xfcm, eklentinin ticaret ve operasyon yeteneklerini k\xf6kten de\u011fi\u015ftiren \\"Vendor Management\\", \\"Financial Architecture\\" ve \\"VIP Transfer\\" mod\xfcllerini beraberinde getiriyor.","date":"2026-03-11T16:00:00.000Z","tags":[{"inline":true,"label":"release","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/release"},{"inline":true,"label":"update","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/update"},{"inline":true,"label":"vendor","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/vendor"},{"inline":true,"label":"finance","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/finance"},{"inline":true,"label":"payment","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/payment"},{"inline":true,"label":"vip-transfer","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/vip-transfer"},{"inline":true,"label":"mhm-rentiva","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/mhm-rentiva"}],"readingTime":1.47,"hasTruncateMarker":true,"authors":[{"name":"MaxHandMade","title":"Maintainer","url":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade","imageURL":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade.png","key":"maxhandmade","page":null}],"frontMatter":{"slug":"v4.21.2-release-summary","title":"MHM Rentiva v4.21.2: Vendor Y\xf6netimi ve Finansal Mimari Devrimi","authors":["maxhandmade"],"tags":["release","update","vendor","finance","payment","vip-transfer","mhm-rentiva"],"date":"2026-03-11T16:00"},"unlisted":false,"prevItem":{"title":"MHM Rentiva v4.23.0: Vendor Transfer Mimarisi & Dashboard Denetimi","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/v4.23.0-release-summary"},"nextItem":{"title":"MHM Rentiva v4.10.0: Block/Shortcode Parity Stabilizasyonu","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/v4.10.0-release-summary"}},"content":"MHM Rentiva **v4.21.2** s\xfcr\xfcm\xfc yay\u0131nland\u0131! Bu s\xfcr\xfcm, eklentinin ticaret ve operasyon yeteneklerini k\xf6kten de\u011fi\u015ftiren \\"Vendor Management\\", \\"Financial Architecture\\" ve \\"VIP Transfer\\" mod\xfcllerini beraberinde getiriyor.\\n\\n\x3c!--truncate--\x3e\\n\\n## \ud83d\ude80 \xd6ne \xc7\u0131kan Yenilikler\\n\\nBu g\xfcncelleme, MHM Rentiva\'y\u0131 sadece bir rezervasyon motoru olmaktan \xe7\u0131kar\u0131p, tam te\u015fekk\xfcll\xfc bir pazaryeri (marketplace) ve transfer y\xf6netim platformuna d\xf6n\xfc\u015ft\xfcr\xfcyor.\\n\\n### \ud83c\udfe2 Vendor (Tedarik\xe7i) Y\xf6netimi\\nArt\u0131k platformunuzda birden fazla tedarik\xe7iyi y\xf6netebilirsiniz. Her tedarik\xe7i kendi ara\xe7lar\u0131n\u0131, fiyatland\u0131rmas\u0131n\u0131 ve rezervasyonlar\u0131n\u0131 kontrol edebilir.\\n- **Tedarik\xe7i Paneli:** \xd6zelle\u015ftirilmi\u015f admin aray\xfcz\xfc.\\n- **Performans Takibi:** Tedarik\xe7i bazl\u0131 doluluk ve gelir raporlar\u0131.\\n\\n### \ud83d\udcb0 Yeni Finansal Mimari\\n\xd6deme y\xf6netimi ve komisyon hesaplamalar\u0131 tamamen standardize edildi.\\n- **Commission Management:** Esnek komisyon oranlar\u0131 ve otomatik hesaplama.\\n- **Ledger System:** T\xfcm finansal hareketlerin \u015feffaf bir \u015fekilde kaydedildi\u011fi muhasebe defteri.\\n- **Payouts:** Tedarik\xe7i \xf6demelerinin merkezi takibi.\\n\\n### \ud83d\ude90 VIP Transfer Mod\xfcl\xfc\\nNoktadan noktaya rota bazl\u0131 fiyatland\u0131rma ve rezervasyon sistemi.\\n- **Rota Bazl\u0131 Fiyatland\u0131rma:** Mesafe veya rota bazl\u0131 dinamik fiyat tan\u0131mlama.\\n- **Transfer Rezervasyonu:** Ara\xe7 kiralama ak\u0131\u015f\u0131ndan ba\u011f\u0131ms\u0131z, optimize edilmi\u015f transfer deneyimi.\\n\\n## \ud83d\udee0\ufe0f Teknik \u0130yile\u015ftirmeler ve G\xfcvenlik\\n\\nSadece \xf6zellik de\u011fil, altyap\u0131 olarak da g\xfc\xe7lendik:\\n- **Hardened REST API:** `SecurityHelper` ve `AuthHelper` ile API u\xe7 noktalar\u0131 daha g\xfcvenli hale getirildi.\\n- **WP 6.7+ Uyumlu:** En son WordPress s\xfcr\xfcmleriyle tam uyumluluk ve performans optimizasyonu.\\n- **Modern Gereksinimler:** Minimum PHP 8.1+ ve WP 6.7+ standartlar\u0131na ge\xe7i\u015f yap\u0131ld\u0131.\\n\\n## \ud83d\udccb De\u011fi\u015fiklik Kayd\u0131\\n\\n| T\xfcr | A\xe7\u0131klama |\\n|-----|----------|\\n| \u2728 Yeni Mod\xfcl | Vendor Y\xf6netim Sistemi (Multi-vendor deste\u011fi). |\\n| \ud83d\udcb8 Finans | Geli\u015fmi\u015f finansal mimari, komisyon ve defter (ledger) sistemi. |\\n| \ud83d\udeeb Transfer | VIP Transfer mod\xfcl\xfc ve rota bazl\u0131 fiyatland\u0131rma motoru. |\\n| \ud83d\udee1\ufe0f G\xfcvenlik | REST API g\xfcvenlik katmanlar\u0131 (`AuthHelper` entegrasyonu). |\\n| \ud83d\ude80 Performans | PHP 8.1+ optimizasyonu ve autoloader iyile\u015ftirmeleri. |\\n| \ud83e\uddf9 Paketleme | `.distignore` ile optimize edilmi\u015f, tertemiz eklenti paketi yap\u0131s\u0131. |\\n\\n### S\xfcr\xfcm Notlar\u0131\\nBu s\xfcr\xfcm, `mhm-rentiva` ekosisteminde bug\xfcne kadar yap\u0131lm\u0131\u015f en kapsaml\u0131 mod\xfcler geni\u015fletmedir. Mod\xfcller aras\u0131 veri b\xfct\xfcnl\xfc\u011f\xfc `Util::has_overlap()` ve `DepositCalculator` gibi merkezi s\u0131n\u0131flar \xfczerinden garanti alt\u0131na al\u0131nm\u0131\u015ft\u0131r.\\n\\n---\\nMHM Rentiva hakk\u0131nda daha fazla bilgi ve dok\xfcmantasyon i\xe7in [Dok\xfcman Sayfam\u0131z\u0131](https://maxhandmade.github.io/mhm-rentiva-docs/) ziyaret edebilirsiniz."},{"id":"v4.10.0-release-summary","metadata":{"permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/v4.10.0-release-summary","editUrl":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade/mhm-rentiva-docs/tree/main/blog/2026-02-18-v4.10.0-release.md","source":"@site/i18n/tr/docusaurus-plugin-content-blog/2026-02-18-v4.10.0-release.md","title":"MHM Rentiva v4.10.0: Block/Shortcode Parity Stabilizasyonu","description":"MHM Rentiva v4.10.0 s\xfcr\xfcm\xfc yay\u0131nland\u0131! Bu b\xfcy\xfck g\xfcncelleme ile Gutenberg bloklar\u0131 ve k\u0131sa kodlar (shortcode) aras\u0131ndaki tam e\u015flik (parity) sa\u011fland\u0131; 19/19 deterministic y\xfczey do\u011fruland\u0131.","date":"2026-02-18T09:00:00.000Z","tags":[{"inline":true,"label":"release","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/release"},{"inline":true,"label":"update","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/update"},{"inline":true,"label":"gutenberg","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/gutenberg"},{"inline":true,"label":"blocks","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/blocks"},{"inline":true,"label":"shortcode","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/shortcode"},{"inline":true,"label":"mhm-rentiva","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/mhm-rentiva"}],"readingTime":0.82,"hasTruncateMarker":true,"authors":[{"name":"MaxHandMade","title":"Maintainer","url":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade","imageURL":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade.png","key":"maxhandmade","page":null}],"frontMatter":{"slug":"v4.10.0-release-summary","title":"MHM Rentiva v4.10.0: Block/Shortcode Parity Stabilizasyonu","authors":["maxhandmade"],"tags":["release","update","gutenberg","blocks","shortcode","mhm-rentiva"],"date":"2026-02-18T09:00"},"unlisted":false,"prevItem":{"title":"MHM Rentiva v4.21.2: Vendor Y\xf6netimi ve Finansal Mimari Devrimi","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/v4.21.2-release-summary"},"nextItem":{"title":"MHM Rentiva v4.9.8: URL Tutarl\u0131l\u0131\u011f\u0131 ve WooCommerce \u0130yile\u015ftirmeleri","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/v4.9.8-release-summary"}},"content":"MHM Rentiva **v4.10.0** s\xfcr\xfcm\xfc yay\u0131nland\u0131! Bu b\xfcy\xfck g\xfcncelleme ile Gutenberg bloklar\u0131 ve k\u0131sa kodlar (shortcode) aras\u0131ndaki tam e\u015flik (parity) sa\u011fland\u0131; 19/19 deterministic y\xfczey do\u011fruland\u0131.\\n\\n\x3c!--truncate--\x3e\\n\\n## \ud83d\ude80 De\u011fi\u015fiklik Kayd\u0131\\n\\n| T\xfcr | A\xe7\u0131klama |\\n|-----|----------|\\n| \ud83c\udfaf E\u015flik (Parity) | Block \u2194 Shortcode tam e\u015fli\u011fi sa\u011fland\u0131 \u2014 19/19 deterministic y\xfczey do\u011fruland\u0131. |\\n| \ud83d\udd17 E\u015fleme (Mapping) | `vehicle-comparison`, `booking-form` ve `testimonials` bloklar\u0131 i\xe7in deterministik alias e\u015flemesi eklendi. |\\n| \ud83d\udd04 D\xf6n\xfc\u015f\xfcm (Transform) | `showFeatures` de\u011fer d\xf6n\xfc\u015f\xfcm\xfc kapsam izolasyonuyla stabilize edildi (boolean \u2192 `all`/`basic`). |\\n| \ud83d\udee1\ufe0f G\xfcvenlik | Booking form dinamik varsay\u0131lan korumas\u0131 eklendi (`defaultDays`/`minDays`/`maxDays` statik override engellendi). |\\n| \ud83d\udccb Denetim | 19/19 Light Parity Audit tam kan\u0131t zinciriyle tamamland\u0131. |\\n| \u2705 Kalite Kap\u0131lar\u0131 | PHPCS, Plugin Check, PHPUnit \u2014 0 hata, tam suite ge\xe7i\u015fi. |\\n\\n### Detaylar\\n\\nBu s\xfcr\xfcm, MHM Rentiva\'n\u0131n blok ve k\u0131sa kod \xe7\u0131kt\u0131lar\u0131n\u0131 birbirinin ayn\u0131s\u0131 haline getiren kapsaml\u0131 bir stabilizasyon \xe7al\u0131\u015fmas\u0131n\u0131n \xfcr\xfcn\xfcd\xfcr. Art\u0131k ayn\u0131 i\xe7erik hem Gutenberg blo\u011fu hem de `[mhm_rentiva_*]` k\u0131sa kodu olarak eklendi\u011finde birebir ayn\u0131 HTML \xe7\u0131kt\u0131s\u0131 ve davran\u0131\u015f elde edilmektedir.\\n\\nKalite kap\u0131lar\u0131 post-bump olarak do\u011fruland\u0131:\\n\\n| Kap\u0131 | Sonu\xe7 |\\n|------|-------|\\n| PHPCS | \u2705 0 hata |\\n| Plugin Check | \u2705 PASS (exit code 0) |\\n| PHPUnit | \u2705 216 test, 0 ba\u015far\u0131s\u0131zl\u0131k |"},{"id":"v4.9.8-release-summary","metadata":{"permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/v4.9.8-release-summary","editUrl":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade/mhm-rentiva-docs/tree/main/blog/2026-02-09-v4.9.8-release.md","source":"@site/i18n/tr/docusaurus-plugin-content-blog/2026-02-09-v4.9.8-release.md","title":"MHM Rentiva v4.9.8: URL Tutarl\u0131l\u0131\u011f\u0131 ve WooCommerce \u0130yile\u015ftirmeleri","description":"MHM Rentiva v4.9.8 s\xfcr\xfcm\xfc yay\u0131nland\u0131! Bu g\xfcncelleme ile WooCommerce entegrasyonu g\xfc\xe7lendirildi ve kal\u0131c\u0131 link (permalink) yap\u0131s\u0131ndaki tutarl\u0131l\u0131k art\u0131r\u0131ld\u0131.","date":"2026-02-09T09:00:00.000Z","tags":[{"inline":true,"label":"release","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/release"},{"inline":true,"label":"update","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/update"},{"inline":true,"label":"woocommerce","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/woocommerce"},{"inline":true,"label":"mhm-rentiva","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/mhm-rentiva"}],"readingTime":0.43,"hasTruncateMarker":true,"authors":[{"name":"MaxHandMade","title":"Maintainer","url":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade","imageURL":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade.png","key":"maxhandmade","page":null}],"frontMatter":{"slug":"v4.9.8-release-summary","title":"MHM Rentiva v4.9.8: URL Tutarl\u0131l\u0131\u011f\u0131 ve WooCommerce \u0130yile\u015ftirmeleri","authors":["maxhandmade"],"tags":["release","update","woocommerce","mhm-rentiva"],"date":"2026-02-09T09:00"},"unlisted":false,"prevItem":{"title":"MHM Rentiva v4.10.0: Block/Shortcode Parity Stabilizasyonu","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/v4.10.0-release-summary"},"nextItem":{"title":"MHM Rentiva v4.9.7: Gutenberg UI/UX Standardizasyonu","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/v4.9.7-release-summary"}},"content":"MHM Rentiva **v4.9.8** s\xfcr\xfcm\xfc yay\u0131nland\u0131! Bu g\xfcncelleme ile WooCommerce entegrasyonu g\xfc\xe7lendirildi ve kal\u0131c\u0131 link (permalink) yap\u0131s\u0131ndaki tutarl\u0131l\u0131k art\u0131r\u0131ld\u0131.\\n\\n\x3c!--truncate--\x3e\\n\\n## \ud83d\ude80 De\u011fi\u015fiklik Kayd\u0131\\n\\n| T\xfcr | A\xe7\u0131klama |\\n|-----|----------|\\n| \ud83d\udee0\ufe0f D\xfczeltme | WooCommerce Hesab\u0131m u\xe7 noktalar\u0131nda fiziksel sayfa k\u0131sa isimlerine (slug) mutlak \xf6ncelik verildi. |\\n| \u26a1 \u0130yile\u015ftirme | Entegre panel d\xfczeni korundu; \xf6zel linklerde (\xf6rn. /favorilerim/) d\u0131\u015fa y\xf6nlendirme sorunu giderildi. |\\n| \u2699\ufe0f Kararl\u0131l\u0131k | URL tutarl\u0131l\u0131\u011f\u0131 i\xe7in kal\u0131c\u0131 linklerin (rewrite rules) otomatik yenilenmesi sa\u011fland\u0131. |\\n\\n### Detaylar\\nBu s\xfcr\xfcm, kullan\u0131c\u0131lar\u0131m\u0131z\u0131n \\"Hesab\u0131m\\" panelindeki deneyimini p\xfcr\xfczs\xfcz hale getirmeye odaklan\u0131yor. \xd6zellikle \xf6zel sayfa yap\u0131s\u0131 kullanan temalarda ya\u015fanan y\xf6nlendirme sorunlar\u0131 giderilerek sistem daha kararl\u0131 hale getirildi."},{"id":"v4.9.7-release-summary","metadata":{"permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/v4.9.7-release-summary","editUrl":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade/mhm-rentiva-docs/tree/main/blog/2026-02-08-v4.9.7-release.md","source":"@site/i18n/tr/docusaurus-plugin-content-blog/2026-02-08-v4.9.7-release.md","title":"MHM Rentiva v4.9.7: Gutenberg UI/UX Standardizasyonu","description":"MHM Rentiva v4.9.7 s\xfcr\xfcm\xfc yay\u0131nland\u0131! Bu g\xfcncelleme ile Gutenberg blok edit\xf6r\xfc deneyimi standartla\u015ft\u0131r\u0131ld\u0131 ve konsol uyar\u0131lar\u0131 temizlendi.","date":"2026-02-08T09:00:00.000Z","tags":[{"inline":true,"label":"release","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/release"},{"inline":true,"label":"update","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/update"},{"inline":true,"label":"gutenberg","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/gutenberg"},{"inline":true,"label":"ui-ux","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/ui-ux"}],"readingTime":0.37,"hasTruncateMarker":true,"authors":[{"name":"MaxHandMade","title":"Maintainer","url":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade","imageURL":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade.png","key":"maxhandmade","page":null}],"frontMatter":{"slug":"v4.9.7-release-summary","title":"MHM Rentiva v4.9.7: Gutenberg UI/UX Standardizasyonu","authors":["maxhandmade"],"tags":["release","update","gutenberg","ui-ux"],"date":"2026-02-08T09:00"},"unlisted":false,"prevItem":{"title":"MHM Rentiva v4.9.8: URL Tutarl\u0131l\u0131\u011f\u0131 ve WooCommerce \u0130yile\u015ftirmeleri","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/v4.9.8-release-summary"},"nextItem":{"title":"MHM Rentiva v4.9.6: Transfer Mod\xfcl\xfc ve B\xfcy\xfck Bak\u0131m","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/v4.9.6-release-summary"}},"content":"MHM Rentiva **v4.9.7** s\xfcr\xfcm\xfc yay\u0131nland\u0131! Bu g\xfcncelleme ile Gutenberg blok edit\xf6r\xfc deneyimi standartla\u015ft\u0131r\u0131ld\u0131 ve konsol uyar\u0131lar\u0131 temizlendi.\\n\\n\x3c!--truncate--\x3e\\n\\n## \ud83d\ude80 De\u011fi\u015fiklik Kayd\u0131\\n\\n| T\xfcr | A\xe7\u0131klama |\\n|-----|----------|\\n| \u2728 \xd6zellik | Gutenberg blok kenar \xe7ubuklar\u0131 (InspectorControls) tutarl\u0131 UI/UX i\xe7in standartla\u015ft\u0131r\u0131ld\u0131. |\\n| \ud83d\udee0\ufe0f D\xfczeltme | Blok edit\xf6r\xfcndeki konsol uyar\u0131lar\u0131 giderilerek kararl\u0131l\u0131k art\u0131r\u0131ld\u0131. |\\n| \u26a1 \u0130yile\u015ftirme | Proje dok\xfcmantasyonu ve kurallar\u0131 g\xfcncellendi. |\\n\\n### Detaylar\\nEdit\xf6r taraf\u0131ndaki kullan\u0131c\u0131 deneyimini iyile\u015ftirmek ad\u0131na Gutenberg blok kontrolleri daha d\xfczenli hale getirildi. Arka planda \xe7al\u0131\u015fan scriptlerdeki ufak hatalar giderilerek temiz bir \xe7al\u0131\u015fma ortam\u0131 sa\u011fland\u0131."},{"id":"v4.9.6-release-summary","metadata":{"permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/v4.9.6-release-summary","editUrl":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade/mhm-rentiva-docs/tree/main/blog/2026-02-02-v4.9.6-release.md","source":"@site/i18n/tr/docusaurus-plugin-content-blog/2026-02-02-v4.9.6-release.md","title":"MHM Rentiva v4.9.6: Transfer Mod\xfcl\xfc ve B\xfcy\xfck Bak\u0131m","description":"MHM Rentiva v4.9.6 s\xfcr\xfcm\xfc yay\u0131nland\u0131! Bu s\xfcr\xfcm, Transfer Mod\xfcl\xfc entegrasyonu ve kapsaml\u0131 veritaban\u0131 ta\u015f\u0131ma mant\u0131\u011f\u0131 gibi kritik g\xfcncellemeler i\xe7ermektedir.","date":"2026-02-02T09:00:00.000Z","tags":[{"inline":true,"label":"release","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/release"},{"inline":true,"label":"update","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/update"},{"inline":true,"label":"transfer","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/transfer"},{"inline":true,"label":"performance","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/performance"}],"readingTime":0.5,"hasTruncateMarker":true,"authors":[{"name":"MaxHandMade","title":"Maintainer","url":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade","imageURL":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade.png","key":"maxhandmade","page":null}],"frontMatter":{"slug":"v4.9.6-release-summary","title":"MHM Rentiva v4.9.6: Transfer Mod\xfcl\xfc ve B\xfcy\xfck Bak\u0131m","authors":["maxhandmade"],"tags":["release","update","transfer","performance"],"date":"2026-02-02T09:00"},"unlisted":false,"prevItem":{"title":"MHM Rentiva v4.9.7: Gutenberg UI/UX Standardizasyonu","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/v4.9.7-release-summary"},"nextItem":{"title":"MHM Rentiva v4.6.7: G\xfcvenlik ve Performans Optimizasyonu","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/v4.6.7-release-summary"}},"content":"MHM Rentiva **v4.9.6** s\xfcr\xfcm\xfc yay\u0131nland\u0131! Bu s\xfcr\xfcm, Transfer Mod\xfcl\xfc entegrasyonu ve kapsaml\u0131 veritaban\u0131 ta\u015f\u0131ma mant\u0131\u011f\u0131 gibi kritik g\xfcncellemeler i\xe7ermektedir.\\n\\n\x3c!--truncate--\x3e\\n\\n## \ud83d\ude80 De\u011fi\u015fiklik Kayd\u0131\\n\\n| T\xfcr | A\xe7\u0131klama |\\n|-----|----------|\\n| \u2728 \xd6zellik | Transfer Mod\xfcl\xfc: \xd6n ek standardizasyonu (rentiva_) ve veritaban\u0131 ta\u015f\u0131ma mant\u0131\u011f\u0131 tamamland\u0131. |\\n| \u26a1 Performans | Genel kod optimizasyonu ve performans iyile\u015ftirmeleri yap\u0131ld\u0131. |\\n| \ud83d\udee0\ufe0f D\xfczeltme | M\xfcsaitlik Takvimi i\xe7in HTML yap\u0131s\u0131 daha iyi eri\u015filebilirlik i\xe7in g\xfcncellendi. |\\n| \ud83c\udfa8 Stil | Daha iyi bak\u0131m i\xe7in CSS mimarisi temizlendi ve yeniden yap\u0131land\u0131r\u0131ld\u0131. |\\n| \ud83c\udf10 i18n | Yeni \xe7eviri dosyalar\u0131 eklendi ve mevcut \xe7eviriler iyile\u015ftirildi. |\\n\\n### Detaylar\\nY\xfcksek performansl\u0131 bir altyap\u0131 i\xe7in CSS ve PHP taraf\u0131nda b\xfcy\xfck \xe7apl\u0131 temizlik yap\u0131ld\u0131. Transfer mod\xfcl\xfcn\xfcn veritaban\u0131 yap\u0131s\u0131 standartlara uygun hale getirilerek sistem kararl\u0131l\u0131\u011f\u0131 art\u0131r\u0131ld\u0131."},{"id":"v4.6.7-release-summary","metadata":{"permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/v4.6.7-release-summary","editUrl":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade/mhm-rentiva-docs/tree/main/blog/2026-02-01-v4.6.7-release.md","source":"@site/i18n/tr/docusaurus-plugin-content-blog/2026-02-01-v4.6.7-release.md","title":"MHM Rentiva v4.6.7: G\xfcvenlik ve Performans Optimizasyonu","description":"MHM Rentiva v4.6.7 s\xfcr\xfcm\xfc yay\u0131nland\u0131! Bu g\xfcncelleme ile y\xf6nlendirme g\xfcvenli\u011fi, SQL optimizasyonu ve stil y\xf6netimi modern standartlara ta\u015f\u0131nd\u0131.","date":"2026-02-01T09:00:00.000Z","tags":[{"inline":true,"label":"release","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/release"},{"inline":true,"label":"update","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/update"},{"inline":true,"label":"security","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/security"},{"inline":true,"label":"performance","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/performance"}],"readingTime":0.42,"hasTruncateMarker":true,"authors":[{"name":"MaxHandMade","title":"Maintainer","url":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade","imageURL":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade.png","key":"maxhandmade","page":null}],"frontMatter":{"slug":"v4.6.7-release-summary","title":"MHM Rentiva v4.6.7: G\xfcvenlik ve Performans Optimizasyonu","authors":["maxhandmade"],"tags":["release","update","security","performance"],"date":"2026-02-01T09:00"},"unlisted":false,"prevItem":{"title":"MHM Rentiva v4.9.6: Transfer Mod\xfcl\xfc ve B\xfcy\xfck Bak\u0131m","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/v4.9.6-release-summary"},"nextItem":{"title":"MHM Rentiva v4.6.6: Rezervasyon Formu ve Fiyatland\u0131rma \u0130yile\u015ftirmeleri","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/v4.6.6-release-summary"}},"content":"MHM Rentiva **v4.6.7** s\xfcr\xfcm\xfc yay\u0131nland\u0131! Bu g\xfcncelleme ile y\xf6nlendirme g\xfcvenli\u011fi, SQL optimizasyonu ve stil y\xf6netimi modern standartlara ta\u015f\u0131nd\u0131.\\n\\n\x3c!--truncate--\x3e\\n\\n## \ud83d\ude80 De\u011fi\u015fiklik Kayd\u0131\\n\\n| T\xfcr | A\xe7\u0131klama |\\n|-----|----------|\\n| \ud83d\udee1\ufe0f G\xfcvenlik | Y\xf6nlendirme g\xfcvenli\u011fini art\u0131rmak i\xe7in `wp_safe_redirect` kullan\u0131m\u0131na ge\xe7ildi. |\\n| \ud83d\udee1\ufe0f G\xfcvenlik | `SecurityHelper::safe_output()` metodu ba\u011flam do\u011frulamas\u0131 ve JSON deste\u011fiyle modernize edildi. |\\n| \u26a1 Performans | SQL transient silme i\u015flemi, native `delete_transient()` fonksiyonuna \xe7evrildi. |\\n| \ud83c\udfa8 Stil | Sat\u0131r i\xe7i CSS kodlar\u0131 `wp_add_inline_style` API\'sine ta\u015f\u0131narak standartla\u015ft\u0131r\u0131ld\u0131. |\\n\\n### Detaylar\\nEklentinin \xe7ekirdek fonksiyonlar\u0131 daha g\xfcvenli ve performansl\u0131 hale getirildi. \xd6zellikle y\xf6nlendirme ve veri \xe7\u0131kt\u0131 i\u015flemleri WordPress\'in en g\xfcncel g\xfcvenlik protokollerine g\xf6re optimize edildi."},{"id":"v4.6.6-release-summary","metadata":{"permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/v4.6.6-release-summary","editUrl":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade/mhm-rentiva-docs/tree/main/blog/2026-01-28-v4.6.6-release.md","source":"@site/i18n/tr/docusaurus-plugin-content-blog/2026-01-28-v4.6.6-release.md","title":"MHM Rentiva v4.6.6: Rezervasyon Formu ve Fiyatland\u0131rma \u0130yile\u015ftirmeleri","description":"MHM Rentiva v4.6.6 s\xfcr\xfcm\xfc yay\u0131nland\u0131! Bu g\xfcncelleme, rezervasyon formundaki g\xf6rsel hatalar\u0131 giderir ve yeni bir fiyatland\u0131rma detay\u0131 ekler.","date":"2026-01-28T09:00:00.000Z","tags":[{"inline":true,"label":"release","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/release"},{"inline":true,"label":"update","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/update"},{"inline":true,"label":"interface","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/interface"},{"inline":true,"label":"booking","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/booking"}],"readingTime":0.51,"hasTruncateMarker":true,"authors":[{"name":"MaxHandMade","title":"Maintainer","url":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade","imageURL":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade.png","key":"maxhandmade","page":null}],"frontMatter":{"slug":"v4.6.6-release-summary","title":"MHM Rentiva v4.6.6: Rezervasyon Formu ve Fiyatland\u0131rma \u0130yile\u015ftirmeleri","authors":["maxhandmade"],"tags":["release","update","interface","booking"],"date":"2026-01-28T09:00"},"unlisted":false,"prevItem":{"title":"MHM Rentiva v4.6.7: G\xfcvenlik ve Performans Optimizasyonu","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/v4.6.7-release-summary"},"nextItem":{"title":"MHM Rentiva v4.6.5: WPCS Uyumlulu\u011fu ve Kod Standartlar\u0131","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/v4.6.5-release-summary"}},"content":"MHM Rentiva **v4.6.6** s\xfcr\xfcm\xfc yay\u0131nland\u0131! Bu g\xfcncelleme, rezervasyon formundaki g\xf6rsel hatalar\u0131 giderir ve yeni bir fiyatland\u0131rma detay\u0131 ekler.\\n\\n\x3c!--truncate--\x3e\\n\\n## \ud83d\ude80 De\u011fi\u015fiklik Kayd\u0131\\n\\n| T\xfcr | A\xe7\u0131klama |\\n|-----|----------|\\n| \ud83d\udee0\ufe0f D\xfczeltme | Rezervasyon formundaki ara\xe7 \xf6zellik ikonlar\u0131n\u0131n (yak\u0131t, vites vb.) kaybolma sorunu giderildi. |\\n| \ud83d\udee0\ufe0f D\xfczeltme | Ara\xe7 \xf6zellik verilerinin i\u015flenmesi s\u0131ras\u0131nda olu\u015fan mant\u0131ksal hatalar d\xfczeltildi. |\\n| \u2728 \xd6zellik | Rezervasyon formu fiyat detay\u0131na \'Hafta Sonu Fark\u0131\' g\xf6sterimi eklendi. |\\n| \u26a1 \u0130yile\u015ftirme | Rezervasyon formu g\xf6rselle\u015ftirmesi ve ikon boyutland\u0131rmalar\u0131 optimize edildi. |\\n| \ud83e\uddf9 Temizlik | \xc7ak\u0131\u015fan eski CSS kodlar\u0131 temizlendi ve modern yap\u0131ya ge\xe7ildi. |\\n\\n### Detaylar\\nKullan\u0131c\u0131 deneyimini iyile\u015ftirmek ad\u0131na rezervasyon formundaki ikon sorunlar\u0131 \xe7\xf6z\xfcld\xfc ve fiyatland\u0131rma \u015feffafl\u0131\u011f\u0131 i\xe7in hafta sonu fark\u0131 detay\u0131 eklendi. CSS yap\u0131s\u0131 daha sade ve h\u0131zl\u0131 hale getirildi."},{"id":"v4.6.5-release-summary","metadata":{"permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/v4.6.5-release-summary","editUrl":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade/mhm-rentiva-docs/tree/main/blog/2026-01-26-v4.6.5-release.md","source":"@site/i18n/tr/docusaurus-plugin-content-blog/2026-01-26-v4.6.5-release.md","title":"MHM Rentiva v4.6.5: WPCS Uyumlulu\u011fu ve Kod Standartlar\u0131","description":"MHM Rentiva v4.6.5 s\xfcr\xfcm\xfc yay\u0131nland\u0131! Bu b\xfcy\xfck \xf6l\xe7ekli altyap\u0131 g\xfcncellemesi ile 110.000+ sat\u0131r kod WordPress standartlar\u0131na (WPCS) uyumlu hale getirildi.","date":"2026-01-26T15:00:00.000Z","tags":[{"inline":true,"label":"release","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/release"},{"inline":true,"label":"update","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/update"},{"inline":true,"label":"security","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/security"},{"inline":true,"label":"refactoring","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/refactoring"}],"readingTime":0.43,"hasTruncateMarker":true,"authors":[{"name":"MaxHandMade","title":"Maintainer","url":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade","imageURL":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade.png","key":"maxhandmade","page":null}],"frontMatter":{"slug":"v4.6.5-release-summary","title":"MHM Rentiva v4.6.5: WPCS Uyumlulu\u011fu ve Kod Standartlar\u0131","authors":["maxhandmade"],"tags":["release","update","security","refactoring"],"date":"2026-01-26T15:00"},"unlisted":false,"prevItem":{"title":"MHM Rentiva v4.6.6: Rezervasyon Formu ve Fiyatland\u0131rma \u0130yile\u015ftirmeleri","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/v4.6.6-release-summary"},"nextItem":{"title":"MHM Rentiva v4.6.4: Veri B\xfct\xfcnl\xfc\u011f\xfc ve \xc7\u0131kt\u0131 G\xfcvenli\u011fi","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/v4.6.4-release-summary"}},"content":"MHM Rentiva **v4.6.5** s\xfcr\xfcm\xfc yay\u0131nland\u0131! Bu b\xfcy\xfck \xf6l\xe7ekli altyap\u0131 g\xfcncellemesi ile 110.000+ sat\u0131r kod WordPress standartlar\u0131na (WPCS) uyumlu hale getirildi.\\n\\n\x3c!--truncate--\x3e\\n\\n## \ud83d\ude80 De\u011fi\u015fiklik Kayd\u0131\\n\\n| T\xfcr | A\xe7\u0131klama |\\n|-----|----------|\\n| \ud83d\udee1\ufe0f G\xfcvenlik | 50+ WPCS g\xfcvenlik uyar\u0131s\u0131 \xe7\xf6z\xfcld\xfc (Girdi Sanitizasyonu & DB \u0130nterpolasyonu). |\\n| \ud83d\udee1\ufe0f G\xfcvenlik | Handler.php ve AccountController.php XSS\'e kar\u015f\u0131 g\xfc\xe7lendirildi. |\\n| \u2699\ufe0f Kararl\u0131l\u0131k | Eski `error_log` yap\u0131s\u0131 modern `AdvancedLogger` mimarisiyle de\u011fi\u015ftirildi. |\\n| \u26a1 \u0130yile\u015ftirme | 110.000+ WordPress Kodlama Standartlar\u0131 (WPCS) uyumsuzlu\u011fu otomatik d\xfczeltildi. |\\n\\n### Detaylar\\nBu g\xfcncelleme eklentimizin gelecekteki geli\u015fimini sa\u011flam bir temele oturtmaktad\u0131r. Geni\u015f \xe7apl\u0131 kod standartlar\u0131 denetimi ile hem g\xfcvenlik hem de bak\u0131m kolayl\u0131\u011f\u0131 en \xfcst d\xfczeye \xe7\u0131kar\u0131ld\u0131."},{"id":"v4.6.4-release-summary","metadata":{"permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/v4.6.4-release-summary","editUrl":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade/mhm-rentiva-docs/tree/main/blog/2026-01-26-v4.6.4-release.md","source":"@site/i18n/tr/docusaurus-plugin-content-blog/2026-01-26-v4.6.4-release.md","title":"MHM Rentiva v4.6.4: Veri B\xfct\xfcnl\xfc\u011f\xfc ve \xc7\u0131kt\u0131 G\xfcvenli\u011fi","description":"MHM Rentiva v4.6.4 s\xfcr\xfcm\xfc yay\u0131nland\u0131! Bu s\xfcr\xfcmde y\xf6netici paneli \xe7\u0131kt\u0131 g\xfcvenli\u011fi ve para birimi sembollerindeki tutarl\u0131l\u0131k hatalar\u0131 giderildi.","date":"2026-01-26T09:00:00.000Z","tags":[{"inline":true,"label":"release","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/release"},{"inline":true,"label":"update","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/update"},{"inline":true,"label":"security","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/security"},{"inline":true,"label":"data-integrity","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/data-integrity"}],"readingTime":0.5,"hasTruncateMarker":true,"authors":[{"name":"MaxHandMade","title":"Maintainer","url":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade","imageURL":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade.png","key":"maxhandmade","page":null}],"frontMatter":{"slug":"v4.6.4-release-summary","title":"MHM Rentiva v4.6.4: Veri B\xfct\xfcnl\xfc\u011f\xfc ve \xc7\u0131kt\u0131 G\xfcvenli\u011fi","authors":["maxhandmade"],"tags":["release","update","security","data-integrity"],"date":"2026-01-26T09:00"},"unlisted":false,"prevItem":{"title":"MHM Rentiva v4.6.5: WPCS Uyumlulu\u011fu ve Kod Standartlar\u0131","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/v4.6.5-release-summary"},"nextItem":{"title":"MHM Rentiva v4.6.3: SQL G\xfcvenli\u011fi ve REST API Kararl\u0131l\u0131\u011f\u0131","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/v4.6.3-release-summary"}},"content":"MHM Rentiva **v4.6.4** s\xfcr\xfcm\xfc yay\u0131nland\u0131! Bu s\xfcr\xfcmde y\xf6netici paneli \xe7\u0131kt\u0131 g\xfcvenli\u011fi ve para birimi sembollerindeki tutarl\u0131l\u0131k hatalar\u0131 giderildi.\\n\\n\x3c!--truncate--\x3e\\n\\n## \ud83d\ude80 De\u011fi\u015fiklik Kayd\u0131\\n\\n| T\xfcr | A\xe7\u0131klama |\\n|-----|----------|\\n| \ud83d\udee1\ufe0f G\xfcvenlik | Admin sekmelerinde `esc_html` ve `wp_kses_post` kullan\u0131larak \xe7\u0131kt\u0131 ka\xe7\u0131rma i\u015flemleri g\xfc\xe7lendirildi. |\\n| \u2699\ufe0f Kararl\u0131l\u0131k | AddonManager ve Rezervasyon Meta Kutular\u0131ndaki fiyat/ID alanlar\u0131 i\xe7in sanitizasyon iyile\u015ftirildi. |\\n| \u26a1 \u0130yile\u015ftirme | Rezervasyon D\xfczenleme ekranlar\u0131ndaki hardcoded para birimi sembol sorunlar\u0131 giderildi. |\\n| \u26a1 \u0130yile\u015ftirme | Ara\xe7 kolonlar\u0131 ve sistem bilgisi sayfalar\u0131ndaki SQL sorgular\u0131 optimize edildi. |\\n| \u26a1 \u0130yile\u015ftirme | Manuel rezarvasyon ve ara\xe7 y\xf6netiminde kalan baz\u0131 T\xfcrk\xe7e dizeler \u0130ngilizce\'ye \xe7evrildi. |\\n\\n### Detaylar\\nY\xf6netici panelindeki veri giri\u015f ve \xe7\u0131k\u0131\u015f noktalar\u0131nda g\xfcvenlik standartlar\u0131 art\u0131r\u0131ld\u0131. \xd6zellikle fiyatland\u0131rma alanlar\u0131ndaki sanitizasyon iyile\u015ftirmeleri veri b\xfct\xfcnl\xfc\u011f\xfcn\xfc garanti alt\u0131na almaktad\u0131r."},{"id":"v4.6.3-release-summary","metadata":{"permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/v4.6.3-release-summary","editUrl":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade/mhm-rentiva-docs/tree/main/blog/2026-01-25-v4.6.3-release.md","source":"@site/i18n/tr/docusaurus-plugin-content-blog/2026-01-25-v4.6.3-release.md","title":"MHM Rentiva v4.6.3: SQL G\xfcvenli\u011fi ve REST API Kararl\u0131l\u0131\u011f\u0131","description":"MHM Rentiva v4.6.3 s\xfcr\xfcm\xfc yay\u0131nland\u0131! Bu g\xfcncelleme, SQL Injection korumas\u0131 ve AJAX g\xfcvenilirli\u011fi \xfczerine \xf6nemli iyile\u015ftirmeler i\xe7ermektedir.","date":"2026-01-25T09:00:00.000Z","tags":[{"inline":true,"label":"release","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/release"},{"inline":true,"label":"update","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/update"},{"inline":true,"label":"security","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/security"},{"inline":true,"label":"rest-api","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/rest-api"}],"readingTime":0.55,"hasTruncateMarker":true,"authors":[{"name":"MaxHandMade","title":"Maintainer","url":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade","imageURL":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade.png","key":"maxhandmade","page":null}],"frontMatter":{"slug":"v4.6.3-release-summary","title":"MHM Rentiva v4.6.3: SQL G\xfcvenli\u011fi ve REST API Kararl\u0131l\u0131\u011f\u0131","authors":["maxhandmade"],"tags":["release","update","security","rest-api"],"date":"2026-01-25T09:00"},"unlisted":false,"prevItem":{"title":"MHM Rentiva v4.6.4: Veri B\xfct\xfcnl\xfc\u011f\xfc ve \xc7\u0131kt\u0131 G\xfcvenli\u011fi","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/v4.6.4-release-summary"},"nextItem":{"title":"MHM Rentiva v4.6.2: G\xfcvenlik Tahkimat\u0131 ve WPCS Uyumlulu\u011fu","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/v4.6.2-security-update"}},"content":"MHM Rentiva **v4.6.3** s\xfcr\xfcm\xfc yay\u0131nland\u0131! Bu g\xfcncelleme, SQL Injection korumas\u0131 ve AJAX g\xfcvenilirli\u011fi \xfczerine \xf6nemli iyile\u015ftirmeler i\xe7ermektedir.\\n\\n\x3c!--truncate--\x3e\\n\\n## \ud83d\ude80 De\u011fi\u015fiklik Kayd\u0131\\n\\n| T\xfcr | A\xe7\u0131klama |\\n|-----|----------|\\n| \ud83d\udee1\ufe0f G\xfcvenlik | Mesaj arama sorgular\u0131 prepared statements kullan\u0131larak SQL Injection\'a kar\u015f\u0131 g\xfc\xe7lendirildi. |\\n| \ud83d\udee1\ufe0f G\xfcvenlik | REST API entegrasyon ayarlar\u0131n\u0131n backend mimarisi, AJAX buton g\xfcvenilirli\u011fini art\u0131racak \u015fekilde g\xfcncellendi. |\\n| \u2699\ufe0f Kararl\u0131l\u0131k | Asenkron isteklerde \'-1\' hatas\u0131n\u0131 \xf6nlemek i\xe7in AJAX hook kay\u0131t sistemi iyile\u015ftirildi. |\\n| \u2699\ufe0f Kararl\u0131l\u0131k | REST ayarlar\u0131nda IP listesi sanitizasyon hatalar\u0131 giderildi. |\\n| \u26a1 \u0130yile\u015ftirme | Proje kaynak kodu dok\xfcmantasyonu WPCS uyumlulu\u011fu i\xe7in tamamen \u0130ngilizce\'ye \xe7evrildi. |\\n\\n### Detaylar\\nBu s\xfcr\xfcmle birlikte mesajla\u015fma sistemindeki arama fonksiyonlar\u0131 ve AJAX tabanl\u0131 ayar kaydediciler daha g\xfcvenli ve kararl\u0131 hale getirildi. \xd6zellikle geli\u015ftiriciler i\xe7in kod taban\u0131ndaki yorum sat\u0131rlar\u0131 d\xfcnya standartlar\u0131na (WPCS) uygun hale getirildi."},{"id":"v4.6.2-security-update","metadata":{"permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/v4.6.2-security-update","editUrl":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade/mhm-rentiva-docs/tree/main/blog/2026-01-22-v4.6.2-release.md","source":"@site/i18n/tr/docusaurus-plugin-content-blog/2026-01-22-v4.6.2-release.md","title":"MHM Rentiva v4.6.2: G\xfcvenlik Tahkimat\u0131 ve WPCS Uyumlulu\u011fu","description":"MHM Rentiva v4.6.2 yay\u0131nda! Bu s\xfcr\xfcm, eklentinin t\xfcm mod\xfcllerini kapsayan devasa bir g\xfcvenlik ve altyap\u0131 g\xfc\xe7lendirme g\xfcncellemesidir. Yeni \xf6zellik eklemekten ziyade, mevcut sistemin a\u015f\u0131lmaz bir kale haline getirilmesine odakland\u0131k.","date":"2026-01-22T06:00:00.000Z","tags":[{"inline":true,"label":"release","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/release"},{"inline":true,"label":"security","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/security"},{"inline":true,"label":"wpcs","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/wpcs"},{"inline":true,"label":"update","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/update"}],"readingTime":1.21,"hasTruncateMarker":true,"authors":[{"name":"MaxHandMade","title":"Maintainer","url":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade","imageURL":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade.png","key":"maxhandmade","page":null}],"frontMatter":{"slug":"v4.6.2-security-update","title":"MHM Rentiva v4.6.2: G\xfcvenlik Tahkimat\u0131 ve WPCS Uyumlulu\u011fu","authors":["maxhandmade"],"tags":["release","security","wpcs","update"],"date":"2026-01-22T06:00"},"unlisted":false,"prevItem":{"title":"MHM Rentiva v4.6.3: SQL G\xfcvenli\u011fi ve REST API Kararl\u0131l\u0131\u011f\u0131","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/v4.6.3-release-summary"},"nextItem":{"title":"v4.6.1 Yay\u0131nda! \ud83d\udee1\ufe0f","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/v4-6-1-released"}},"content":"MHM Rentiva **v4.6.2** yay\u0131nda! Bu s\xfcr\xfcm, eklentinin t\xfcm mod\xfcllerini kapsayan devasa bir g\xfcvenlik ve altyap\u0131 g\xfc\xe7lendirme g\xfcncellemesidir. Yeni \xf6zellik eklemekten ziyade, mevcut sistemin **a\u015f\u0131lmaz bir kale** haline getirilmesine odakland\u0131k.\\n\\n\x3c!--truncate--\x3e\\n\\n## \ud83d\udee1\ufe0f G\xfcvenlik Denetimi \xd6zeti\\n\\nSon 24 saat i\xe7inde, MHM Rentiva\'n\u0131n 22 farkl\u0131 mod\xfcl\xfc \xfczerinde sat\u0131r sat\u0131r kod analizi ger\xe7ekle\u015ftirdik. Hedefimiz sadece \\"\xe7al\u0131\u015fan\\" bir eklenti de\u011fil, \\"en g\xfcvenli\\" kiralama eklentisi olmakt\u0131r.\\n\\n\u0130\u015fte bu g\xfcncellemenin karnesi:\\n\\n| Metrik | De\u011fer |\\n|--------|-------|\\n| **Denetlenen Mod\xfcller** | 22 (T\xfcm\xfc) |\\n| **D\xfczenlenen Dosyalar** | 59+ |\\n| **Nonce (CSRF) Yamas\u0131** | 91+ |\\n| **WPCS Uyumlulu\u011fu** | %100 |\\n\\n### Neler De\u011fi\u015fti?\\n\\n#### 1. Tam Kapsaml\u0131 Nonce Korumas\u0131\\nWordPress\'in g\xfcvenlik mekanizmas\u0131 olan `nonce` (number used once) kullan\u0131m\u0131 t\xfcm form ve AJAX i\u015flemlerinde standartla\u015ft\u0131r\u0131ld\u0131. Her bir do\u011frulama i\u015flemi art\u0131k `sanitize_text_field(wp_unslash())` sarmalay\u0131c\u0131s\u0131 ile ekstra bir temizlik katman\u0131ndan ge\xe7iriliyor.\\n\\n#### 2. REST API ve Rate Limiting\\nAPI taraf\u0131nda **H\u0131z S\u0131n\u0131rlama (Rate Limiting)** ve **IP K\u0131s\u0131tlama** mekanizmalar\u0131 \xe7ekirdek yap\u0131ya daha s\u0131k\u0131 entegre edildi. Art\u0131k `CoreSettings` yerine `RESTSettings` \xfczerinden y\xf6netilen bu yap\u0131, yetkisiz eri\u015fim denemelerini an\u0131nda engelliyor.\\n\\n> Detaylar i\xe7in yenilenen [REST API Dok\xfcmantasyonu](../docs/api/overview) sayfas\u0131n\u0131 inceleyebilirsiniz.\\n\\n#### 3. Kod Kalitesi ve PHP 8.4+ Uyumu\\nGelece\u011fe haz\u0131rl\u0131k kapsam\u0131nda, PHP 8.4 ve \xfczeri s\xfcr\xfcmlerde ortaya \xe7\u0131kabilecek \\"Implicit Nullable Parameter\\" uyar\u0131lar\u0131 giderildi. Kod taban\u0131 daha modern, temiz ve hatas\u0131z hale getirildi.\\n\\n## \ud83c\udfd7\ufe0f Yeni Teknik Dok\xfcmantasyon\\n\\nMod\xfcler yap\u0131m\u0131z\u0131 daha iyi anlatabilmek ve geli\u015ftiricilere rehberlik etmek i\xe7in dok\xfcmantasyonumuza yeni bir b\xf6l\xfcm ekledik:\\n\\n*   [**Mod\xfcl Mimarisi ve Teknik Harita:**](../docs/developer/core/technical-architecture) Eklentinin 22 mod\xfcl\xfcn\xfcn ili\u015fkilerini, dosya yap\u0131s\u0131n\u0131 ve g\xfcvenlik durumunu g\xf6steren kapsaml\u0131 bir rehber.\\n\\n---\\n\\nMHM Rentiva ile g\xfcvenli ve performansl\u0131 kiralamalar dileriz! \ud83d\ude80"},{"id":"v4-6-1-released","metadata":{"permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/v4-6-1-released","editUrl":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade/mhm-rentiva-docs/tree/main/blog/2026-01-21-v4-6-1-released.md","source":"@site/i18n/tr/docusaurus-plugin-content-blog/2026-01-21-v4-6-1-released.md","title":"v4.6.1 Yay\u0131nda! \ud83d\udee1\ufe0f","description":"MHM Rentiva v4.6.1 s\xfcr\xfcm\xfc yay\u0131nland\u0131! Bu s\xfcr\xfcm, veri b\xfct\xfcnl\xfc\u011f\xfc, g\xfcvenlik ve WooCommerce entegrasyonu konular\u0131nda kritik iyile\u015ftirmeler i\xe7eren bir g\xfcvenlik ve kararl\u0131l\u0131k g\xfcncellemesidir.","date":"2026-01-21T00:00:00.000Z","tags":[{"inline":true,"label":"release","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/release"},{"inline":true,"label":"update","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/update"},{"inline":true,"label":"v4.6.1","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/v-4-6-1"},{"inline":true,"label":"security","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/security"},{"inline":true,"label":"critical","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/critical"},{"inline":true,"label":"woocommerce","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/woocommerce"}],"readingTime":1.18,"hasTruncateMarker":true,"authors":[{"name":"MaxHandMade","title":"Maintainer","url":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade","imageURL":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade.png","key":"maxhandmade","page":null}],"frontMatter":{"slug":"v4-6-1-released","title":"v4.6.1 Yay\u0131nda! \ud83d\udee1\ufe0f","authors":["maxhandmade"],"tags":["release","update","v4.6.1","security","critical","woocommerce"],"date":"2026-01-21T00:00:00.000Z"},"unlisted":false,"prevItem":{"title":"MHM Rentiva v4.6.2: G\xfcvenlik Tahkimat\u0131 ve WPCS Uyumlulu\u011fu","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/v4.6.2-security-update"},"nextItem":{"title":"v4.6.0 Yay\u0131nda! \ud83d\ude80","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/v4-6-0-released"}},"content":"MHM Rentiva **v4.6.1** s\xfcr\xfcm\xfc yay\u0131nland\u0131! Bu s\xfcr\xfcm, **veri b\xfct\xfcnl\xfc\u011f\xfc**, **g\xfcvenlik** ve **WooCommerce entegrasyonu** konular\u0131nda kritik iyile\u015ftirmeler i\xe7eren bir g\xfcvenlik ve kararl\u0131l\u0131k g\xfcncellemesidir.\\n\\n\x3c!-- truncate --\x3e\\n\\n## \ud83d\udee1\ufe0f Kritik G\xfcvenlik ve Veri Koruma\\n\\n### \ud83e\uddf9 DatabaseCleaner \u0130yile\u015ftirmesi\\nVeritaban\u0131 temizleme arac\u0131m\u0131z, art\u0131k \xe7ok daha ak\u0131ll\u0131 ve g\xfcvenli.\\n- **Geni\u015fletilmi\u015f Koruma:** WooCommerce sipari\u015f ID\'leri, \xf6deme detaylar\u0131 ve m\xfc\u015fteri meta verileri dahil olmak \xfczere **40\'tan fazla kritik meta anahtar** (`_mhm_` prefixli) koruma listesine eklendi.\\n- **Veri Kayb\u0131 \xd6nleme:** Bak\u0131m i\u015flemleri s\u0131ras\u0131nda yanl\u0131\u015fl\u0131kla veri silinmesinin \xf6n\xfcne ge\xe7mek i\xe7in koruma mekanizmalar\u0131 g\xfc\xe7lendirildi.\\n\\n### \ud83d\udd12 SQL G\xfcvenli\u011fi (Hardening)\\nSistem genelinde SQL sorgular\u0131 g\xf6zden ge\xe7irildi ve g\xfcvenlik seviyesi art\u0131r\u0131ld\u0131.\\n- **Prepared Statements:** `BookingColumns` ve `ExportStats` s\u0131n\u0131flar\u0131ndaki dinamik sorgular, SQL Injection risklerine kar\u015f\u0131 `wpdb->prepare()` kullan\u0131larak standardize edildi.\\n\\n## \ud83d\udecd\ufe0f WooCommerce ve \xd6deme \u0130yile\u015ftirmeleri\\n\\n### \u269b\ufe0f Atomik \xc7ak\u0131\u015fma Kilidi (Atomic Overlap Lock)\\nYo\u011fun rezervasyon trafi\u011fi olan siteler i\xe7in hayati bir \xf6zellik eklendi.\\n- **\xc7ift Rezervasyon \xd6nleme:** WooCommerce \xfczerinden ayn\u0131 saniyede gelen rezervasyon isteklerinde \xe7ak\u0131\u015fmay\u0131 \xf6nlemek i\xe7in veritaban\u0131 seviyesinde atomik kilit mekanizmas\u0131 devreye al\u0131nd\u0131.\\n\\n### \ud83d\udcb0 Vergi Hesaplama D\xfczeltmesi\\n- **Do\u011fru Vergi Matrah\u0131:** Depozito \xf6demelerinde verginin sadece \xf6denen depozito \xfczerinden de\u011fil, **toplam rezervasyon tutar\u0131** \xfczerinden hesaplanmas\u0131 sa\u011fland\u0131. Bu sayede faturaland\u0131rma ve muhasebe s\xfcre\xe7leri hatas\u0131z hale getirildi.\\n\\n### \ud83c\udfa8 Kullan\u0131c\u0131 Aray\xfcz\xfc\\n- **\xd6deme Ayarlar\u0131 Uyar\u0131s\u0131:** WooCommerce aktif oldu\u011funda, kullan\u0131c\u0131lar\u0131n yanl\u0131\u015f (lokal) \xf6deme ayarlar\u0131yla vakit kaybetmesini \xf6nlemek i\xe7in \\"\xd6deme i\u015flemleri WooCommerce taraf\u0131ndan y\xf6netilmektedir\\" \u015feklinde bilgilendirici bir uyar\u0131 eklendi.\\n\\n---\\n\\n**Nas\u0131l G\xfcncellerim?**\\nWordPress y\xf6netim panelinizden **Eklentiler** sayfas\u0131n\u0131 ziyaret ederek g\xfcncellemeyi tek t\u0131kla y\xfckleyebilirsiniz. Bu s\xfcr\xfcm **Kritik** olarak i\u015faretlenmi\u015ftir, t\xfcm kullan\u0131c\u0131lar\u0131n en k\u0131sa s\xfcrede ge\xe7i\u015f yapmas\u0131 \xf6nerilir.\\n\\nG\xfcvenli ve keyifli kiralamalar! \ud83d\ude97\ud83d\udca8"},{"id":"v4-6-0-released","metadata":{"permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/v4-6-0-released","editUrl":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade/mhm-rentiva-docs/tree/main/blog/2026-01-16-v4-6-0-released.md","source":"@site/i18n/tr/docusaurus-plugin-content-blog/2026-01-16-v4-6-0-released.md","title":"v4.6.0 Yay\u0131nda! \ud83d\ude80","description":"MHM Rentiva v4.6.0 s\xfcr\xfcm\xfc yay\u0131nland\u0131! Bu s\xfcr\xfcm, uzun zamand\u0131r beklenen VIP Transfer Mod\xfcl\xfc, geli\u015fmi\u015f rota y\xf6netimi ve esnek fiyatland\u0131rma motoru gibi b\xfcy\xfck \xf6zellikler i\xe7eriyor.","date":"2026-01-16T00:00:00.000Z","tags":[{"inline":true,"label":"release","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/release"},{"inline":true,"label":"update","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/update"},{"inline":true,"label":"v4.6.0","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/v-4-6-0"},{"inline":true,"label":"vip-transfer","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/vip-transfer"}],"readingTime":1.17,"hasTruncateMarker":true,"authors":[{"name":"MaxHandMade","title":"Maintainer","url":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade","imageURL":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade.png","key":"maxhandmade","page":null}],"frontMatter":{"slug":"v4-6-0-released","title":"v4.6.0 Yay\u0131nda! \ud83d\ude80","authors":["maxhandmade"],"tags":["release","update","v4.6.0","vip-transfer"],"date":"2026-01-16T00:00:00.000Z"},"unlisted":false,"prevItem":{"title":"v4.6.1 Yay\u0131nda! \ud83d\udee1\ufe0f","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/v4-6-1-released"},"nextItem":{"title":"v4.5.5 Yay\u0131nda! \ud83d\ude80","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/v4-5-5-released"}},"content":"MHM Rentiva **v4.6.0** s\xfcr\xfcm\xfc yay\u0131nland\u0131! Bu s\xfcr\xfcm, uzun zamand\u0131r beklenen **VIP Transfer Mod\xfcl\xfc**, geli\u015fmi\u015f rota y\xf6netimi ve esnek fiyatland\u0131rma motoru gibi b\xfcy\xfck \xf6zellikler i\xe7eriyor.\\n\\n\x3c!-- truncate --\x3e\\n\\n## \ud83c\udf1f \xd6ne \xc7\u0131kanlar\\n\\n### \ud83d\ude80 VIP Transfer Mod\xfcl\xfc (\u015eof\xf6rl\xfc Hizmet)\\nArt\u0131k sadece ara\xe7 kiralama de\u011fil, **VIP Transfer** hizmeti de verebilirsiniz!\\n- **Noktadan Noktaya Transfer:** Belirli lokasyonlar aras\u0131nda sabit veya mesafeye dayal\u0131 fiyatland\u0131rma.\\n- **\u015eof\xf6rl\xfc Ara\xe7 Kiralama:** Saatlik veya g\xfcnl\xfck \u015fof\xf6rl\xfc ara\xe7 opsiyonlar\u0131.\\n- **Ekstra Hizmetler:** Kar\u015f\u0131lama, bebek koltu\u011fu, ikramlar gibi ekstralar.\\n\\n### \ud83d\uddfa\ufe0f Rota ve Lokasyon Y\xf6netimi\\nAdmin panelinden detayl\u0131 **Rota Y\xf6netimi** yapabilirsiniz.\\n- Kalk\u0131\u015f ve Var\u0131\u015f noktalar\u0131 i\xe7in \xf6zel fiyatlar tan\u0131mlay\u0131n.\\n- \u0130ki nokta aras\u0131ndaki mesafeyi ve s\xfcreyi otomatik hesaplay\u0131n veya manuel girin.\\n\\n### \ud83d\udcb0 Esnek Fiyatland\u0131rma Motoru\\nTransferler i\xe7in geli\u015fmi\u015f fiyatland\u0131rma se\xe7enekleri:\\n- **Sabit Fiyat:** \\"Havaliman\u0131 -> \u015eehir Merkezi: 500 TL\\" gibi sabit rotalar olu\u015fturun.\\n- **Mesafe Bazl\u0131:** KM ba\u015f\u0131na \xfccretlendirme ile dinamik fiyatlar hesaplay\u0131n.\\n\\n### \ud83d\udd0d Geli\u015fmi\u015f Transfer Arama\\nYeni **`[mhm_rentiva_transfer_search]`** k\u0131sa kodu ile web sitenize profesyonel bir transfer arama motoru ekleyin.\\n- Tarih, saat, kalk\u0131\u015f ve var\u0131\u015f noktas\u0131 se\xe7imi.\\n- Yolcu say\u0131s\u0131 ve bagaj kapasitesine g\xf6re ara\xe7 filtreleme.\\n\\n### \ud83d\udee1\ufe0f Operasyonel Kontrol (Buffer Time)\\nAra\xe7lar\u0131n\u0131z\u0131n temizli\u011fi ve haz\u0131rl\u0131\u011f\u0131 i\xe7in iki rezervasyon aras\u0131na otomatik **Tampon S\xfcre (Buffer Time)** ekleyebilirsiniz. Art\u0131k ara\xe7lar\u0131n\u0131z\u0131n \\"M\xfcsait\\" durumu daha ger\xe7ek\xe7i y\xf6netiliyor.\\n\\n## \ud83d\udee0\ufe0f D\xfczeltmeler ve \u0130yile\u015ftirmeler\\n\\n- **Cart & Payment:** WooCommerce sepet entegrasyonu \\"Depozito\\" veya \\"Tam \xd6deme\\" se\xe7enekleriyle g\xfc\xe7lendirildi.\\n- **Data Integrity:** Transfer detaylar\u0131 (kalk\u0131\u015f/var\u0131\u015f, yolcu say\u0131s\u0131) art\u0131k sipari\u015f notlar\u0131na ve meta verilerine eksiksiz kaydediliyor.\\n\\n---\\n\\n**Nas\u0131l G\xfcncellerim?**\\nWordPress panelinizden otomatik g\xfcncelleme yapabilirsiniz. Herhangi bir sorun ya\u015farsan\u0131z l\xfctfen GitHub \xfczerinden veya destek sayfam\u0131zdan bize ula\u015f\u0131n.\\n\\nKeyifli s\xfcr\xfc\u015fler! \ud83c\udfce\ufe0f\ud83d\udca8"},{"id":"v4-5-5-released","metadata":{"permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/v4-5-5-released","editUrl":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade/mhm-rentiva-docs/tree/main/blog/2026-01-15-v4-5-5-released.md","source":"@site/i18n/tr/docusaurus-plugin-content-blog/2026-01-15-v4-5-5-released.md","title":"v4.5.5 Yay\u0131nda! \ud83d\ude80","description":"MHM Rentiva v4.5.5 s\xfcr\xfcm\xfc yay\u0131nland\u0131! Bu s\xfcr\xfcm, kararl\u0131l\u0131k iyile\u015ftirmeleri, kritik performans d\xfczeltmeleri ve dok\xfcmantasyon altyap\u0131s\u0131nda b\xfcy\xfck yenilikler i\xe7eriyor.","date":"2026-01-15T00:00:00.000Z","tags":[{"inline":true,"label":"release","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/release"},{"inline":true,"label":"update","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/update"},{"inline":true,"label":"v4.5.5","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/tags/v-4-5-5"}],"readingTime":0.64,"hasTruncateMarker":true,"authors":[{"name":"MaxHandMade","title":"Maintainer","url":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade","imageURL":"https://github.com/MaxHandMade.png","key":"maxhandmade","page":null}],"frontMatter":{"slug":"v4-5-5-released","title":"v4.5.5 Yay\u0131nda! \ud83d\ude80","authors":["maxhandmade"],"tags":["release","update","v4.5.5"],"date":"2026-01-15T00:00:00.000Z"},"unlisted":false,"prevItem":{"title":"v4.6.0 Yay\u0131nda! \ud83d\ude80","permalink":"/mhm-rentiva-docs/tr/blog/v4-6-0-released"}},"content":"MHM Rentiva **v4.5.5** s\xfcr\xfcm\xfc yay\u0131nland\u0131! Bu s\xfcr\xfcm, kararl\u0131l\u0131k iyile\u015ftirmeleri, kritik performans d\xfczeltmeleri ve dok\xfcmantasyon altyap\u0131s\u0131nda b\xfcy\xfck yenilikler i\xe7eriyor.\\n\\n\x3c!--truncate--\x3e\\n\\n## \ud83c\udf1f \xd6ne \xc7\u0131kanlar\\n\\n*   **G\xfcvenlik & Mimari:** Plugin kaynak kodlar\u0131 art\u0131k Private bir repoda korunurken, dok\xfcmantasyon (bu site) Public bir repoda herkesin eri\u015fimine a\xe7\u0131k hale getirildi.\\n*   **Performans:** Raporlama mod\xfcl\xfcndeki SQL sorgular\u0131, `DATE()` fonksiyonu kald\u0131r\u0131larak indeks kullan\u0131m\u0131na uygun hale getirildi. Art\u0131k \xe7ok daha h\u0131zl\u0131 \xe7al\u0131\u015f\u0131yor.\\n*   **Mobil Uyumluluk:** Ara\xe7 detay sayfalar\u0131 mobilde art\u0131k ta\u015fma yapm\u0131yor, butonlar ve g\xf6rseller tam uyumlu.\\n\\n## \ud83d\udee0\ufe0f D\xfczeltmeler\\n\\n*   **Fixed:** `Plugin.php` i\xe7indeki m\xfckerrer kodlar temizlendi.\\n*   **Fixed:** `ReportRepository` s\u0131n\u0131f\u0131ndaki yava\u015f sorgular optimize edildi.\\n*   **Fixed:** Ara\xe7 k\u0131yaslama sayfas\u0131ndaki hizalama sorunlar\u0131 giderildi.\\n*   **Fixed:** \\"Hizmete Kapal\u0131\\" (Out of Use) etiketi art\u0131k varyasyonlu \xfcr\xfcnlerde de do\u011fru \xe7al\u0131\u015f\u0131yor.\\n\\n## \ud83d\udce6 Y\xfckseltme\\n\\nWordPress panelinizden otomatik g\xfcncelleme yapabilirsiniz. Herhangi bir sorun ya\u015farsan\u0131z l\xfctfen GitHub \xfczerinden veya destek sayfam\u0131zdan bize ula\u015f\u0131n.\\n\\nKeyifli kiralamalar! \ud83d\ude97\ud83d\udca8"}]}}')}}]);